801 
802 class CreateToolTip(object):
803 
804  def __init__(self, widget, text='widget info'):
805  self.waittime = 500 #miliseconds
806  self.wraplength = 100 #pixels
807  self.widget = widget
808  self.text = text
809  self.widget.bind("<Enter>", self.enter)
810  self.widget.bind("<Leave>", self.leave)
811  self.widget.bind("<ButtonPress>", self.leave)
812  self.id = None
813  self.tw = None
814 
815  def enter(self, event=None):
816  self.schedule()
817 
818  def leave(self, event=None):
819  self.unschedule()
820  self.hidetip()
821 
822  def schedule(self):
823  self.unschedule()
824  self.id = self.widget.after(self.waittime, self.showtip)
825 
826  def unschedule(self):
827  id = self.id
828  self.id = None
829  if id:
830  self.widget.after_cancel(id)
831 
832  def showtip(self, event=None):
833  x = y = 0
834  x, y, cx, cy = self.widget.bbox("insert")
835  x += self.widget.winfo_rootx() + 25
836  y += self.widget.winfo_rooty() + 20
837  # creates a toplevel window
838  self.tw = Toplevel(self.widget)
839  # Leaves only the label and removes the app window
840  self.tw.wm_overrideredirect(True)
841  self.tw.wm_geometry("+%d+%d" % (x, y))
842  label = Label(self.tw, text=self.text, justify='left',
843  background="#ffffe0", foreground="#000000",
844  relief='solid', borderwidth=1,
845  wraplength = self.wraplength)
846  label.pack(ipadx=1)
847 
848  def hidetip(self):
849  tw = self.tw
850  self.tw= None
851  if tw:
852  tw.destroy()
853 
854  def configure(self, text):
855  self.text = text
856 #
857 # =========== Start widgets routines =============================
858

1907 def BSaveData():

1909 
1910  # open file to save data
1911  filename = asksaveasfilename(defaultextension = ".csv", filetypes=[("Comma Separated Values", "*.csv")])

1913  DataFile.write( 'Sample-#, CA-V, CA-I, CB-V, CB-I \n' )
1914  for index in range(len(VBuffA)):
1915  TimePnt = float((index+0.0)/SAMPLErate)
1916  DataFile.write( str(TimePnt) + ', ' + str(VBuffA[index]) + ', ' + str(IBuffA[index]) + ', '
1917  + str(VBuffB[index]) + ', ' + str(IBuffB[index]) + '\n')
1918  DataFile.close()

1934 def BSaveChannelData():
1935  global SAMPLErate, VBuffA, VBuffB, IBuffA, IBuffB, VBuffMA, VBuffMB, VBuffMC, VBuffMD
1936 
1937  # ask user for channel to save
1938  Channel = askstring("Choose Channel", "CA-V, CB-V, CA-I, CB-I\n MuxA, MuxB, MuxC, MuxD \n Channel:\n", initialvalue="CA-V")
1939  if (Channel == None): # If Cancel pressed, then None
1940  return
1941  # open file to save data
1942  filename = asksaveasfilename(defaultextension = ".csv", filetypes=[("Comma Separated Values", "*.csv")])
1943  DataFile = open(filename, 'w')
1944  if Channel == "CA-V":
1945  DataFile.write( 'Sample-#, CA-V\n' )
1946  for index in range(len(VBuffA)):
1947  TimePnt = float((index+0.0)/SAMPLErate)
1948  DataFile.write( str(TimePnt) + ', ' + str(VBuffA[index]) + '\n')
1949  elif Channel == "CA-I":
1950  DataFile.write( 'Sample-#, CA-I,\n' )
1951  for index in range(len(IBuffA)):
1952  TimePnt = float((index+0.0)/SAMPLErate)
1953  DataFile.write( str(TimePnt) + ', ' + str(IBuffA[index]) + '\n')
1954  elif Channel == "CB-V":
1955  DataFile.write( 'Sample-#, CB-V\n' )
1956  for index in range(len(VBuffB)):
1957  TimePnt = float((index+0.0)/SAMPLErate)
1958  DataFile.write( str(TimePnt) + ', ' + str(VBuffB[index]) + '\n')
1959  elif Channel == "CB-I":
1960  DataFile.write( 'Sample-#, CB-I,\n' )
1961  for index in range(len(IBuffB)):
1962  TimePnt = float((index+0.0)/SAMPLErate)
1963  DataFile.write( str(TimePnt) + ', ' + str(IBuffB[index]) + '\n')
1964  elif Channel == "MuxA":
1965  DataFile.write( 'Sample-#, MuxA\n' )
1966  for index in range(len(VBuffMA)):
1967  TimePnt = float((index+0.0)/SAMPLErate)
1968  DataFile.write( str(TimePnt) + ', ' + str(VBuffMA[index]) + '\n')
1969  elif Channel == "MuxB":
1970  DataFile.write( 'Sample-#, MuxB\n' )
1971  for index in range(len(VBuffMB)):
1972  TimePnt = float((index+0.0)/SAMPLErate)
1973  DataFile.write( str(TimePnt) + ', ' + str(VBuffMB[index]) + '\n')
1974  elif Channel == "MuxC":
1975  DataFile.write( 'Sample-#, MuxC\n' )
1976  for index in range(len(VBuffMC)):
1977  TimePnt = float((index+0.0)/SAMPLErate)
1978  DataFile.write( str(TimePnt) + ', ' + str(VBuffMC[index]) + '\n')
1979  elif Channel == "MuxD":
1980  DataFile.write( 'Sample-#, MuxD\n' )
1981  for index in range(len(VBuffMD)):
1982  TimePnt = float((index+0.0)/SAMPLErate)
1983  DataFile.write( str(TimePnt) + ', ' + str(VBuffMD[index]) + '\n')
1984  DataFile.close()

1986 def BReadData():
1987  global VBuffA, VBuffB, IBuffA, IBuffB, SHOWsamples
1988 
1989  # Read values from CVS file
1990  filename = askopenfilename(defaultextension = ".csv", filetypes=[("CSV files", "*.csv")])
1991  try:
1992  CSVFile = open(filename)
1993  dialect = csv.Sniffer().sniff(CSVFile.read(2048))
1994  CSVFile.seek(0)
1995  csv_f = csv.reader(CSVFile, dialect)
1996  VBuffA = []
1997  VBuffB = []
1998  IBuffA = []
1999  IBuffB = []
2000  SHOWsamples = 0
2001  for row in csv_f:
2002  try:
2003  VBuffA.append(float(row[1]))
2004  IBuffA.append(float(row[2]))
2005  VBuffB.append(float(row[3]))
2006  IBuffB.append(float(row[4]))
2007  SHOWsamples = SHOWsamples + 1
2008  except:
2009  print( 'skipping non-numeric row')
2010  VBuffA = numpy.array(VBuffA)
2011  IBuffA = numpy.array(IBuffA)
2012  VBuffB = numpy.array(VBuffB)
2013  IBuffB = numpy.array(IBuffB)
2014  CSVFile.close()
2015  UpdateTimeTrace()
2016  except:
2017  showwarning("WARNING","No such file found or wrong format!")
2018

2116  CHB_A2.set(float(chb_A2Entry.get()))

2128  CalFile.write('CHB_A2.set(' + str(CHB_A2.get()) + ')\n')

2131  CalFile.write('cha_TC2Entry.delete(0,END)\n')

2503  MidV2 = (MaxV2+MinV2)/2

2511  DCString = ' {0:.2f} '.format(MidI1)

2513  DCString = ' {0:.2f} '.format(MidV2)

2515  DCString = ' {0:.2f} '.format(MidI2)

2523  DCString = ' {0:.2f} '.format(MidVMuxB)

2527  DCString = ' {0:.2f} '.format(MidVMuxD)
2528 #
2529  TRIGGERlevel = eval(DCString)
2530  TRIGGERentry.delete(0,END)
2531  TRIGGERentry.insert(4, DCString)

2750  CHB.mode = Mode.HI_Z_SPLIT # Put CHB in Hi Z split mode

2765 def BStart():
2766  global RUNstatus, PowerStatus, devx, PwrBt, DevID, FWRevOne, session, AWGSync
2767  global contloop, discontloop, TIMEdiv, First_Slow_sweep
2768  global TimeDisp, XYDisp, PhADisp, FreqDisp, BodeDisp, IADisp
2769 
2770  if DevID == "No Device":
2771  showwarning("WARNING","No Device Plugged In!")
2772  elif FWRevOne == 0.0:
2773  showwarning("WARNING","Out of data Firmware!")
2774  elif TimeDisp.get() == 0 and XYDisp.get() == 0 and PhADisp.get() == 0 and FreqDisp.get() == 0 and BodeDisp.get() == 0 and IADisp.get() == 0:
2775  showwarning("WARNING","Enable at least one Instrument!")
2776  else:
2777  if PowerStatus == 0:
2778  PowerStatus = 1
2779  PwrBt.config(style="Pwr.TButton",text="PWR-On")
2780  devx.ctrl_transfer( 0x40, 0x51, 49, 0, 0, 0, 100) # turn on analog power
2781  if (RUNstatus.get() == 0):
2782  RUNstatus.set(1)
2783  if AWGSync.get() == 0:
2784  session.flush()
2785  CHA.mode = Mode.HI_Z_SPLIT # Put CHA in Hi Z mode
2786  CHB.mode = Mode.HI_Z_SPLIT # Put CHB in Hi Z mode
2787  BAWGEnab()
2788  if not session.continuous:
2789  session.start(0)
2790  time.sleep(0.02) # wait awhile here for some reason
2791  elif session.continuous:
2792  session.end()
2793  session.flush()
2794  CHA.mode = Mode.HI_Z_SPLIT # Put CHA in Hi Z mode
2795  CHB.mode = Mode.HI_Z_SPLIT # Put CHB in Hi Z mode
2796 
2808  BAWGEnab()
2809  else:
2810  contloop = 0
2811  discontloop = 1
2812  if session.continuous:
2813  session.end() # end continuous session mode
2814 
2815  # UpdateTimeScreen() # Always Update
2816  if TIMEdiv >= 100:
2817  First_Slow_sweep = 0
2818  else:
2819  First_Slow_sweep = 1
2820 #$ Start running Ohmmeter tool

2828  session.start(0)

2833  else:
2834  contloop = 0
2835  discontloop = 1

2919 def BTime():
2920  global TIMEdiv, TMsb, RUNstatus, Two_X_Sample, ETSDisp, FWRevOne, ChopMuxMode
2921  global ShowC1_V, ShowC1_I, ShowC2_V, ShowC2_I, AWGSync

2923  try: # get time scale in mSec/div
2924  TIMEdiv = float(eval(TMsb.get()))
2925  if TIMEdiv < 0.0002:
2926  TIMEdiv = 0.01
2927  TMsb.delete(0,"end")
2928  TMsb.insert(0,TIMEdiv)
2929  except:
2930  TIMEdiv = 0.5
2931  TMsb.delete(0,"end")
2932  TMsb.insert(0,TIMEdiv)
2933  # Switch to 2X sampleling if time scale small enough and not runing ETS
2934  # and not in analog input mux Chop mode.
2935  if ETSDisp.get() == 0 and ChopMuxMode.get() == 0:
2936  Samples_per_div = TIMEdiv * 100.0 # samples per mSec @ base sample rate
2937  if FWRevOne > 2.16:
2938  if Samples_per_div < 20.0:
2939  NumTraces = ShowC1_V.get() + ShowC1_I.get() + ShowC2_V.get() + ShowC2_I.get()
2940  if NumTraces > 2 and AWGSync.get() == 0:
2941  showwarning("WARNING","You need to Select only 2 Traces or Enable AWG Sync Mode!")
2942  BStop()
2943  Two_X_Sample.set(1)
2944  TraceSelectADC_Mux()
2945  else:
2946  Two_X_Sample.set(0)
2947  SetADC_Mux()
2948  #
2949  if RUNstatus.get() == 0: # if not running
2950  UpdateTimeTrace() # Update

3178  else:

3213  if TRACEresetTime == True:

3223  else:

3231  if TRACEresetTime == True:

3240  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, 0x50, PIO_1, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set PIO 1 to 0
3241  else:

3256  else: # do this if in Chop mode

3259  if TRACEmodeTime.get() == 0 and TRACEresetTime == False:

3261  elif TRACEmodeTime.get() == 1:

3271  if IADisp.get() > 0 or BodeDisp.get() > 0:
3272  CutDC.set(1) # remove DC portion of waveform
3273  AWGSync.set(1) # Impedance analyzer and Bode plotter must be run in discontinuous mode
3274  if BodeDisp.get() > 0:

3277  if FregPoint < 100.0:
3278  SMPfft = 16384
3279  elif FregPoint < 500.0:
3280  SMPfft = 8192
3281  elif FregPoint < 2000.0:
3282  SMPfft = 4096
3283  else:
3284  SMPfft = 2048
3285  if Two_X_Sample.get() > 0 and FregPoint < 2000.0:
3286  SMPfft = SMPfft * 2
3287

3294 def Ohm_Analog_In():
3295  global RMode, CHATestVEntry, CHATestREntry, CHA, CHB, devx, OhmA0, OhmA1, discontloop
3296  global AWGAMode, AWGBMode, AWGAShape, AWGSync, AWGBTerm, AWGAOffsetEntry
3297  global AWGAIOMode, AWGBIOMode, Two_X_Sample
3298 
3299 # Do input probe Calibration CH1VGain, CH2VGain, CH1VOffset, CH2VOffset
3300  try:
3301  InOffA = float(eval(CHAVOffsetEntry.get()))
3302  except:
3303  CHAVOffsetEntry.delete(0,END)
3304  CHAVOffsetEntry.insert(0, InOffA)
3305  try:
3306  InGainA = float(eval(CHAVGainEntry.get()))
3307  except:
3308  CHAVGainEntry.delete(0,END)
3309  CHAVGainEntry.insert(0, InGainA)
3310  try:
3311  InOffB = float(eval(CHBVOffsetEntry.get()))
3312  except:
3313  CHBVOffsetEntry.delete(0,END)
3314  CHBVOffsetEntry.insert(0, InOffB)
3315  try:
3316  InGainB = float(eval(CHBVGainEntry.get()))
3317  except:
3318  CHBVGainEntry.delete(0,END)
3319  CHBVGainEntry.insert(0, InGainB)
3320  try:
3321  CurOffA = float(CHAIOffsetEntry.get())
3322  except:
3323  CurOffA = 0.0
3324  try:
3325  CurOffB = float(CHBIOffsetEntry.get())
3326  except:
3327  CurOffB = 0.0
3328  try:
3329  CurGainA = float(CHAIGainEntry.get())
3330  except:
3331  CurGainA = 1.0
3332  try:
3333  CurGainB = float(CHBIGainEntry.get())
3334  except:
3335  CurGainB = 1.0
3336  try:
3337  chatestv = float(eval(CHATestVEntry.get()))
3338  if chatestv > 5.0:
3339  chatestv = 5.0
3340  CHATestVEntry.delete(0,END)
3341  CHATestVEntry.insert(0, chatestv)
3342  except:
3343  CHATestVEntry.delete(0,END)
3344  CHATestVEntry.insert(0, chatestv)
3345  try:
3346  chatestr = float(eval(CHATestREntry.get()))
3347  except:
3348  CHATestREntry.delete(0,END)
3349  CHATestREntry.insert(0, chatestr)
3350  #
3351  DCVA0 = DCVB0 = DCIA0 = DCIB0 = 0.0 # initalize measurment variable
3352  RIN = 1000000 # nominal ALM1000 input resistance is 1 Mohm
3353  Two_X_Sample.set(0) # make sure we are in 1V sample rate mode
3354  SetADC_Mux()
3355  # set A and B channels
3356  AWGAMode.set(0) # Set AWG A to SVMI
3357  AWGAShape.set(0) # DC
3358  AWGBMode.set(2) # Set AWG B to Hi-Z
3359  AWGAIOMode.set(0) # turn off Split I/O mode
3360  AWGBIOMode.set(0) # turn off Split I/O mode
3361  AWGAOffsetEntry.delete(0,"end")
3362  AWGAOffsetEntry.insert(0, chatestv)
3363  BAWGAModeLabel()
3364  BAWGBModeLabel() # update AWG labels
3365 
3366  if RMode.get() == 0:
3367  AWGBTerm.set(0)
3368  else:
3369  AWGBTerm.set(1)
3370  #
3371  if AWGSync.get() > 0: # awg syn flag set so run in discontinuous mode
3372  if discontloop > 0:
3373  session.flush()
3374  else:
3375  discontloop = 1
3376  time.sleep(0.01)
3377  BAWGEnab()
3378  ADsignal1 = devx.get_samples(210) # get samples for both channel A and B
3379  # time.sleep(1000.0/SHOWsamples)
3380  else: # running in continuous mode
3381  if session.continuous:
3382  ADsignal1 = devx.read(210, -1, True) # get samples for both channel A and B
3383  #
3384  # get_samples returns a list of values for voltage [0] and current [1]
3385  for index in range(200): # calculate average
3386  DCVA0 += ADsignal1[index+10][0][0] # VAdata # Sum for average CA voltage
3387  DCVB0 += ADsignal1[index+10][1][0] # VBdata # Sum for average CB voltage
3388  DCIA0 += ADsignal1[index+10][0][1] # Sum for average CA current
3389  DCIB0 += ADsignal1[index+10][1][1] # Sum for average CB current
3390 
3391  DCVA0 = DCVA0 / 200.0 # calculate average
3392  DCVB0 = DCVB0 / 200.0 # calculate average
3393  DCIA0 = DCIA0 / 200.0 # calculate average
3394  DCIB0 = DCIB0 / 200.0 # calculate average
3395  DCVA0 = (DCVA0 - InOffA) * InGainA
3396  DCVB0 = (DCVB0 - InOffB) * InGainB
3397  DCIA0 = ((DCIA0*1000) - CurOffA) * CurGainA
3398  DCIB0 = ((DCIB0*1000) - CurOffB) * CurGainB
3399  if RMode.get() == 0: # external resistor
3400  DCM = chatestr * (DCVB0/(DCVA0-DCVB0))
3401  DCR = (DCM * RIN) / (RIN - DCM) # correct for channel B input resistance
3402  else: # use internal 50 ohm resistor
3403  DCR = chatestr * ((DCVA0-DCVB0)/DCVB0)
3404  if DCR < 1000:
3405  OhmString = '{0:.2f} '.format(DCR) + "Ohms "# format with 2 decimal places
3406  else:
3407  OhmString = '{0:.3f} '.format(DCR/1000) + "KOhms " # divide by 1000 and format with 3 decimal places
3408  IAString = "Meas " + ' {0:.2f} '.format(DCIA0) + " mA " + ' {0:.2f} '.format(DCVB0) + " V"
3409  OhmA0.config(text = OhmString) # change displayed value
3410  OhmA1.config(text = IAString) # change displayed value
3411 #
3412  time.sleep(0.1)
3413  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, 0x51, 38, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set CHB GND switch to open
3414 
3416 def Analog_Time_In():
3417  global TIMEdiv, TMsb, TRACEmodeTime, TRACEresetTime, TRACEaverage
3418  global VBuffMA, VmemoryMuxA, VBuffMB, VmemoryMuxB, VBuffMC, VmemoryMuxC, VBuffMD, VmemoryMuxD
3419  global CHAVOffsetEntry, CHAVGainEntry, CHBVOffsetEntry, CHBVGainEntry
3420  global CHAIOffsetEntry, CHBIOffsetEntry, CHAIGainEntry, CHBIGainEntry
3421  global InOffA, InGainA, InOffB, InGainB
3422  global CurOffA, CurOffB, CurGainA, CurGainB
3423  global PhADisp, PhAScreenStatus, MuxScreenStatus, ChopMuxMode
3424  global Show_CBA, Show_CBB, Show_CBC, Show_CBD
3425 
3426  # get time scale
3427  try:
3428  TIMEdiv = eval(TMsb.get())
3429  except:
3430  TIMEdiv = 0.5
3431  TMsb.delete(0,"end")
3432  TMsb.insert(0,TIMEdiv)
3433  if TIMEdiv < 0.0002:
3434  TIMEdiv = 0.01
3435  #
3436 # Do input divider Calibration CH1VGain, CH2VGain, CH1VOffset, CH2VOffset
3437  try:
3438  InOffA = float(eval(CHAVOffsetEntry.get()))
3439  except:
3440  CHAVOffsetEntry.delete(0,END)
3441  CHAVOffsetEntry.insert(0, InOffA)
3442  try:
3443  InGainA = float(eval(CHAVGainEntry.get()))
3444  except:
3445  CHAVGainEntry.delete(0,END)
3446  CHAVGainEntry.insert(0, InGainA)
3447  try:
3448  InOffB = float(eval(CHBVOffsetEntry.get()))
3449  except:
3450  CHBVOffsetEntry.delete(0,END)
3451  CHBVOffsetEntry.insert(0, InOffB)
3452  try:
3453  InGainB = float(eval(CHBVGainEntry.get()))
3454  except:
3455  CHBVGainEntry.delete(0,END)
3456  CHBVGainEntry.insert(0, InGainB)
3457  try:
3458  CurOffA = float(CHAIOffsetEntry.get()) #/1000.0 # convert to Amps # leave in mA
3459  except:
3460  CurOffA = 0.0
3461  try:
3462  CurOffB = float(CHBIOffsetEntry.get())#/1000.0 # convert to Amps
3463  except:
3464  CurOffB = 0.0
3465  try:
3466  CurGainA = float(CHAIGainEntry.get())
3467  except:
3468  CurGainA = 1.0
3469  try:
3470  CurGainB = float(CHBIGainEntry.get())
3471  except:
3472  CurGainB = 1.0
3473 # Dedecide which Fast or Slow sweep routine to call
3474  if TIMEdiv > 500:
3475  Analog_Slow_time() # failed attempt as rolling trace
3476  else:
3477  Analog_Fast_time()
3478 #
3479  if PhADisp.get() > 0 and PhAScreenStatus.get() == 1:
3480  Analog_Phase_In()
3481 #

3754  else:

3758  # waite to finish then return to open termination

3760  devx.ctrl_transfer( 0x40, 0x51, 33, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set CHA GND switch to open

3773  #
3774  else:

3776 
3777  # get_samples returns a list of values for voltage [0] and current [1]
3778  for index in range(NumSamples): # calculate average
3779  DCVA0 += ADsignal1[index][0][0] # Sum for average CA voltage
3780  DCVB0 += ADsignal1[index][1][0] # Sum for average CB voltage
3781  DCIA0 += ADsignal1[index][0][1] # Sum for average CA current
3782  DCIB0 += ADsignal1[index][1][1] # Sum for average CB current
3783  DCVA0 = DCVA0/(NumSamples) # calculate V average
3784  DCVB0 = DCVB0/(NumSamples) # calculate V average
3785  DCVA0 = (DCVA0 - InOffA) * InGainA
3786  DCVB0 = (DCVB0 - InOffB) * InGainB
3787  DCIA0 = DCIA0/(NumSamples) # calculate I average
3788  DCIB0 = DCIB0/(NumSamples) # calculate I average
3789  DCIA0 = DCIA0 * 1000 # convert to mA
3790  DCIB0 = DCIB0 * 1000 # convert to mA
3791  DCIA0 = (DCIA0 - CurOffA) * CurGainA
3792  DCIB0 = (DCIB0 - CurOffB) * CurGainB
3793 # Shift in next new sample

3795  VBuffB = shift_buffer(VBuffB, -1, DCVB0)
3796  IBuffA = shift_buffer(IBuffA, -1, DCIA0)
3797  IBuffB = shift_buffer(IBuffB, -1, DCIB0)
3798 # Calculate measurement values
3799  DCV1 = numpy.mean(VBuffA)
3800  DCV2 = numpy.mean(VBuffB)
3801  DCI1 = numpy.mean(IBuffA)
3802  DCI2 = numpy.mean(IBuffB)
3803 # find min and max values
3804  MinV1 = numpy.amin(VBuffA)
3805  MaxV1 = numpy.amax(VBuffA)
3806  MinV2 = numpy.amin(VBuffB)
3807  MaxV2 = numpy.amax(VBuffB)
3808  MinI1 = numpy.amin(IBuffA)
3809  MaxI1 = numpy.amax(IBuffA)
3810  MinI2 = numpy.amin(IBuffB)
3811  MaxI2 = numpy.amax(IBuffB)
3812 # RMS value = square root of average of the data record squared
3813  SV1 = numpy.sqrt(numpy.mean(numpy.square(VBuffA)))
3814  SI1 = numpy.sqrt(numpy.mean(numpy.square(IBuffA)))
3815  SV2 = numpy.sqrt(numpy.mean(numpy.square(VBuffB)))
3816  SI2 = numpy.sqrt(numpy.mean(numpy.square(IBuffB)))
3817  SVA_B = numpy.sqrt(numpy.mean(numpy.square(VBuffA-VBuffB)))

3836 def Analog_Chop_Time():
3837  global ADsignal1, VBuffMA, VBuffMB, VBuffMC, VBuffMD
3838  global DCVMuxA, MinVMuxA, MaxVMuxA, MidVMuxA, PPVMuxA, SVMuxA
3839  global DCVMuxB, MinVMuxB, MaxVMuxB, MidVMuxB, PPVMuxB, SVMuxB
3840  global DCVMuxC, MinVMuxC, MaxVMuxC, MidVMuxC, PPVMuxC, SVMuxC
3841  global DCVMuxD, MinVMuxD, MaxVMuxD, MidVMuxD, PPVMuxD, SVMuxD
3842  global SHOWsamples, ChopModeFilter
3843 
3844  VBuffMA = [] # Clear the Mux A array
3845  VBuffMB = [] # Clear the Mux B array
3846  VBuffMC = [] # Clear the Mux C array
3847  VBuffMD = [] # Clear the Mux D array
3848  index = 1
3849  while index < SHOWsamples-3: # build arrays VBuffMA, VBuffMB, VBuffMC, VBuffMD
3850  pointer = 0
3851  while pointer < 4:
3852  VBuffMA.append(ADsignal1[index+3][0][0]) # chop AIN into Mux A and B
3853  VBuffMB.append(ADsignal1[index+1][0][0])
3854  VBuffMC.append(ADsignal1[index+3][1][0]) # chop BIN into Mux C and D
3855  VBuffMD.append(ADsignal1[index+1][1][0])
3856  pointer = pointer + 1
3857  index = index + 4
3858  VBuffMA = numpy.array(VBuffMA)
3859  VBuffMB = numpy.array(VBuffMB)
3860  VBuffMC = numpy.array(VBuffMC)
3861  VBuffMD = numpy.array(VBuffMD)
3862  # apply a digital filter to interpolate back to 100 KSPS
3863  VBuffMA = numpy.pad(VBuffMA, (4, 0), "edge")
3864  VBuffMA = numpy.convolve(VBuffMA, ChopModeFilter )
3865  VBuffMA = numpy.roll(VBuffMA, -4)
3866  VBuffMB = numpy.pad(VBuffMB, (4, 0), "edge")
3867  VBuffMB = numpy.convolve(VBuffMB, ChopModeFilter)
3868  VBuffMB = numpy.roll(VBuffMB, -6)
3869  VBuffMC = numpy.pad(VBuffMC, (4, 0), "edge")
3870  VBuffMC = numpy.convolve(VBuffMC, ChopModeFilter )
3871  VBuffMC = numpy.roll(VBuffMC, -4)
3872  VBuffMD = numpy.pad(VBuffMD, (4, 0), "edge")
3873  VBuffMD = numpy.convolve(VBuffMD, ChopModeFilter )
3874  VBuffMD = numpy.roll(VBuffMD, -6)
3875  # calculate waveform scalers
3876  EndSample = SHOWsamples-4
3877  DCVMuxA = numpy.mean(VBuffMA[:EndSample])
3878  MinVMuxA = numpy.amin(VBuffMA[:EndSample])
3879  MaxVMuxA = numpy.amax(VBuffMA[:EndSample])
3880  MidVMuxA = (MaxVMuxA+MinVMuxA)/2.0
3881  PPVMuxA = MaxVMuxA-MinVMuxA
3882 #
3883  DCVMuxB = numpy.mean(VBuffMB[:EndSample])
3884  MinVMuxB = numpy.amin(VBuffMB[:EndSample])
3885  MaxVMuxB = numpy.amax(VBuffMB[:EndSample])
3886  MidVMuxB = (MaxVMuxB+MinVMuxB)/2.0
3887  PPVMuxB = MaxVMuxB-MinVMuxB
3888 #
3889  DCVMuxC = numpy.mean(VBuffMC[:EndSample])
3890  MinVMuxC = numpy.amin(VBuffMC[:EndSample])
3891  MaxVMuxC = numpy.amax(VBuffMC[:EndSample])
3892  MidVMuxC = (MaxVMuxC+MinVMuxC)/2.0
3893  PPVMuxC = MaxVMuxC-MinVMuxC
3894 #
3895  DCVMuxD = numpy.mean(VBuffMD[:EndSample])
3896  MinVMuxD = numpy.amin(VBuffMD[:EndSample])
3897  MaxVMuxD = numpy.amax(VBuffMD[:EndSample])
3898  MidVMuxD = (MaxVMuxD+MinVMuxD)/2.0
3899  PPVMuxD = MaxVMuxD-MinVMuxD
3900  # RMS value = square root of average of the data record squared
3901  SVMuxA = numpy.sqrt(numpy.mean(numpy.square(VBuffMA[:EndSample])))
3902  SVMuxB = numpy.sqrt(numpy.mean(numpy.square(VBuffMB[:EndSample])))
3903  SVMuxC = numpy.sqrt(numpy.mean(numpy.square(VBuffMC[:EndSample])))
3904  SVMuxD = numpy.sqrt(numpy.mean(numpy.square(VBuffMD[:EndSample])))

4633 #
4634 # Function to calculate relative phase angle between two sine waves of the same frequency
4635 # Removes any DC content
4636 def Sine_Phase():
4637  global DCV1, DCV2, VBuffA, VBuffB
4638 
4639  sum1 = 0.0
4640  sum2 = 0.0
4641  sum12 = 0.0
4642  i = 0
4643  n = len(VBuffA)
4644  while i < n:
4645  sum1 += (VBuffA[i]-DCV1)*(VBuffA[i]-DCV1)
4646  sum2 += (VBuffB[i]-DCV2)*(VBuffB[i]-DCV2)
4647  sum12 += (VBuffA[i]-DCV1)*(VBuffB[i]-DCV2)
4648  i += 1
4649  return math.acos(sum12/math.sqrt(sum1*sum2))*180.0/numpy.pi
4650 #
4651 # High Pass y[n] = alpha * (y[n-1] + x[n] - x[n-1])
4652 # Low Pass y[n] = y[n-1] + (alpha * ((x[n] - x[n-1]))
4653 # All Pass y[n] = alpha * y[n-1] - alpha * (x[n] + x[n-1])
4654 # All Pass y[n] = alpha * (y[n-1] - x[n] - x[n-1])
4655 
4656 
4658 def Digital_RC_High_Pass( InBuff, TC1, Gain ):
4659  global SAMPLErate
4660 
4661  OutBuff = []
4662  n = len(InBuff)
4663  Delta = 1.0/SAMPLErate
4664  TC = TC1 * 1.0E-6
4665  Alpha = TC / (TC + Delta)
4666  OutBuff.append(InBuff[1]-InBuff[0]) # set inital sample to derivative (difference of first two samples)
4667  i = 1
4668  while i < n:
4669  OutBuff.append( Alpha * (OutBuff[i-1] + InBuff[i] - InBuff[i-1]) )
4670  i += 1
4671  OutBuff = numpy.array(OutBuff)
4672  OutBuff = InBuff + (OutBuff * Gain)
4673  return OutBuff
4674 
4676 def Digital_RC_Low_Pass( InBuff, TC1, Gain ): # TC1 is in micro seconds
4677  global SAMPLErate
4678 
4679  OutBuff = []
4680  n = len(InBuff)
4681  Delta = 1.0/SAMPLErate
4682  TC = TC1 * 1.0E-6
4683  Alpha = Delta / (TC + Delta)
4684  i = 1
4685  OutBuff.append(Alpha*InBuff[0])
4686  while i < n:
4687  OutBuff.append( OutBuff[i-1] + (Alpha * (InBuff[i] - InBuff[i-1])) )
4688  i += 1
4689  OutBuff = numpy.array(OutBuff)
4690  OutBuff = (OutBuff * Gain)
4691  return OutBuff
4692 
4696 def shift_buffer(arr, num, fill_value=numpy.nan):
4697  result = numpy.empty_like(arr)
4698  if num > 0:
4699  result[:num] = fill_value
4700  result[num:] = arr[:-num]
4701  elif num < 0:
4702  result[num:] = fill_value
4703  result[:num] = arr[-num:]
4704  else:
4705  result[:] = arr
4706  return result

5018 def MakeHistogram():
5019  global VBuffA, VBuffB, IBuffA, IBuffB, HBuffA, HBuffB
5020  global CH1pdvRange, CHAOffset, CH2pdvRange, CHBOffset
5021  global ShowC1_V, ShowC1_I, ShowC2_V, ShowC2_I, Xsignal
5022  global DCV1, DCV2, MinV1, MaxV1, MinV2, MaxV2
5023  global DCI1, DCI2, MinI1, MaxI1, MinI2, MaxI2
5024  global VABase, VATop, VBBase, VBTop
5025 
5026  if ShowC1_V.get() == 1 or Xsignal.get() == 6:
5027  CHAGridMax = (5 * CH1pdvRange ) + CHAOffset # Calculate CHA Grid Min and Max
5028  CHAGridMin = (-5 * CH1pdvRange ) + CHAOffset
5029  VAMid = (MinV1 + MaxV1)/2 # Find CHA mid value
5030  HBuffA = numpy.histogram(VBuffA, bins=5000, range=[CHAGridMin, CHAGridMax] )
5031  LowerPeak = 0
5032  UpperPeak = 0
5033  b = 0
5034  while (b < 4999):
5035  if HBuffA[0][b] > HBuffA[0][LowerPeak] and HBuffA[1][b] < VAMid:
5036  LowerPeak = b
5037  VABase = HBuffA[1][b]
5038  if HBuffA[0][b] > HBuffA[0][UpperPeak] and HBuffA[1][b] > VAMid:
5039  UpperPeak = b
5040  VATop = HBuffA[1][b]
5041  b = b + 1
5042  if ShowC2_V.get() == 1 or Xsignal.get() == 7:
5043  CHBGridMax = (5 * CH2pdvRange ) + CHBOffset # Calculate CHB Grid Min and Max
5044  CHBGridMin = (-5 * CH2pdvRange ) + CHBOffset
5045  VBMid = (MinV2 + MaxV2)/2 # Find CHB mid value
5046  HBuffB = numpy.histogram(VBuffB, bins=5000, range=[CHBGridMin, CHBGridMax] )
5047  LowerPeak = 0
5048  UpperPeak = 0
5049  b = 0
5050  while (b < 4999):
5051  if HBuffB[0][b] > HBuffB[0][LowerPeak] and HBuffB[1][b] < VBMid:
5052  LowerPeak = b
5053  VBBase = HBuffB[1][b]
5054  if HBuffB[0][b] > HBuffB[0][UpperPeak] and HBuffB[1][b] > VBMid:
5055  UpperPeak = b
5056  VBTop = HBuffB[1][b]
5057  b = b + 1

5067 def FindRisingEdge(Trace1, Trace2):
5068  global MinV1, MaxV1, MinV2, MaxV2, HoldOff, TRIGGERsample, TgInput, LShift
5069  global ETSrecord, DISsamples
5070  global SHOWsamples, SAMPLErate, CHAperiod, CHAfreq, CHBperiod, CHBfreq
5071  global CHAHW, CHALW, CHADCy, CHBHW, CHBLW, CHBDCy, ShowC1_V, ShowC2_V
5072  global CHABphase, CHBADelayR1, CHBADelayR2, CHBADelayF
5073 
5074  anr1 = bnr1 = 0
5075  anf1 = bnf1 = 1
5076  anr2 = bnr2 = 2
5077  hldn = int(HoldOff * SAMPLErate/1000)
5078  # print(DISsamples, len(Trace1))
5079  if TgInput.get() > 0: # if triggering right shift arrays to undo trigger left shift
5080  Trace1 = numpy.roll(Trace1, -LShift)
5081  Trace2 = numpy.roll(Trace2, -LShift)
5082  else:
5083  Trace1 = numpy.roll(Trace1, -hldn)
5084  Trace2 = numpy.roll(Trace2, -hldn)
5085  try:
5086  MidV1 = (numpy.amax(Trace1)+numpy.amin(Trace1))/2.0
5087  MidV2 = (numpy.amax(Trace2)+numpy.amin(Trace2))/2.0
5088  except:
5089  MidV1 = (MinV1+MaxV1)/2
5090  MidV2 = (MinV2+MaxV2)/2
5091 # search Trace 1
5092 
5099  Arising = [i for (i, val) in enumerate(Trace1) if val >= MidV1 and Trace1[i-1] < MidV1]
5100  Afalling = [i for (i, val) in enumerate(Trace1) if val <= MidV1 and Trace1[i-1] > MidV1]
5101  AIrising = [i - (Trace1[i] - MidV1)/(Trace1[i] - Trace1[i-1]) for i in Arising]
5102  AIfalling = [i - (MidV1 - Trace1[i])/(Trace1[i-1] - Trace1[i]) for i in Afalling]
5103 
5104  CHAfreq = SAMPLErate / numpy.mean(numpy.diff(AIrising))
5105  CHAperiod = (numpy.mean(numpy.diff(AIrising)) * 1000.0) / SAMPLErate # time in mSec
5106 # Catch zero length array?
5107  try:
5108  Dummy_read = Arising[0]
5109  except:
5110  return
5111  if len(Arising) > 0 or len(Afalling) > 0:
5112  if Arising[0] > 0:
5113  try:
5114  anr1 = AIrising[0]
5115  except:
5116  anr1 = 0
5117  try:
5118  anr2 = AIrising[1]
5119  except:
5120  anr2 = SHOWsamples
5121  try:
5122  if AIfalling[0] < AIrising[0]:
5123  anf1 = AIfalling[1]
5124  else:
5125  anf1 = AIfalling[0]
5126  except:
5127  anf1 = 1
5128  else:
5129  try:
5130  anr1 = AIrising[1]
5131  except:
5132  anr1 = 0
5133  try:
5134  anr2 = AIrising[2]
5135  except:
5136  anr2 = SHOWsamples
5137  try:
5138  if AIfalling[1] < AIrising[1]:
5139  anf1 = AIfalling[2]
5140  else:
5141  anf1 = AIfalling[1]
5142  except:
5143  anf1 = 1
5144 # search Trace 2
5145 
5152  Brising = [i for (i, val) in enumerate(Trace2) if val >= MidV2 and Trace2[i-1] < MidV2]
5153  Bfalling = [i for (i, val) in enumerate(Trace2) if val <= MidV2 and Trace2[i-1] > MidV2]
5154  BIrising = [i - (Trace2[i] - MidV2)/(Trace2[i] - Trace2[i-1]) for i in Brising]
5155  BIfalling = [i - (MidV2 - Trace2[i])/(Trace2[i-1] - Trace2[i]) for i in Bfalling]
5156 
5157  CHBfreq = SAMPLErate / numpy.mean(numpy.diff(BIrising))
5158  CHBperiod = (numpy.mean(numpy.diff(BIrising)) * 1000.0) / SAMPLErate # time in mSec
5159 # Catch zero length array?
5160  try:
5161  Dummy_read = Brising[0]
5162  except:
5163  return
5164  if len(Brising) > 0 or len(Bfalling) > 0:
5165  if Brising[0] > 0:
5166  try:
5167  bnr1 = BIrising[0]
5168  except:
5169  bnr1 = 0
5170  try:
5171  bnr2 = BIrising[1]
5172  except:
5173  bnr2 = SHOWsamples
5174  try:
5175  if BIfalling[0] < BIrising[0]:
5176  bnf1 = BIfalling[1]
5177  else:
5178  bnf1 = BIfalling[0]
5179  except:
5180  bnf1 = 1
5181  else:
5182  try:
5183  bnr1 = BIrising[1]
5184  except:
5185  bnr1 = 0
5186  try:
5187  bnr2 = BIrising[2]
5188  except:
5189  bnr2 = SHOWsamples
5190  try:
5191  if BIfalling[1] < BIrising[1]:
5192  bnf1 = BIfalling[2]
5193  else:
5194  bnf1 = BIfalling[1]
5195  except:
5196  bnf1 = 1
5197  #
5198  CHAHW = float(((anf1 - anr1) * 1000.0) / SAMPLErate)
5199  CHALW = float(((anr2 - anf1) * 1000.0) / SAMPLErate)
5200  CHADCy = float(anf1 - anr1) / float(anr2 - anr1) * 100.0 # in percent
5201  CHBHW = float(((bnf1 - bnr1) * 1000.0) / SAMPLErate)
5202  CHBLW = float(((bnr2 - bnf1) * 1000.0) / SAMPLErate)
5203  CHBDCy = float(bnf1 - bnr1) / float(bnr2 - bnr1) * 100.0 # in percent
5204 #
5205  if bnr1 > anr1:
5206  CHBADelayR1 = float((bnr1 - anr1) * 1000.0 / SAMPLErate)
5207  else:
5208  CHBADelayR1 = float((bnr2 - anr1) * 1000.0 / SAMPLErate)
5209  CHBADelayR2 = float((bnr2 - anr2) * 1000.0 / SAMPLErate)
5210  CHBADelayF = float((bnf1 - anf1) * 1000.0 / SAMPLErate)
5211  try:
5212  CHABphase = 360.0*(float((bnr1 - anr1) * 1000.0 / SAMPLErate))/CHAperiod
5213  except:
5214  CHABphase = 0.0
5215  if CHABphase < 0.0:
5216  CHABphase = CHABphase + 360.0
5217 
5218 def ReInterploateTrigger(TrgBuff):
5219  global DX, TRIGGERsample, TRIGGERlevel
5220 
5221  DX = 0
5222  n = TRIGGERsample
5223  DY = TrgBuff[int(n)] - TrgBuff[int(n+1)]
5224  if DY != 0.0:
5225  DX = (TRIGGERlevel - TrgBuff[int(n+1)])/DY # calculate interpolated trigger point
5226  else:
5227  DX = 0

5229 def FindTriggerSample(TrgBuff): # find trigger time sample point of passed waveform array
5230  global AutoLevel, TgInput, TRIGGERlevel, TRIGGERentry, DX, SAMPLErate, Is_Triggered
5231  global HoldOffentry, HozPossentry, TRIGGERsample, TRACEsize, HozPoss, hozpos
5232  global Trigger_LPF_length, LPFTrigger
5233 
5234  # Set the TRACEsize variable
5235  TRACEsize = SHOWsamples # Set the trace length
5236  DX = 0
5237  Is_Triggered = 0
5238  if LPFTrigger.get() > 0:
5239  TFiltCoef = [] # empty coef array
5240  for n in range(Trigger_LPF_length.get()):
5241  TFiltCoef.append(float(1.0/Trigger_LPF_length.get()))
5242  TFiltCoef = numpy.array(TFiltCoef)
5243  TrgBuff = numpy.convolve(TrgBuff, TFiltCoef)
5244 
5245  if len(TrgBuff) == 0:
5246  return
5247  try:
5248  TrgMin = numpy.amin(TrgBuff)
5249  except:
5250  TrgMin = 0.0
5251  try:
5252  TrgMax = numpy.amax(TrgBuff)
5253  except:
5254  TrgMax = 0.0
5255 # Find trigger sample
5256  try:
5257  if AutoLevel.get() == 1:
5258  TRIGGERlevel = (TrgMin + TrgMax)/2
5259  TRIGGERentry.delete(0,"end")
5260  TRIGGERentry.insert(0, ' {0:.4f} '.format(TRIGGERlevel))
5261  else:
5262  TRIGGERlevel = eval(TRIGGERentry.get())
5263  except:
5264  TRIGGERentry.delete(0,END)
5265  TRIGGERentry.insert(0, TRIGGERlevel)
5266 # Start from first sample after HoldOff
5267  try:
5268  HoldOff = float(eval(HoldOffentry.get()))
5269  if HoldOff < 0:
5270  HoldOff = 0
5271  HoldOffentry.delete(0,END)
5272  HoldOffentry.insert(0, HoldOff)
5273  except:
5274  HoldOffentry.delete(0,END)
5275  HoldOffentry.insert(0, HoldOff)
5276 # slide trace left right by HozPoss
5277  try:
5278  HozPoss = float(eval(HozPossentry.get()))
5279  except:
5280  HozPossentry.delete(0,END)
5281  HozPossentry.insert(0, HozPoss)
5282 
5283  hldn = int(HoldOff * SAMPLErate/1000)
5284  hozpos = int(HozPoss * SAMPLErate/1000)
5285  if hozpos >= 0:
5286  TRIGGERsample = hldn
5287  else:
5288  TRIGGERsample = abs(hozpos)
5289 #
5290  Nmax = int(TRACEsize / 1.5) # first 2/3 of data set
5291  DX = 0
5292  n = TRIGGERsample
5293  TRIGGERlevel2 = 0.99 * TRIGGERlevel # Hysteresis to avoid triggering on noise
5294  if TRIGGERlevel2 < TrgMin:
5295  TRIGGERlevel2 = TrgMin
5296  if TRIGGERlevel2 > TrgMax:
5297  TRIGGERlevel2 = TrgMax
5298  ChInput = TrgBuff[int(n)]
5299  Prev = ChInput
5300  while ( ChInput >= TRIGGERlevel2) and n < Nmax:
5301  n = n + 1
5302  ChInput = TrgBuff[int(n)]
5303  while (ChInput <= TRIGGERlevel) and n < Nmax:
5304  Prev = ChInput
5305  n = n + 1
5306  ChInput = TrgBuff[int(n)]
5307  DY = ChInput - Prev
5308  if DY != 0.0:
5309  DX = (TRIGGERlevel - Prev)/DY # calculate interpolated trigger point
5310  else:
5311  DX = 0
5312  if TgEdge.get() == 1:
5313  TRIGGERlevel2 = 1.01 * TRIGGERlevel
5314  if TRIGGERlevel2 < TrgMin:
5315  TRIGGERlevel2 = TrgMin
5316  if TRIGGERlevel2 > TrgMax:
5317  TRIGGERlevel2 = TrgMax
5318  ChInput = TrgBuff[int(n)]
5319  Prev = ChInput
5320  while (ChInput <= TRIGGERlevel2) and n < Nmax:
5321  n = n + 1
5322  ChInput = TrgBuff[int(n)]
5323  while (ChInput >= TRIGGERlevel) and n < Nmax:
5324  Prev = ChInput
5325  n = n + 1
5326  ChInput = TrgBuff[int(n)]
5327  DY = Prev - ChInput
5328  try:
5329  DX = (Prev - TRIGGERlevel)/DY # calculate interpolated trigger point
5330  except:
5331  DX = 0
5332 
5333 # check to insure trigger point is in bounds
5334  if n < Nmax:
5335  TRIGGERsample = n - 1
5336  Is_Triggered = 1
5337  elif n > Nmax: # Didn't find edge in first 2/3 of data set
5338  TRIGGERsample = 1 + hldn # reset to begining
5339  Is_Triggered = 0
5340  if DX > 1:
5341  DX = 1 # never more than 100% of a sample period
5342  elif DX < 0:
5343  DX = 0 # never less than 0% of a sample period
5344  if math.isnan(DX):
5345  DX = 0
5346  TRIGGERsample = TRIGGERsample + hozpos
5347

5682 
5683  # Set the TRACEsize variable
5684  if len(VBuffA) < 100 and MuxScreenStatus.get() == 0:
5685  return
5686  TRACEsize = SHOWsamples # Set the trace length
5687  SCstart = 0
5688  ylo = 0.0
5689  xlo = 0.0
5690  Ymin = Y0T # Minimum position of time grid (top)
5691  Ymax = Y0T + GRH # Maximum position of time grid (bottom)
5692  Xmin = X0L # Minimum position of time grid (left)
5693  Xmax = X0L + GRW # Maximum position of time grid (right)
5694 
5695  # prevent divide by zero error
5696  if TIMEdiv < 0.0002:
5697  TIMEdiv = 0.01
5698  # Check for Auto Centering
5699  if AutoCenterA.get() > 0:
5700  CHAOffset = DCV1
5701  CHAVPosEntry.delete(0,END)
5702  CHAVPosEntry.insert(0, ' {0:.2f} '.format(CHAOffset))
5703  if AutoCenterB.get() > 0:
5704  CHBOffset = DCV2
5705  CHBVPosEntry.delete(0,END)
5706  CHBVPosEntry.insert(0, ' {0:.2f} '.format(CHBOffset))
5707  # get the vertical ranges
5708  try:
5709  CH1pdvRange = float(eval(CHAsb.get()))
5710  except:
5711  CHAsb.delete(0,END)
5712  CHAsb.insert(0, CH1pdvRange)
5713  try:
5714  CH2pdvRange = float(eval(CHBsb.get()))
5715  except:
5716  CHBsb.delete(0,END)
5717  CHBsb.insert(0, CH2pdvRange)
5718  try:

5720  except:

5722  CHAIsb.insert(0, CH1IpdvRange)
5723  try:

5725  except:
5726  CHBIsb.delete(0,END)
5727  CHBIsb.insert(0, CH2IpdvRange)
5728  # get the vertical offsets
5729  try:
5730  CHAOffset = float(eval(CHAVPosEntry.get()))
5731  except:
5732  CHAVPosEntry.delete(0,END)
5733  CHAVPosEntry.insert(0, CHAOffset)
5734  try:
5735  CHAIOffset = float(eval(CHAIPosEntry.get()))
5736  except:
5737  CHAIPosEntry.delete(0,END)
5738  CHAIPosEntry.insert(0, CHAIOffset)
5739  try:

5741  except:
5742  CHBVPosEntry.delete(0,END)
5743  CHBVPosEntry.insert(0, CHBOffset)
5744  try:

5746  except:
5747  CHBIPosEntry.delete(0,END)
5748  CHBIPosEntry.insert(0, CHBIOffset)
5749  # prevent divide by zero error
5750  if CH1pdvRange < 0.001:
5751  CH1pdvRange = 0.001
5752  if CH2pdvRange < 0.001:
5753  CH2pdvRange = 0.001
5754  if CH1IpdvRange < 0.1:
5755  CH1IpdvRange = 0.1
5756  if CH2IpdvRange < 0.1:
5757  CH2IpdvRange = 0.1

5759  try:

5761  if HoldOff < 0:
5762  HoldOff = 0
5763  HoldOffentry.delete(0,END)
5764  HoldOffentry.insert(0, HoldOff)
5765  except:
5766  HoldOffentry.delete(0,END)
5767  HoldOffentry.insert(0, HoldOff)
5768 #
5769  try:
5770  HozPoss = float(eval(HozPossentry.get()))
5771  except:
5772  HozPossentry.delete(0,END)
5773  HozPossentry.insert(0, HozPoss)
5774 #
5775  hldn = int(HoldOff * SAMPLErate/1000 )
5776  hozpos = int(HozPoss * SAMPLErate/1000 )
5777  if hozpos < 0:
5778  hozpos = 0
5779  # drawing the traces
5780  if TRACEsize == 0: # If no trace, skip rest of this routine
5781  T1Vline = [] # Trace line channel A V
5782  T2Vline = [] # Trace line channel B V
5783  T1Iline = []
5784  T2Iline = []
5785  TMAVline = [] # V Trace line Mux channel A
5786  TMBVline = [] # V Trace line Mux channel B
5787  TMCVline = [] # V Trace line Mux channel C
5788  TMDVline = [] # V Trace line Mux channel D
5789  Tmathline = [] # math trce line
5790  return()
5791 
5792  # set and/or corrected for in range
5793  if TgInput.get() > 0 or ChopTrig.get() > 0:
5794  SCmin = int(-1 * TRIGGERsample)
5795  SCmax = int(TRACEsize - TRIGGERsample - 0)
5796  else:
5797  SCmin = 0 # hldn
5798  SCmax = TRACEsize - 1
5799  if SCstart < SCmin: # No reading before start of array
5800  SCstart = SCmin
5801  if SCstart > SCmax: # No reading after end of array
5802  SCstart = SCmax
5803 
5804  # Make Trace lines etc.
5805 
5806  Yconv1 = float(GRH/10.0) / CH1pdvRange # Vertical Conversion factors from samples to screen points
5807  Yconv2 = float(GRH/10.0) / CH2pdvRange
5808  YIconv1 = float(GRH/10.0) / CH1IpdvRange
5809  YIconv2 = float(GRH/10.0) / CH2IpdvRange
5810  Xconv1 = float(GRW/10.0) / CH1pdvRange # Horizontal Conversion factors from samples to screen points
5811  Xconv2 = float(GRW/10.0) / CH2pdvRange
5812  XIconv1 = float(GRW/10.0) / CH1IpdvRange
5813  XIconv2 = float(GRW/10.0) / CH2IpdvRange
5814  if MuxScreenStatus.get() == 1: # if using analog Mux set up axis controls
5815  try:
5816  CHMApdvRange = float(eval(CHB_Asb.get()))
5817  except:
5818  CHB_Asb.delete(0,END)
5819  CHB_Asb.insert(0, CHMApdvRange)
5820  try:
5821  CHMBpdvRange = float(eval(CHB_Bsb.get()))
5822  except:

5824  CHB_Bsb.insert(0, CHMBpdvRange)

5827  except:

5832  except:

5838  YconvMD = float(GRH/10.0) / CHMDpdvRange
5839  try:
5840  CHBAOffset = float(eval(CHB_APosEntry.get()))
5841  except:
5842  CHB_APosEntry.delete(0,END)
5843  CHB_APosEntry.insert(0, CHBAOffset)
5844  try:
5845  CHBBOffset = float(eval(CHB_BPosEntry.get()))
5846  except:
5847  CHB_BPosEntry.delete(0,END)
5848  CHB_BPosEntry.insert(0, CHBBOffset)
5849  try:

5851  except:
5852  CHB_CPosEntry.delete(0,END)
5853  CHB_CPosEntry.insert(0, CHBCOffset)
5854  try:
5855  CHBDOffset = float(eval(CHB_DPosEntry.get()))
5856  except:
5857  CHB_DPosEntry.delete(0,END)
5858  CHB_DPosEntry.insert(0, CHBDOffset)
5859  if MathAxis == "V-A":
5860  YconvM = Yconv1
5861  CHMOffset = CHAOffset
5862  elif MathAxis == "V-B":
5863  YconvM = Yconv2
5864  CHMOffset = CHBOffset
5865  elif MathAxis == "I-A":
5866  YconvM = YIconv1
5867  CHMOffset = CHAIOffset
5868  elif MathAxis == "I-B":
5869  YconvM = YIconv2
5870  CHMOffset = CHBIOffset
5871  else:
5872  YconvM = Yconv1
5873  CHMOffset = CHAOffset
5874 # include ploting X and Y math formulas vs time
5875  if MathYAxis == "V-A":
5876  YconvMxy = Yconv1
5877  CHMYOffset = CHAOffset
5878  elif MathYAxis == "V-B":
5879  YconvMxy = Yconv2
5880  CHMYOffset = CHBOffset
5881  elif MathYAxis == "I-A":
5882  YconvMxy = YIconv1
5883  CHMYOffset = CHAIOffset
5884  elif MathYAxis == "I-B":
5885  YconvMxy = YIconv2
5886  CHMYOffset = CHBIOffset
5887  else:
5888  YconvMxy = Yconv1
5889  CHMYOffset = CHAOffset
5890 #
5891  if MathXAxis == "V-A":
5892  XconvMxy = Yconv1
5893  CHMXOffset = CHAOffset
5894  elif MathXAxis == "V-B":
5895  XconvMxy = Yconv2
5896  CHMXOffset = CHBOffset
5897  elif MathXAxis == "I-A":
5898  XconvMxy = YIconv1
5899  CHMXOffset = CHAIOffset
5900  elif MathXAxis == "I-B":
5901  XconvMxy = YIconv2
5902  CHMXOffset = CHBIOffset
5903  else:
5904  XconvMxy = Yconv1
5905  CHMXOffset = CHAOffset
5906 #
5907  c1 = GRH / 2.0 + Y0T # fixed correction channel A
5908  c2 = GRH / 2.0 + Y0T # fixed correction channel B
5909 
5910  DISsamples = SAMPLErate * 10.0 * TIMEdiv / 1000.0 # number of samples to display
5911  T1Vline = [] # V Trace line channel A
5912  T2Vline = [] # V Trace line channel B
5913  T1Iline = [] # I Trace line channel A
5914  T2Iline = [] # I Trace line channel B
5915  TMAVline = [] # V Trace line Mux channel A
5916  TMBVline = [] # V Trace line Mux channel B
5917  TMCVline = [] # V Trace line Mux channel C
5918  TMDVline = [] # V Trace line Mux channel D
5919  Tmathline = [] # math trce line
5920  TMXline = [] # X math Trace line
5921  TMYline = [] # Y math Trace line
5922  if len(VBuffA) < 4 and len(VBuffB) < 4 and len(IBuffA) < 4 and len(IBuffB) < 4:
5923  return
5924  t = int(SCstart + TRIGGERsample) # - (TriggerPos * SAMPLErate) # t = Start sample in trace
5925  if t < 0:
5926  t = 0
5927  x = 0 # Horizontal screen pixel
5928 #
5929  ypv1 = int(c1 - Yconv1 * (VBuffA[t] - CHAOffset))
5930  ypi1 = int(c1 - YIconv1 * (IBuffA[t] - CHAIOffset))
5931  ypv2 = int(c2 - Yconv2 * (VBuffB[t] - CHBOffset))
5932  ypi2 = int(c1 - YIconv2 * (IBuffB[t] - CHBIOffset))
5933  DvY1 = DvY2 = DiY1 = DiY2 = 0
5934 #
5935  if (DISsamples <= GRW):
5936  Xstep = GRW / DISsamples
5937  if AWGBMode.get() == 2 and Two_X_Sample.get() == 0:
5938  xa = int((Xstep/-2.5) - (Xstep*DX))
5939  else:
5940  xa = 0 - int(Xstep*DX) # adjust start pixel for interpolated trigger point
5941  x = 0 - int(Xstep*DX)
5942  Tstep = 1
5943  x1 = 0 # x position of trace line
5944  xa1 = 0
5945  y1 = 0.0 # y position of trace line
5946  ypv1 = int(c1 - Yconv1 * (VBuffA[t] - CHAOffset))
5947  ytemp = IBuffA[t]
5948  ypi1 = int(c1 - YIconv1 * (ytemp - CHAIOffset))
5949  ypv2 = int(c2 - Yconv2 * (VBuffB[t] - CHBOffset))
5950  if MuxScreenStatus.get() == 1:
5951  if len(VBuffMA) > 4:
5952  ypvma = int(c2 - YconvMA * (VBuffMA[t] - CHBAOffset))
5953  if len(VBuffMB) > 4:
5954  ypvmb = int(c2 - YconvMB * (VBuffMB[t] - CHBBOffset))
5955  if len(VBuffMC) > 4:
5956  ypvmc = int(c2 - YconvMC * (VBuffMC[t] - CHBCOffset))
5957  if len(VBuffMD) > 4:
5958  ypvmd = int(c2 - YconvMD * (VBuffMD[t] - CHBDOffset))
5959  ytemp = IBuffB[t]
5960  ypi2 = int(c1 - YIconv2 * (ytemp - CHBIOffset))
5961  ypm = ypmx = ypmy = GRH / 2.0 + Y0T
5962  if TgInput.get() == 0:
5963  Xlimit = GRW
5964  else:
5965  Xlimit = GRW+Xstep
5966  while x <= Xlimit:
5967  if t < TRACEsize:
5968  xa1 = xa + X0L
5969  x1 = x + X0L
5970  y1 = int(c1 - Yconv1 * (VBuffA[t] - CHAOffset))
5971  ytemp = IBuffA[t]
5972  yi1 = int(c1 - YIconv1 * (ytemp - CHAIOffset))
5973 
5974  if y1 < Ymin: # clip waveform if going off grid
5975  y1 = Ymin
5976  if y1 > Ymax:
5977  y1 = Ymax
5978  if yi1 < Ymin:
5979  yi1 = Ymin
5980  if yi1 > Ymax:
5981  yi1 = Ymax
5982  if ShowC1_V.get() == 1 :
5983  if ZOHold.get() == 1:
5984  T1Vline.append(int(xa1))
5985  T1Vline.append(int(ypv1))
5986  T1Vline.append(int(xa1))
5987  T1Vline.append(int(y1))
5988  else:
5989  T1Vline.append(int(xa1))
5990  T1Vline.append(int(y1))
5991  DvY1 = ypv1 - y1
5992  ypv1 = y1
5993  if ShowC1_I.get() == 1:
5994  if ZOHold.get() == 1:
5995  T1Iline.append(int(xa1))
5996  T1Iline.append(int(ypi1))
5997  T1Iline.append(int(xa1))
5998  T1Iline.append(int(yi1))
5999  else:
6000  T1Iline.append(int(xa1))
6001  T1Iline.append(int(yi1))
6002  DiY1 = ypi1 - yi1
6003  ypi1 = yi1
6004  if ShowC2_V.get() == 1:
6005  y1 = int(c2 - Yconv2 * (VBuffB[t] - CHBOffset))
6006  if y1 < Ymin: # clip waveform if going off grid
6007  y1 = Ymin
6008  if y1 > Ymax:
6009  y1 = Ymax
6010  if ZOHold.get() == 1:
6011  T2Vline.append(int(x1))
6012  T2Vline.append(int(ypv2))
6013  T2Vline.append(int(x1))
6014  T2Vline.append(int(y1))
6015  else:
6016  T2Vline.append(int(x1))
6017  T2Vline.append(int(y1))
6018  DvY2 = ypv2 - y1
6019  ypv2 = y1
6020  if Show_CBA.get() == 1 and MuxScreenStatus.get() == 1 and len(VBuffMA)>4:
6021  y1 = int(c2 - YconvMA * (VBuffMA[t] - CHBAOffset))
6022  if y1 < Ymin: # clip waveform if going off grid
6023  y1 = Ymin
6024  if y1 > Ymax:
6025  y1 = Ymax
6026  if ZOHold.get() == 1:
6027  TMAVline.append(int(x1))
6028  TMAVline.append(int(ypvma))
6029  TMAVline.append(int(x1))
6030  TMAVline.append(int(y1))
6031  else:
6032  TMAVline.append(int(x1))
6033  TMAVline.append(int(y1))
6034  ypvma = y1
6035  if (MouseX - X0L) >= x and (MouseX - X0L) < (x + Xstep):
6036  Xfine = MouseX - X0L - x
6037  MouseMuxA = ypvma - (y1 - ypvma) * (Xfine/Xstep)
6038  if Show_CBB.get() == 1 and MuxScreenStatus.get() == 1 and len(VBuffMB)>4:
6039  y1 = int(c2 - YconvMB * (VBuffMB[t] - CHBBOffset))
6040  if y1 < Ymin: # clip waveform if going off grid
6041  y1 = Ymin
6042  if y1 > Ymax:
6043  y1 = Ymax
6044  if ZOHold.get() == 1:
6045  TMBVline.append(int(x1))
6046  TMBVline.append(int(ypvmb))
6047  TMBVline.append(int(x1))
6048  TMBVline.append(int(y1))
6049  else:
6050  TMBVline.append(int(x1))
6051  TMBVline.append(int(y1))
6052  ypvmb = y1
6053  if (MouseX - X0L) >= x and (MouseX - X0L) < (x + Xstep):
6054  Xfine = MouseX - X0L - x
6055  MouseMuxB = ypvmb - (y1 - ypvmb) * (Xfine/Xstep)
6056  if Show_CBC.get() == 1 and MuxScreenStatus.get() == 1 and len(VBuffMC)>4:
6057  y1 = int(c2 - YconvMC * (VBuffMC[t] - CHBCOffset))
6058  if y1 < Ymin: # clip waveform if going off grid
6059  y1 = Ymin
6060  if y1 > Ymax:
6061  y1 = Ymax
6062  if ZOHold.get() == 1:
6063  TMCVline.append(int(x1))
6064  TMCVline.append(int(ypvmc))
6065  TMCVline.append(int(x1))
6066  TMCVline.append(int(y1))
6067  else:
6068  TMCVline.append(int(x1))
6069  TMCVline.append(int(y1))
6070  ypvmc = y1
6071  if (MouseX - X0L) >= x and (MouseX - X0L) < (x + Xstep):
6072  Xfine = MouseX - X0L - x
6073  MouseMuxC = ypvmc - (y1 - ypvmc) * (Xfine/Xstep)
6074  if Show_CBD.get() == 1 and MuxScreenStatus.get() == 1 and len(VBuffMD)>4:
6075  y1 = int(c2 - YconvMD * (VBuffMD[t] - CHBDOffset))
6076  if y1 < Ymin: # clip waveform if going off grid
6077  y1 = Ymin
6078  if y1 > Ymax:
6079  y1 = Ymax
6080  if ZOHold.get() == 1:
6081  TMDVline.append(int(x1))
6082  TMDVline.append(int(ypvmd))
6083  TMDVline.append(int(x1))
6084  TMDVline.append(int(y1))
6085  else:
6086  TMDVline.append(int(x1))
6087  TMDVline.append(int(y1))
6088  ypvmd = y1
6089  if (MouseX - X0L) >= x and (MouseX - X0L) < (x + Xstep):
6090  Xfine = MouseX - X0L - x
6091  MouseMuxD = ypvmd - (y1 - ypvmd) * (Xfine/Xstep)
6092  if ShowC2_I.get() == 1:
6093  ytemp = IBuffB[t]
6094  yi1 = int(c1 - YIconv2 * (ytemp - CHBIOffset))
6095  if yi1 < Ymin:
6096  yi1 = Ymin
6097  if yi1 > Ymax:
6098  yi1 = Ymax
6099  if (ZOHold.get() == 1):
6100  T2Iline.append(int(x1))
6101  T2Iline.append(int(ypi2))
6102  T2Iline.append(int(x1))
6103  T2Iline.append(int(yi1))
6104  else:
6105  T2Iline.append(int(x1))
6106  T2Iline.append(int(yi1))
6107  DiY2 = ypi2 - yi1
6108  ypi2 = yi1
6109  if MathTrace.get() > 0:
6110  if MathTrace.get() == 1: # plot sum of CA-V and CB-V
6111  y1 = int(c1 - Yconv1 * (VBuffA[t] + VBuffB[t] - CHAOffset))
6112 
6113  elif MathTrace.get() == 2: # plot difference of CA-V and CB-V
6114  y1 = int(c1 - Yconv1 * (VBuffA[t] - VBuffB[t] - CHAOffset))
6115 
6116  elif MathTrace.get() == 3: # plot difference of CB-V and CA-V
6117  y1 = int(c2 - Yconv2 * (VBuffB[t] - VBuffA[t] - CHBOffset))
6118 
6119  elif MathTrace.get() == 4: # plot product of CA-V and CA-I
6120  Ypower = VBuffA[t] * IBuffA[t] # mAmps * Volts = mWatts
6121  ytemp = YIconv1 * (Ypower - CHAIOffset)
6122  y1 = int(c1 - ytemp)
6123 
6124  elif MathTrace.get() == 5: # plot product of CB-V and CB-I
6125  Ypower = VBuffB[t] * IBuffB[t] # mAmps * Volts = mWatts
6126  ytemp = YIconv2 * (Ypower - CHBIOffset)
6127  y1 = int(c2 - ytemp)
6128 
6129  elif MathTrace.get() == 6: # plot ratio of CA-V and CA-I
6130  Yohms = VBuffA[t] / (IBuffA[t] / 1000.0) # Volts / Amps = ohms
6131  ytemp = YIconv1 * (Yohms - CHAIOffset)

6667  if (y1 < Ymin):
6668  y1 = Ymin
6669  if (y1 > Ymax):
6670  y1 = Ymax
6671  Triggerline.append(int(x1-5))
6672  Triggerline.append(int(y1+5))
6673  Triggerline.append(int(x1+5))
6674  Triggerline.append(int(y1))
6675  Triggerline.append(int(x1-5))
6676  Triggerline.append(int(y1-5))
6677  Triggerline.append(int(x1-5))
6678  Triggerline.append(int(y1+5))
6679  x1 = X0L + (GRW/2)
6680  if TgEdge.get() == 0: # draw rising edge symbol
6681  y1 = -3
6682  y2 = -13
6683  else:
6684  y1 = -13
6685  y2 = -3
6686  Triggersymbol.append(int(x1-10))
6687  Triggersymbol.append(int(Ymin+y1))
6688  Triggersymbol.append(int(x1))
6689  Triggersymbol.append(int(Ymin+y1))
6690  Triggersymbol.append(int(x1))
6691  Triggersymbol.append(int(Ymin+y2))
6692  Triggersymbol.append(int(x1+10))
6693  Triggersymbol.append(int(Ymin+y2))

6695 def MakeXYTrace():

6771  # prevent divide by zero error
6772  if CH1pdvRange < 0.001:
6773  CH1pdvRange = 0.001
6774  if CH2pdvRange < 0.001:
6775  CH2pdvRange = 0.001
6776  if CH1IpdvRange < 0.1:

6778  if CH2IpdvRange < 0.1:
6779  CH2IpdvRange = 0.1

6782  Yconv2 = float(GRHXY/10.0) / CH2pdvRange
6783  YIconv1 = float(GRHXY/10.0) / CH1IpdvRange
6784  YIconv2 = float(GRHXY/10.0) / CH2IpdvRange
6785  Xconv1 = float(GRWXY/10.0) / CH1pdvRange # Horizontal Conversion factors from samples to screen points
6786  Xconv2 = float(GRWXY/10.0) / CH2pdvRange
6787  XIconv1 = float(GRWXY/10.0) / CH1IpdvRange
6788  XIconv2 = float(GRWXY/10.0) / CH2IpdvRange
6789 
6790  if MathYAxis == "V-A":

6792  CHMYOffset = CHAOffset

6796  elif MathYAxis == "I-A":

6798  CHMYOffset = CHAIOffset
6799  elif MathYAxis == "I-B":
6800  YconvMxy = YIconv2
6801  CHMYOffset = CHBIOffset

6804  CHMYOffset = CHAOffset

6808  elif MathXAxis == "V-B":

6811  elif MathYAxis == "I-A":

6813  CHMXOffset = CHAIOffset
6814  elif MathXAxis == "I-B":

6816  CHMXOffset = CHBIOffset
6817  else:

6819  CHMXOffset = CHAOffset
6820  # draw an X/Y plot

6833  xlo = VBuffA[t] - CHAOffset

6837  if ( MathTrace.get() == 2): # plot difference of CA-V and CB-V
6838  ylo = VBuffB[t] - CHBOffset
6839  ylo = int(c1 - Yconv2 * ylo)

6841  xlo = int(c2 + Xconv1 * xlo)
6842  elif (Xsignal.get() == 5 and Ysignal.get() == 4): # mode CBI/Math
6843  if ( MathTrace.get() == 2): # plot difference of CA-V and CB-V
6844  ylo = (IBuffB[t]) - CHBIOffset
6845  ylo = int(c1 - YIconv2 * ylo)
6846  xlo = VBuffA[t] - VBuffB[t] - CHAOffset
6847  xlo = int(c2 + Xconv1 * xlo)
6848  elif (Xsignal.get() == 5 and Ysignal.get() == 2): # mode CAI/Math
6849  if MathTrace.get() == 3: # plot difference of CB-V and CA-V
6850  ylo = (IBuffA[t]) - CHAIOffset
6851  ylo = int(c1 - YIconv1 * ylo)
6852  xlo = VBuffB[t] - VBuffA[t] - CHBOffset
6853  xlo = int(c2 + Xconv2 * xlo)
6854  elif (Xsignal.get() == 3 and Ysignal.get() == 5): # mode Math/CBV
6855  if MathTrace.get() == 2: # plot difference of CA-V and CB-V
6856  ylo = VBuffA[t] - VBuffB[t] - CHAOffset
6857  ylo = int(c1 - Yconv1 * ylo)
6858  xlo = VBuffB[t] - CHBOffset
6859  xlo = int(c2 + Xconv2 * xlo)
6860  elif (Xsignal.get() == 5 and Ysignal.get() == 1): # mode CAV/Math

6936  if xlo > XmaxXY:

6939  TXYline.append(int(ylo))
6940  t = int(t + 1)

8592 def onCanvasClickScroll(event):
8593  global ShowTCur, ShowVCur, TCursor, VCursor, RUNstatus, ca, MWcount
8594  global MeasGateStatus, MeasGateLeft, MeasGateRight, TIMEdiv, GRW
8595 
8596  ShiftKeyDwn = event.state & 1
8597  if event.widget == ca:
8598  if ShowTCur.get() > 0 or ShowVCur.get() > 0: # move cursors if shown
8599  if ShowTCur.get() > 0 and ShiftKeyDwn == 0:
8600  # respond to Linux or Windows wheel event
8601  if event.num == 5 or event.delta == -120:
8602  TCursor -= 1
8603  if event.num == 4 or event.delta == 120:
8604  TCursor += 1
8605  elif ShowVCur.get() > 0 or ShiftKeyDwn == 1:
8606  # respond to Linux or Windows wheel event
8607  if event.num == 5 or event.delta == -120:
8608  VCursor += 1
8609  if event.num == 4 or event.delta == 120:
8610  VCursor -= 1
8611 
8615  else:
8616  if MeasGateStatus.get() == 1:
8617  Tstep = (TIMEdiv / GRW) / 10 # time in mS per pixel
8618  if ShiftKeyDwn == 0:
8619  if event.num == 5 or event.delta == -120:
8620  MeasGateLeft = MeasGateLeft + (-100 * Tstep)
8621  if event.num == 4 or event.delta == 120:
8622  MeasGateLeft = MeasGateLeft + (100 * Tstep)
8623  # MeasGateLeft = MeasGateLeft + (event.delta * Tstep) #+ HoldOff
8624  if ShiftKeyDwn == 1:
8625  if event.num == 5 or event.delta == -120:
8626  MeasGateRight = MeasGateRight + (-100 * Tstep)
8627  if event.num == 4 or event.delta == 120:
8628  MeasGateRight = MeasGateRight + (100 * Tstep)
8629  #MeasGateRight = MeasGateRight + (event.delta * Tstep) #+ HoldOff
8630  try:
8631  onSpinBoxScroll(event) # if cursor are not showing scroll the Horx time base
8632  except:
8633  donothing()
8634  if RUNstatus.get() == 0:
8635  UpdateTimeScreen()
8636 
8637 def onCanvasUpArrow(event):

8641  if event.widget == ca:

8645  VCursor = VCursor - 5

8653  YCursor = YCursor - 5
8654  if RUNstatus.get() == 0:
8655  UpdateXYScreen()
8656  except:
8657  donothing()

9379  V_label = V_label + VxString + " V, " + VyString + " mA"
9380  if MarkerNum > 1:
9381  DeltaY = ' {0:.2f} '.format(PrevY-ymA)
9382  DeltaX = ' {0:.3f} '.format(PrevX-xvolts)
9383  DeltaR = ' {0:.3f} '.format(((PrevX-xvolts)/(PrevY-ymA))*1000)
9384  V_label = V_label + " Delta " + DeltaX + " V, " + DeltaY + " mA"
9385  V_label = V_label + ", dV/dI " + DeltaR
9386  PrevY = ymA
9387  elif (Xsignal.get()==3 or Xsignal.get()==5) and (Ysignal.get()==2 or Ysignal.get()==5):
9388  xvolts = ((xc1-event.x)/Xconv2) - CHBOffset
9389  ymA = ((event.y-c2)/YIconv1) - CHAIOffset
9390  VxString = ' {0:.3f} '.format(-xvolts)
9391  VyString = ' {0:.1f} '.format(-ymA)
9392  V_label = V_label + VxString + " V, " + VyString + " mA"
9393  if MarkerNum > 1:
9394  DeltaY = ' {0:.2f} '.format(PrevY-ymA)
9395  DeltaX = ' {0:.3f} '.format(PrevX-xvolts)
9396  DeltaR = ' {0:.3f} '.format(((PrevX-xvolts)/(PrevY-ymA))*1000)
9397  V_label = V_label + " Delta " + DeltaX + " V, " + DeltaY + " mA"
9398  V_label = V_label + ", dV/dI " + DeltaR
9399  PrevY = ymA
9400  elif (Xsignal.get()==1 or Xsignal.get()==5) and (Ysignal.get()==4 or Ysignal.get()==5):
9401  xvolts = ((xc1-event.x)/Xconv1) - CHAOffset
9402  ymA = ((event.y-c2)/YIconv2) - CHBIOffset
9403  VxString = ' {0:.3f} '.format(-xvolts)
9404  VyString = ' {0:.1f} '.format(-ymA)
9405  V_label = V_label + VxString + " V, " + VyString + " mA"
9406  if MarkerNum > 1:
9407  DeltaY = ' {0:.2f} '.format(PrevY-ymA)
9408  DeltaX = ' {0:.3f} '.format(PrevX-xvolts)
9409  DeltaR = ' {0:.3f} '.format(((PrevX-xvolts)/(PrevY-ymA))*1000)
9410  V_label = V_label + " Delta " + DeltaX + " V, " + DeltaY + " mA"
9411  V_label = V_label + ", dV/dI " + DeltaR
9412  PrevY = ymA
9413  XYca.create_text(x, y, text=V_label, fill=COLORtext, anchor="w", font=("arial", FontSize ))
9414  PrevX = xvolts
9415 #
9416 def SchroederPhase(Length, NrTones, Ampl):
9417  # Generate a Schroeder Phase (Chirp) of Length samples and having NrTones
9418  OutArray = []
9419  OutArray = Ampl*numpy.cos(numpy.linspace(0, 2*numpy.pi, Length)) # the fundamental
9420  k = 2
9421  while k <= NrTones:
9422  # Add all harmonics up to NrTones
9423  Harmonic = Ampl*numpy.cos(numpy.linspace(0, k*2*numpy.pi, Length)+(numpy.pi*k*k/NrTones))
9424  OutArray = OutArray + Harmonic
9425  k = k + 1
9426  OutArray = OutArray + 2.5 # Center wavefrom on 2.5 V
9427  return(OutArray)
9428 #
9429 def Wrap(InArray, WrFactor):
9430  # Build new array by skipping WrFactor samples and wrapping back around
9431  # [1,2,3,4,5,6} becomes [1,3,5,2,4,6]
9432  # effectively multiplies the frequency content by WrFactor
9433  OutArray = []
9434  OutArray = numpy.array(OutArray)
9435  InArray = numpy.array(InArray)
9436  EndIndex = len(InArray)
9437  StartIndex = 0
9438  while StartIndex < WrFactor:
9439  OutArray = numpy.concatenate((OutArray, InArray[StartIndex:EndIndex:WrFactor]), axis=0)
9440  StartIndex = StartIndex + 1
9441  return OutArray
9442 #
9443 def UnWrap(InArray, WrFactor):
9444  # Build new array by splitting arrray into WrFactor sections and interleaving samples from each section
9445  # [1,2,3,4,5,6} becomes [1,4,2,5,3,6]
9446  # effectively divided the frequency content by WrFactor
9447  OutArray = []
9448  InArray = numpy.array(InArray)
9449  EndIndex = int(len(InArray)/WrFactor)
9450  StartIndex = 0
9451  while StartIndex < EndIndex:
9452  LoopIndex = 0
9453  while LoopIndex < WrFactor:
9454  OutArray.append(InArray[StartIndex+LoopIndex])
9455  LoopIndex = LoopIndex + 1
9456  StartIndex = StartIndex + 1
9457  OutArray = numpy.array(OutArray)
9458  return OutArray
9459 #
9460 def Write_WAV(data, repeat, filename):
9461  global SAMPLErate
9462  # write data array to mono .wav file 100KSPS
9463  # copy buffer repeat times in output file
9464  # Use : Write_WAV(VBuffB, 2, "write_wave_1.wav")
9465  wavfile = wave.open(filename, "w")
9466  nchannels = 1
9467  sampwidth = 2
9468  framerate = SAMPLErate
9469  amplitude = 32766
9470  nframes = len(data)
9471  comptype = "NONE"
9472  compname = "not compressed"
9473  wavfile.setparams((nchannels,
9474  sampwidth,
9475  framerate,
9476  nframes,
9477  comptype,
9478  compname))
9479  # Normalize data
9480  ArrN = numpy.array(data)
9481  ArrN /= numpy.max(numpy.abs(data))
9482  frames = []
9483  for s in ArrN:
9484  mul = int(s * amplitude)
9485  # print "s: %f mul: %d" % (s, mul)
9486  frames.append(struct.pack('h', mul))
9487  print( len(frames))
9488  frames = ''.join(frames)
9489  print( len(frames))
9490  for x in xrange(0, repeat):
9491  print( x )
9492  wavfile.writeframes(frames)
9493  wavfile.close()

9520  AWGAAmplEntry.delete(0,"end")

9523  AWGAAmplvalue = -2.50 / AWGA_Ext_Gain.get()
9524  AWGAAmplEntry.delete(0,"end")

9774 def AWGALoadWAV():
9775  global AWGAwaveform, AWGALength, AWGAShape, awgwindow, AWGBwaveform, AWGBLength, AWGBShape
9776  global AWG_2X, AWGA2X, AWGAwavFile
9777 
9778  try:
9779  spf = wave.open(AWGAwavFile,'r')
9780  except:
9781  showwarning("WARNING","No such file found or wrong format!", parent=awgwindow)
9782  AWGAwaveform = []
9783  AWGBwaveform = []
9784  Length = spf.getnframes()
9785  if Length > 90000:
9786  Length = 90000
9787  # If Stereo put first channel in AWGA and second channel in AWGB
9788  if spf.getnchannels() == 2:
9789  showwarning("Split Stereo","Left to AWGA Right to AWGB", parent=awgwindow)
9790  signal = spf.readframes(Length)
9791  Stereo = numpy.fromstring(signal, 'Int16') # convert strings to Int
9792  n = 0
9793  while n < Length*2:
9794  AWGAwaveform.append((Stereo[n] * 2.5 / 32768) + 2.5)
9795  n = n + 1
9796  AWGBwaveform.append((Stereo[n] * 2.5 / 32768) + 2.5)
9797  n = n + 1
9798  AWGAwaveform = numpy.array(AWGAwaveform)
9799  AWGBwaveform = numpy.array(AWGBwaveform)
9800  AWGBShape.set(AWGAShape.get())
9801  else:
9802  #Extract Raw Audio from Wav File
9803  signal = spf.readframes(Length)
9804  WAVsignal = numpy.fromstring(signal, 'Int16') # convert strings to Int
9805  # offset and scale for 0 5 V range
9806  AWGAwaveform = (WAVsignal * 2.5 / 32768) + 2.5
9807  AWGAwaveform = numpy.array(AWGAwaveform)
9808  SplitAWGAwaveform()
9809  spf.close()
9810  UpdateAwgCont()

9866  if AWGAFreqvalue > 0.0:
9867  if AWG_2X.get() == 1:
9868  AWGAperiodvalue = (BaseSampleRate*2)/AWGAFreqvalue
9869  else:
9870  AWGAperiodvalue = BaseSampleRate/AWGAFreqvalue
9871  else:
9872  AWGAperiodvalue = 10.0
9873 
9874  if AWGAPhaseDelay.get() == 0:
9875  if AWGAPhasevalue > 0:
9876  AWGAdelayvalue = AWGAperiodvalue * AWGAPhasevalue / 360.0
9877  else:
9878  AWGAdelayvalue = 0.0
9879  elif AWGAPhaseDelay.get() == 1:
9880  AWGAdelayvalue = AWGAPhasevalue * SAMPLErate / 1000
9881  Cycles = int(AWGRecLength/AWGAperiodvalue)
9882  if Cycles < 1:
9883  Cycles = 1
9884  RecLength = int(Cycles * AWGAperiodvalue)
9885  if RecLength % 2 != 0: # make sure record length is even so 2X mode works for all Freq
9886  RecLength = RecLength + 1
9887  AWGAwaveform = []
9888  AWGAwaveform = numpy.cos(numpy.linspace(0, 2*Cycles*numpy.pi, RecLength))
9889 
9890  if AWG_Amp_Mode.get() == 0:
9891  if AWGAMode.get() == 1: # convert to mA
9892  amplitude = (AWGAOffsetvalue-AWGAAmplvalue) / -2000.0
9893  offset = (AWGAOffsetvalue+AWGAAmplvalue) / 2000.0
9894  else:
9895  amplitude = (AWGAOffsetvalue-AWGAAmplvalue) / -2.0
9896  offset = (AWGAOffsetvalue+AWGAAmplvalue) / 2.0
9897  else:
9898  if AWGAMode.get() == 1: # convert to mA
9899  amplitude = AWGAAmplvalue/1000.0
9900  offset = AWGAOffsetvalue/1000.0
9901  else:
9902  amplitude = AWGAAmplvalue*AWGA_Ext_Gain.get()
9903  offset = (AWGAOffsetvalue * AWGA_Ext_Gain.get()) + AWGA_Ext_Offset.get()
9904  AWGAwaveform = (AWGAwaveform * amplitude) + offset # scale and offset the waveform
9905  AWGAwaveform = numpy.roll(AWGAwaveform, int(AWGAdelayvalue))
9906 #
9907  SplitAWGAwaveform()
9908  BAWGAPhaseDelay()
9909  duty1lab.config(text="%")
9910  UpdateAwgCont()

9912 def AWGAMakeFMSine():
9913  global AWGAwaveform, AWGSAMPLErate, AWGAAmplvalue, AWGAOffsetvalue, AWGALength, AWGAperiodvalue
9914  global AWGADutyCyclevalue, AWGAFreqvalue, duty1lab, AWGAgain, AWGAoffset, AWGAPhaseDelay, AWGAMode
9915  global AWGA2X, AWG_2X, SAMPLErate, BaseSampleRate, phasealab, AWG_Amp_Mode
9916  global AWGA_Ext_Gain, AWGA_Ext_Offset, AWGB_Ext_Gain, AWGB_Ext_Offset, AWGRecLength
9917 
9918  BAWGAAmpl(0)
9919  BAWGAOffset(0)
9920  BAWGAFreq(0)
9921 # uses dyty cycle entry for Modulation index and phase entry for Modulation frequency
9922  duty1lab.config(text = "M Index")
9923  phasealab.config(text = "M Freq")
9924 
9925  if AWGAFreqvalue > 0.0:
9926  if AWG_2X.get() == 1:
9927  AWGAperiodvalue = (BaseSampleRate*2)/AWGAFreqvalue
9928  else:
9929  AWGAperiodvalue = BaseSampleRate/AWGAFreqvalue
9930  else:
9931  AWGAperiodvalue = 10.0
9932 
9933  try:
9934  ModFreq = float(eval(AWGAPhaseEntry.get()))
9935  except:
9936  ModFreq = 10
9937  AWGAPhaseEntry.delete(0,"end")
9938  AWGAPhaseEntry.insert(0, ModFreq)
9939 
9940  if ModFreq < 10:
9941  ModFreq = 10
9942  AWGAPhaseEntry.delete(0,"end")
9943  AWGAPhaseEntry.insert(0, ModFreq)
9944 
9945  if AWG_2X.get() == 1:
9946  MODperiodvalue = (BaseSampleRate*2)/ModFreq
9947  else:
9948  MODperiodvalue = BaseSampleRate/ModFreq
9949

9951  ModIndex = float(eval(AWGADutyCycleEntry.get()))
9952  except:
9953  ModIndex = 1.0
9954  AWGADutyCycleEntry.delete(0,"end")
9955  AWGADutyCycleEntry.insert(0, ModIndex)
9956 
9957  ModCycles = int(AWGRecLength/MODperiodvalue) # find a whole number of cycles
9958  if ModCycles < 1:
9959  ModCycles = 1
9960  RecLength = int(ModCycles * MODperiodvalue)
9961  if RecLength % 2 != 0: # make sure record length is even so 2X mode works for all Freq
9962  RecLength = RecLength + 1
9963  CarCycles = int(RecLength/AWGAperiodvalue) # insure a whole number of carrier cycles in record
9964  AWGAwaveform = []
9965  AWGAwaveform = numpy.sin( (numpy.linspace(0, CarCycles*2*numpy.pi, RecLength)) - ModIndex*numpy.cos(numpy.linspace(0, ModCycles*2*numpy.pi, RecLength)) )
9966  if AWG_Amp_Mode.get() == 0:
9967  if AWGAMode.get() == 1: # convert to mA
9968  amplitude = (AWGAOffsetvalue-AWGAAmplvalue) / -2000.0
9969  offset = (AWGAOffsetvalue+AWGAAmplvalue) / 2000.0
9970  else:
9971  amplitude = (AWGAOffsetvalue-AWGAAmplvalue) / -2.0
9972  offset = (AWGAOffsetvalue+AWGAAmplvalue) / 2.0
9973  else:
9974  if AWGAMode.get() == 1: # convert to mA
9975  amplitude = AWGAAmplvalue/1000.0
9976  offset = AWGAOffsetvalue/1000.0
9977  else:
9978  amplitude = AWGAAmplvalue*AWGA_Ext_Gain.get()
9979  offset = (AWGAOffsetvalue * AWGA_Ext_Gain.get()) + AWGA_Ext_Offset.get()
9980  AWGAwaveform = (AWGAwaveform * amplitude) + offset # scale and offset the waveform
9981  AWGAwaveform = numpy.roll(AWGAwaveform, int(AWGAdelayvalue))
9982 #
9983  SplitAWGAwaveform() # if needed
9984  UpdateAwgCont()

9986 def AWGAMakeAMSine():
9987  global AWGAwaveform, AWGSAMPLErate, AWGAAmplvalue, AWGAOffsetvalue, AWGALength, AWGAperiodvalue
9988  global AWGADutyCyclevalue, AWGAFreqvalue, duty1lab, AWGAgain, AWGAoffset, AWGAPhaseDelay, AWGAMode
9989  global AWGA2X, AWG_2X, SAMPLErate, BaseSampleRate, phasealab, AWG_Amp_Mode
9990  global AWGA_Ext_Gain, AWGA_Ext_Offset, AWGB_Ext_Gain, AWGB_Ext_Offset, AWGRecLength
9991 
9992  BAWGAAmpl(0)
9993  BAWGAOffset(0)
9994  BAWGAFreq(0)
9995 # uses dyty cycle entry for Modulation index and phase entry for Modulation frequency
9996  duty1lab.config(text = "M Index")
9997  phasealab.config(text = "M Freq")
9998 
9999  if AWGAFreqvalue > 0.0:
10000  if AWG_2X.get() == 1:
10001  AWGAperiodvalue = (BaseSampleRate*2)/AWGAFreqvalue
10002  else:
10003  AWGAperiodvalue = BaseSampleRate/AWGAFreqvalue

10007  try:

10009  except:

10013

10018 
10019  if AWG_2X.get() == 1:

10026  except:
10027  ModIndex = 50.0

10038  AWGAwaveform = []
10039  AWGAwaveform = numpy.sin(numpy.linspace(0, CarCycles*2*numpy.pi, RecLength)) * (0.5+(ModIndex*(numpy.cos(numpy.linspace(0, ModCycles*2*numpy.pi, RecLength)))))
10040  if AWG_Amp_Mode.get() == 0:
10041  if AWGAMode.get() == 1: # convert to mA
10042  amplitude = (AWGAOffsetvalue-AWGAAmplvalue) / -2000.0
10043  offset = (AWGAOffsetvalue+AWGAAmplvalue) / 2000.0
10044  else:

10047  else:

10050  offset = AWGAOffsetvalue/1000.0
10051  else:
10052  amplitude = AWGAAmplvalue*AWGA_Ext_Gain.get()
10053  offset = (AWGAOffsetvalue * AWGA_Ext_Gain.get()) + AWGA_Ext_Offset.get()
10054  AWGAwaveform = (AWGAwaveform * amplitude) + offset # scale and offset the waveform
10055  AWGAwaveform = numpy.roll(AWGAwaveform, int(AWGAdelayvalue))

10060 def AWGAMakePWMSine():
10061  global AWGAwaveform, AWGSAMPLErate, AWGAAmplvalue, AWGAOffsetvalue, AWGALength
10062  global AWGADutyCyclevalue, AWGAFreqvalue, duty1lab, AWG_Amp_Mode # 0 = Min/Max mode, 1 = Amp/Offset
10063  global AWGA2X, AWG_2X, SAMPLErate, BaseSampleRate
10064  global AWGA_Ext_Gain, AWGA_Ext_Offset, AWGB_Ext_Gain, AWGB_Ext_Offset
10065 
10066  BAWGAAmpl(0)
10067  BAWGAOffset(0)
10068  BAWGAFreq(0)
10069  BAWGAPhase(0)
10070  BAWGADutyCycle(0)
10071 
10072  if AWGAFreqvalue > 0.0:
10073  if AWG_2X.get() == 1:
10074  AWGAperiodvalue = int((BaseSampleRate*2)/AWGAFreqvalue)
10075  else:
10076  AWGAperiodvalue = BaseSampleRate/AWGAFreqvalue
10077  else:
10078  AWGAperiodvalue = 0.0
10079  if AWG_Amp_Mode.get() == 1:
10080  MaxV = (AWGAOffsetvalue * AWGA_Ext_Gain.get()) + AWGA_Ext_Offset.get() + (AWGAAmplvalue * AWGA_Ext_Gain.get())
10081  MinV = (AWGAOffsetvalue * AWGA_Ext_Gain.get()) + AWGA_Ext_Offset.get() - (AWGAAmplvalue * AWGA_Ext_Gain.get())
10082  else:
10083  MaxV = AWGAOffsetvalue
10084  MinV = AWGAAmplvalue
10085 
10086  PulseWidth = int(AWGADutyCyclevalue*100)
10087  PulseSamples = int(AWGAperiodvalue/PulseWidth)
10088  AWGAwaveform = []
10089  for i in range(PulseSamples): #(i = 0; i < cPulse; i++)
10090  v = round(PulseWidth/2*(1+numpy.sin(i*2*numpy.pi/PulseSamples)))
10091  # print(v)
10092  for j in range(PulseWidth): #(j = 0; j < cLength; j++)
10093  if j >= v:
10094  AWGAwaveform.append(MaxV) # j>=v?1:0
10095  else:
10096  AWGAwaveform.append(MinV) # j>=v?1:0
10097  SplitAWGAwaveform()
10098  duty1lab.config(text="PWidth")
10099  UpdateAwgCont()

10101 def AWGAMakeFourier():
10102  global AWGAwaveform, AWGSAMPLErate, AWGAAmplvalue, AWGAOffsetvalue, AWGALength
10103  global AWGADutyCyclevalue, AWGAFreqvalue, duty1lab, AWG_Amp_Mode # 0 = Min/Max mode, 1 = Amp/Offset
10104  global AWGA2X, AWG_2X, SAMPLErate, BaseSampleRate
10105  global AWGA_Ext_Gain, AWGA_Ext_Offset, AWGB_Ext_Gain, AWGB_Ext_Offset
10106 
10107  BAWGAAmpl(0)
10108  BAWGAOffset(0)
10109  BAWGAFreq(0)
10110  BAWGADutyCycle(0)
10111 
10112  Max_term = int(AWGADutyCyclevalue*100)
10113  if AWG_2X.get() == 1:
10114  TempRate = (BaseSampleRate*2)
10115  else:
10116  TempRate = BaseSampleRate
10117  AWGAwaveform = []
10118  AWGAwaveform = numpy.cos(numpy.linspace(0, 2*numpy.pi, TempRate/AWGAFreqvalue)) # the fundamental
10119  k = 3
10120  while k <= Max_term:
10121  # Add odd harmonics up to max_term
10122  Harmonic = (math.sin(k*numpy.pi/2.0)/k)*(numpy.cos(numpy.linspace(0, k*2*numpy.pi, TempRate/AWGAFreqvalue)))
10123  AWGAwaveform = AWGAwaveform + Harmonic
10124  k = k + 2 # skip even numbers
10125  if AWG_Amp_Mode.get() == 0:
10126  amplitude = (AWGAOffsetvalue-AWGAAmplvalue)/2.0
10127  offset = (AWGAOffsetvalue+AWGAAmplvalue)/2.0
10128  else:
10129  amplitude = AWGAAmplvalue*AWGA_Ext_Gain.get()
10130  offset = (AWGAOffsetvalue * AWGA_Ext_Gain.get()) + AWGA_Ext_Offset.get()
10131  AWGAwaveform = (AWGAwaveform * amplitude) + offset # scale and offset the waveform
10132  SplitAWGAwaveform()
10133  duty1lab.config(text="Harmonics")
10134  BAWGAPhaseDelay()
10135  UpdateAwgCont()
10136 #
10137 def AWGAMakeSinc():
10138  global AWGAwaveform, AWGSampleRate, AWGAAmplvalue, AWGAOffsetvalue, AWGALength, AWGAperiodvalue
10139  global AWGADutyCyclevalue, AWGAFreqvalue, duty1lab, AWGAgain, AWGAoffset, AWGAPhaseDelay
10140  global AWGA2X, AWG_2X, SAMPLErate, BaseSampleRate, AWG_Amp_Mode # 0 = Min/Max mode, 1 = Amp/Offset
10141  global AWGA_Ext_Gain, AWGA_Ext_Offset, AWGB_Ext_Gain, AWGB_Ext_Offset
10142 
10143  BAWGAAmpl(0)
10144  BAWGAOffset(0)
10145  BAWGAFreq(0)
10146  BAWGAPhase(0)
10147  BAWGADutyCycle(0)
10148 
10149  if AWGAFreqvalue > 0.0:
10150  if AWG_2X.get() == 1:
10151  AWGAperiodvalue = int((BaseSampleRate*2)/AWGAFreqvalue)
10152  SamplesPermS = int((BaseSampleRate*2)/1000) # 200
10153  if AWGAperiodvalue % 2 != 0: # make sure record length is even so 2X mode works for all Freq
10154  AWGAperiodvalue = AWGAperiodvalue + 1
10155  else:
10156  AWGAperiodvalue = BaseSampleRate/AWGAFreqvalue
10157  SamplesPermS = int(BaseSampleRate/1000) # 100
10158  else:
10159  AWGAperiodvalue = 0.0
10160  if AWG_Amp_Mode.get() == 1:
10161  MaxV = (AWGAOffsetvalue * AWGA_Ext_Gain.get()) + AWGA_Ext_Offset.get() + (AWGAAmplvalue * AWGA_Ext_Gain.get())
10162  MinV = (AWGAOffsetvalue * AWGA_Ext_Gain.get()) + AWGA_Ext_Offset.get() - (AWGAAmplvalue * AWGA_Ext_Gain.get())
10163  else:
10164  MaxV = AWGAOffsetvalue
10165  MinV = AWGAAmplvalue
10166 
10167  if AWGAPhaseDelay.get() == 0:
10168  if AWGAPhasevalue > 0:
10169  AWGAdelayvalue = AWGAperiodvalue * AWGAPhasevalue / 360.0
10170  else:
10171  AWGAdelayvalue = 0.0
10172  elif AWGAPhaseDelay.get() == 1:
10173  AWGAdelayvalue = AWGAPhasevalue * SAMPLErate / 1000
10174 
10175  Cycles = int(AWGADutyCyclevalue*100)
10176  NCycles = -1 * Cycles
10177  AWGAwaveform = []
10178  AWGAwaveform = numpy.sinc(numpy.linspace(NCycles, Cycles, SAMPLErate/AWGAFreqvalue))
10179  amplitude = (MaxV-MinV) / 2.0
10180  offset = (MaxV+MinV) / 2.0
10181  AWGAwaveform = (AWGAwaveform * amplitude) + offset # scale and offset the waveform
10182  Cycles = int(37500/AWGAperiodvalue)
10183  if Cycles < 1:
10184  Cycles = 1
10185  if Cycles > 1:
10186  Extend = int((Cycles-1.0)*AWGAperiodvalue/2.0)
10187  AWGAwaveform = numpy.pad(AWGAwaveform, (Extend,Extend), 'wrap')
10188  AWGAwaveform = numpy.roll(AWGAwaveform, int(AWGAdelayvalue))
10189  SplitAWGAwaveform()
10190  #BAWGAPhaseDelay()
10191  duty1lab.config(text="Cycles")
10192  BAWGAPhaseDelay()
10193  UpdateAwgCont()

10195 def AWGAMakeSSQ():
10196  global AWGAwaveform, AWGAAmplvalue, AWGAOffsetvalue, AWGALength, AWGAPhaseDelay, phasealab, duty1lab
10197  global AWGAFreqvalue, AWGAperiodvalue, AWGSAMPLErate, AWGADutyCyclevalue, AWGAPhasevalue, AWG_Amp_Mode # 0 = Min/Max mode, 1 = Amp/Offset
10198  global AWGABurstFlag, AWGACycles, AWGABurstDelay
10199  global AWGA2X, AWG_2X, SAMPLErate, BaseSampleRate
10200  global AWGA_Ext_Gain, AWGA_Ext_Offset, AWGB_Ext_Gain, AWGB_Ext_Offset
10201 
10202  BAWGAAmpl(0)
10203  BAWGAOffset(0)
10204  BAWGAFreq(0)
10205  BAWGAPhase(0)
10206  BAWGADutyCycle(0)
10207 
10208  if AWGAFreqvalue > 0.0:
10209  if AWG_2X.get() == 1:
10210  AWGAperiodvalue = int((BaseSampleRate*2)/AWGAFreqvalue)
10211  SamplesPermS = int((BaseSampleRate*2)/1000) # 200
10212  if AWGAperiodvalue % 2 != 0: # make sure record length is even so 2X mode works for all Freq
10213  AWGAperiodvalue = AWGAperiodvalue + 1
10214  else:
10215  AWGAperiodvalue = BaseSampleRate/AWGAFreqvalue
10216  SamplesPermS = int(BaseSampleRate/1000) # 100
10217  else:
10218  AWGAperiodvalue = 0.0
10219  if AWG_Amp_Mode.get() == 1:
10220  MaxV = (AWGAOffsetvalue * AWGA_Ext_Gain.get()) + AWGA_Ext_Offset.get() + (AWGAAmplvalue * AWGA_Ext_Gain.get())
10221  MinV = (AWGAOffsetvalue * AWGA_Ext_Gain.get()) + AWGA_Ext_Offset.get() - (AWGAAmplvalue * AWGA_Ext_Gain.get())
10222  else:
10223  MaxV = AWGAOffsetvalue
10224  MinV = AWGAAmplvalue
10225  AWGAwaveform = []
10226  SlopeValue = int(AWGAPhasevalue*SamplesPermS)
10227  if SlopeValue <= 0:
10228  SlopeValue = 1
10229  PulseWidth = int(AWGAperiodvalue * AWGADutyCyclevalue)
10230  if PulseWidth <=0:
10231  PulseWidth = 1
10232  Remainder = int((AWGAperiodvalue - PulseWidth - SlopeValue)/2)
10233  if Remainder <= 0:
10234  Remainder = 1
10235  PulseWidth = PulseWidth - SlopeValue
10236  if PulseWidth <=0:
10237  PulseWidth = 1
10238  StepAmp = (MaxV - MinV)/2
10239  StepOff = (MaxV + MinV)/2
10240  AWGAwaveform = StepAmp * (numpy.cos(numpy.linspace(0, 2*numpy.pi, SlopeValue*2))) + StepOff
10241  MidArray = numpy.ones(PulseWidth) * MinV
10242  AWGAwaveform = numpy.insert(AWGAwaveform, SlopeValue, MidArray)
10243  AWGAwaveform = numpy.pad(AWGAwaveform, (Remainder, Remainder), 'edge')
10244  if AWGABurstFlag.get() == 1:
10245  TempOneCycle = AWGAwaveform
10246  for i in range(AWGACycles-1):
10247  AWGAwaveform = numpy.concatenate((AWGAwaveform, TempOneCycle))
10248  TempDelay = int(AWGABurstDelay*SamplesPermS/2) # convert mS to samples
10249  AWGAwaveform = numpy.pad(AWGAwaveform, (TempDelay, TempDelay), 'edge')
10250  SplitAWGAwaveform()
10251  duty1lab.config(text="%")
10252  phasealab.config(text = "Rise Time")
10253  UpdateAwgCont()
10254 #
10255 def AWGAMakeTrapazoid():
10256  global AWGAwaveform, AWGAAmplvalue, AWGAOffsetvalue, AWGALength, AWGAPhaseDelay, phasealab, duty1lab
10257  global AWGAFreqvalue, AWGAperiodvalue, AWGSAMPLErate, AWGADutyCyclevalue, AWGAPhasevalue, AWG_Amp_Mode # 0 = Min/Max mode, 1 = Amp/Offset
10258  global AWGABurstFlag, AWGACycles, AWGABurstDelay
10259  global AWGA2X, AWG_2X, SAMPLErate, BaseSampleRate
10260  global AWGA_Ext_Gain, AWGA_Ext_Offset, AWGB_Ext_Gain, AWGB_Ext_Offset
10261 
10262  BAWGAAmpl(0)
10263  BAWGAOffset(0)
10264  BAWGAFreq(0)
10265  BAWGAPhase(0)
10266  BAWGADutyCycle(0)
10267 
10268  if AWGAFreqvalue > 0.0:
10269  if AWG_2X.get() == 1:
10270  AWGAperiodvalue = int((BaseSampleRate*2)/AWGAFreqvalue)
10271  SamplesPermS = int((BaseSampleRate*2)/1000) # 200
10272  if AWGAperiodvalue % 2 != 0: # make sure record length is even so 2X mode works for all Freq
10273  AWGAperiodvalue = AWGAperiodvalue + 1
10274  else:
10275  AWGAperiodvalue = BaseSampleRate/AWGAFreqvalue
10276  SamplesPermS = int(BaseSampleRate/1000) # 100
10277  else:
10278  AWGAperiodvalue = 0.0
10279  if AWG_Amp_Mode.get() == 1:
10280  MaxV = (AWGAOffsetvalue * AWGA_Ext_Gain.get()) + AWGA_Ext_Offset.get() + (AWGAAmplvalue * AWGA_Ext_Gain.get())
10281  MinV = (AWGAOffsetvalue * AWGA_Ext_Gain.get()) + AWGA_Ext_Offset.get() - (AWGAAmplvalue * AWGA_Ext_Gain.get())
10282  else:
10283  MaxV = AWGAOffsetvalue
10284  MinV = AWGAAmplvalue
10285  AWGAwaveform = []
10286  SlopeValue = int(AWGAPhasevalue*SamplesPermS) # convert mS to samples
10287  if SlopeValue <= 0:
10288  SlopeValue = 1
10289  PulseWidth = int(AWGAperiodvalue * AWGADutyCyclevalue)
10290  if PulseWidth <=0:
10291  PulseWidth = 1
10292  Remainder = int(AWGAperiodvalue - PulseWidth) - SlopeValue
10293  if Remainder <= 0:
10294  Remainder = 1
10295  PulseWidth = PulseWidth - SlopeValue
10296  if PulseWidth <=0:
10297  PulseWidth = 1
10298  StepValue = (MaxV - MinV) / SlopeValue
10299  SampleValue = MinV
10300  for i in range(SlopeValue):
10301  AWGAwaveform.append(SampleValue)
10302  SampleValue = SampleValue + StepValue
10303  for i in range(PulseWidth):
10304  AWGAwaveform.append(MaxV)
10305  for i in range(SlopeValue):
10306  AWGAwaveform.append(SampleValue)
10307  SampleValue = SampleValue - StepValue
10308  for i in range(Remainder):
10309  AWGAwaveform.append(MinV)
10310  if AWGABurstFlag.get() == 1:
10311  TempOneCycle = AWGAwaveform
10312  for i in range(AWGACycles-1):
10313  AWGAwaveform = numpy.concatenate((AWGAwaveform, TempOneCycle))
10314  TempDelay = int(AWGABurstDelay*SamplesPermS/2) # convert mS to samples
10315  AWGAwaveform = numpy.pad(AWGAwaveform, (TempDelay, TempDelay), 'edge')
10316  SplitAWGAwaveform()
10317  duty1lab.config(text="%")
10318  phasealab.config(text = "Rise Time")
10319  UpdateAwgCont()
10320 #
10321 def AWGAMakePulse():
10322  global AWGAwaveform, AWGAAmplvalue, AWGAOffsetvalue, AWGALength, AWGAPhaseDelay, phasealab, duty1lab
10323  global AWGAFreqvalue, AWGAperiodvalue, AWGSAMPLErate, AWGADutyCyclevalue, AWGAPhasevalue, AWG_Amp_Mode # 0 = Min/Max mode, 1 = Amp/Offset
10324  global AWGABurstFlag, AWGACycles, AWGABurstDelay
10325  global AWGA2X, AWG_2X, SAMPLErate, BaseSampleRate
10326  global AWGA_Ext_Gain, AWGA_Ext_Offset, AWGB_Ext_Gain, AWGB_Ext_Offset
10327 
10328  BAWGAAmpl(0)
10329  BAWGAOffset(0)
10330  BAWGAFreq(0)
10331  BAWGAPhase(0)
10332 
10333  try:
10334  AWGADutyCyclevalue = float(eval(AWGADutyCycleEntry.get()))
10335  except:
10336  AWGADutyCycleEntry.delete(0,"end")
10337  AWGADutyCycleEntry.insert(0, AWGADutyCyclevalue)
10338 
10339  if AWGAFreqvalue > 0.0:
10340  if AWG_2X.get() == 1:
10341  AWGAperiodvalue = int((BaseSampleRate*2)/AWGAFreqvalue)
10342  SamplesPermS = int((BaseSampleRate*2)/1000) # 200
10343  if AWGAperiodvalue % 2 != 0: # make sure record length is even so 2X mode works for all Freq
10344  AWGAperiodvalue = AWGAperiodvalue + 1
10345  else:
10346  AWGAperiodvalue = BaseSampleRate/AWGAFreqvalue
10347  SamplesPermS = int(BaseSampleRate/1000) # 100
10348  else:
10349  AWGAperiodvalue = 0.0
10350  if AWG_Amp_Mode.get() == 1:
10351  MaxV = (AWGAOffsetvalue * AWGA_Ext_Gain.get()) + AWGA_Ext_Offset.get() + (AWGAAmplvalue * AWGA_Ext_Gain.get())
10352  MinV = (AWGAOffsetvalue * AWGA_Ext_Gain.get()) + AWGA_Ext_Offset.get() - (AWGAAmplvalue * AWGA_Ext_Gain.get())
10353  else:
10354  MaxV = AWGAOffsetvalue
10355  MinV = AWGAAmplvalue
10356  AWGAwaveform = []
10357  SlopeValue = int(AWGAPhasevalue*SamplesPermS) # convert mS to samples
10358  if SlopeValue <= 0:
10359  SlopeValue = 1
10360  PulseWidth = int(AWGADutyCyclevalue*SamplesPermS) # convert mS to samples
10361  if PulseWidth <=0:
10362  PulseWidth = 1
10363  Remainder = int(AWGAperiodvalue - PulseWidth) - SlopeValue
10364  if Remainder <= 0:
10365  Remainder = 1
10366  PulseWidth = PulseWidth - SlopeValue
10367  if PulseWidth <=0:
10368  PulseWidth = 1
10369  StepValue = (MaxV - MinV) / SlopeValue
10370  SampleValue = MinV
10371  for i in range(SlopeValue):
10372  AWGAwaveform.append(SampleValue)
10373  SampleValue = SampleValue + StepValue
10374  for i in range(PulseWidth):
10375  AWGAwaveform.append(MaxV)
10376  for i in range(SlopeValue):
10377  AWGAwaveform.append(SampleValue)
10378  SampleValue = SampleValue - StepValue
10379  for i in range(Remainder):
10380  AWGAwaveform.append(MinV)
10381  if AWGABurstFlag.get() == 1:
10382  TempOneCycle = AWGAwaveform
10383  for i in range(AWGACycles-1):
10384  AWGAwaveform = numpy.concatenate((AWGAwaveform, TempOneCycle))
10385  TempDelay = int(AWGABurstDelay*SamplesPermS/2) # convert mS to samples
10386  AWGAwaveform = numpy.pad(AWGAwaveform, (TempDelay, TempDelay), 'edge')
10387  SplitAWGAwaveform()
10388  duty1lab.config(text="Width mS")
10389  phasealab.config(text = "Rise Time")
10390  UpdateAwgCont()
