10455 def AWGAMakeUpDownRamp():
10456  global AWGAwaveform, AWGAAmplvalue, AWGAOffsetvalue, AWGALength, AWGAPhaseDelay, duty1lab
10457  global AWGAFreqvalue, AWGAperiodvalue, AWGSAMPLErate, AWGADutyCyclevalue, AWGAPhasevalue, AWG_Amp_Mode # 0 = Min/Max mode, 1 = Amp/Offset
10458  global AWGABurstFlag, AWGACycles, AWGABurstDelay
10459  global AWGA2X, AWG_2X, SAMPLErate, BaseSampleRate
10460  global AWGA_Ext_Gain, AWGA_Ext_Offset, AWGB_Ext_Gain, AWGB_Ext_Offset
10461 
10462  BAWGAAmpl(0)
10463  BAWGAOffset(0)
10464  BAWGAFreq(0)
10465  BAWGAPhase(0)
10466  BAWGADutyCycle(0)
10467 
10468  if AWGAFreqvalue > 0.0:
10469  if AWG_2X.get() == 1:
10470  AWGAperiodvalue = int((BaseSampleRate*2)/AWGAFreqvalue)
10471  SamplesPermS = int((BaseSampleRate*2)/1000) # 200
10472  if AWGAperiodvalue % 2 != 0: # make sure record length is even so 2X mode works for all Freq
10473  AWGAperiodvalue = AWGAperiodvalue + 1
10474  else:
10475  AWGAperiodvalue = AWGSAMPLErate/AWGAFreqvalue
10476  SamplesPermS = int(BaseSampleRate/1000) # 100
10477  else:
10478  AWGAperiodvalue = 0.0
10479  if AWG_Amp_Mode.get() == 1:
10480  MaxV = (AWGAOffsetvalue * AWGA_Ext_Gain.get()) + AWGA_Ext_Offset.get() + (AWGAAmplvalue * AWGA_Ext_Gain.get())
10481  MinV = (AWGAOffsetvalue * AWGA_Ext_Gain.get()) + AWGA_Ext_Offset.get() - (AWGAAmplvalue * AWGA_Ext_Gain.get())
10482  else:
10483  MaxV = AWGAOffsetvalue
10484  MinV = AWGAAmplvalue
10485  #
10486  if AWGAPhaseDelay.get() == 0:
10487  if AWGAPhasevalue > 0:
10488  AWGAdelayvalue = AWGAperiodvalue * AWGAPhasevalue / 360.0
10489  else:
10490  AWGAdelayvalue = 0.0
10491  elif AWGAPhaseDelay.get() == 1:
10492  AWGAdelayvalue = AWGAPhasevalue * SAMPLErate / 1000
10493  #
10494  AWGAwaveform = []
10495  PulseWidth = int(AWGAperiodvalue * AWGADutyCyclevalue)
10496  if PulseWidth <=0:
10497  PulseWidth = 1
10498  Remainder = int(AWGAperiodvalue - PulseWidth)
10499  if Remainder <= 0:
10500  Remainder = 1
10501  UpStepValue = (MaxV - MinV) / PulseWidth
10502  DownStepValue = (MaxV - MinV) / Remainder
10503  SampleValue = MinV
10504  for i in range(PulseWidth):
10505  AWGAwaveform.append(SampleValue)
10506  SampleValue = SampleValue + UpStepValue
10507  for i in range(Remainder):
10508  AWGAwaveform.append(SampleValue)
10509  SampleValue = SampleValue - DownStepValue
10510  AWGAwaveform = numpy.roll(AWGAwaveform, int(AWGAdelayvalue))
10511  if AWGABurstFlag.get() == 1:
10512  TempOneCycle = AWGAwaveform
10513  for i in range(AWGACycles-1):
10514  AWGAwaveform = numpy.concatenate((AWGAwaveform, TempOneCycle))
10515  TempDelay = int(AWGABurstDelay*SamplesPermS) # convert mS to samples
10516  AWGAwaveform = numpy.pad(AWGAwaveform, (TempDelay, 0), 'edge')
10517  SplitAWGAwaveform()
10518  BAWGAPhaseDelay()
10519  duty1lab.config(text = "Symmetry")
10520  BAWGAPhaseDelay()
10521  UpdateAwgCont()

10523 def AWGAMakeImpulse():
10524  global AWGAwaveform, AWGAAmplvalue, AWGAOffsetvalue, AWGALength, AWGAPhaseDelay, AWG_Amp_Mode # 0 = Min/Max mode, 1 = Amp/Offset
10525  global AWGAFreqvalue, AWGAperiodvalue, AWGSAMPLErate, AWGADutyCyclevalue, AWGAPhasevalue
10526  global AWGABurstFlag, AWGACycles, AWGABurstDelay
10527  global AWGA2X, AWG_2X, SAMPLErate, BaseSampleRate
10528  global AWGA_Ext_Gain, AWGA_Ext_Offset, AWGB_Ext_Gain, AWGB_Ext_Offset
10529 
10530  BAWGAAmpl(0)
10531  BAWGAOffset(0)
10532  BAWGAFreq(0)
10533  BAWGAPhase(0)
10534  BAWGADutyCycle(0)
10535 
10536  if AWGAFreqvalue > 0.0:
10537  if AWG_2X.get() == 1:
10538  AWGAperiodvalue = int((BaseSampleRate*2)/AWGAFreqvalue)
10539  SamplesPermS = int((BaseSampleRate*2)/1000) # 200
10540  if AWGAperiodvalue % 2 != 0: # make sure record length is even so 2X mode works for all Freq
10541  AWGAperiodvalue = AWGAperiodvalue + 1
10542  else:
10543  AWGAperiodvalue = BaseSampleRate/AWGAFreqvalue
10544  SamplesPermS = int(BaseSampleRate/1000) # 100
10545  else:
10546  AWGAperiodvalue = 0.0
10547  if AWG_Amp_Mode.get() == 1:
10548  MaxV = (AWGAOffsetvalue * AWGA_Ext_Gain.get()) + AWGA_Ext_Offset.get() + (AWGAAmplvalue * AWGA_Ext_Gain.get())
10549  MinV = (AWGAOffsetvalue * AWGA_Ext_Gain.get()) + AWGA_Ext_Offset.get() - (AWGAAmplvalue * AWGA_Ext_Gain.get())
10550  else:
10551  MaxV = AWGAOffsetvalue
10552  MinV = AWGAAmplvalue
10553  AWGAwaveform = []
10554  PulseWidth = int(AWGAperiodvalue * AWGADutyCyclevalue / 2.0)
10555  if AWGAPhaseDelay.get() == 0:
10556  DelayValue = int(AWGAperiodvalue*(AWGAPhasevalue/360))
10557  elif AWGAPhaseDelay.get() == 1:
10558  DelayValue = int(AWGAPhasevalue*SamplesPermS)
10559  for i in range(DelayValue-PulseWidth):
10560  AWGAwaveform.append((MinV+MaxV)/2.0)
10561  for i in range(PulseWidth):
10562  AWGAwaveform.append(MaxV)
10563  for i in range(PulseWidth):
10564  AWGAwaveform.append(MinV)
10565  DelayValue = int(AWGAperiodvalue-DelayValue)
10566  for i in range(DelayValue-PulseWidth):
10567  AWGAwaveform.append((MinV+MaxV)/2.0)
10568  if AWGABurstFlag.get() == 1:
10569  TempOneCycle = AWGAwaveform
10570  for i in range(AWGACycles-1):
10571  AWGAwaveform = numpy.concatenate((AWGAwaveform, TempOneCycle))
10572  TempDelay = int(AWGABurstDelay*SamplesPermS) # convert mS to samples
10573  AWGAwaveform = numpy.pad(AWGAwaveform, (TempDelay, 0), 'edge')
10574  SplitAWGAwaveform()
10575  duty1lab.config(text = "Duty Cycle")
10576  BAWGAPhaseDelay()
10577  UpdateAwgCont()

10579 def AWGAMakeUUNoise():
10580  global AWGAwaveform, AWGSAMPLErate, AWGAAmplvalue, AWGAOffsetvalue, AWGAFreqvalue
10581  global AWGALength, AWGAperiodvalue, AWG_Amp_Mode # 0 = Min/Max mode, 1 = Amp/Offset
10582  global AWGABurstFlag, AWGACycles, AWGABurstDelay
10583  global AWGA2X, AWG_2X, SAMPLErate, BaseSampleRate
10584  global AWGA_Ext_Gain, AWGA_Ext_Offset, AWGB_Ext_Gain, AWGB_Ext_Offset
10585 
10586  BAWGAAmpl(0)
10587  BAWGAOffset(0)
10588  BAWGAFreq(0)
10589 
10590  if AWGAFreqvalue > 0.0:
10591  if AWG_2X.get() == 1:
10592  AWGAperiodvalue = int((BaseSampleRate*2)/AWGAFreqvalue)
10593  SamplesPermS = int((BaseSampleRate*2)/1000) # 200
10594  if AWGAperiodvalue % 2 != 0: # make sure record length is even so 2X mode works for all Freq
10595  AWGAperiodvalue = AWGAperiodvalue + 1
10596  else:
10597  AWGAperiodvalue = BaseSampleRate/AWGAFreqvalue
10598  SamplesPermS = int(BaseSampleRate/1000) # 100
10599  else:
10600  AWGAperiodvalue = 0.0
10601  if AWG_Amp_Mode.get() == 1:
10602  MaxV = (AWGAOffsetvalue * AWGA_Ext_Gain.get()) + AWGA_Ext_Offset.get() + (AWGAAmplvalue * AWGA_Ext_Gain.get())
10603  MinV = (AWGAOffsetvalue * AWGA_Ext_Gain.get()) + AWGA_Ext_Offset.get() - (AWGAAmplvalue * AWGA_Ext_Gain.get())
10604  else:
10605  if AWGAAmplvalue > AWGAOffsetvalue:
10606  MinV = AWGAOffsetvalue
10607  MaxV = AWGAAmplvalue
10608  else:
10609  MaxV = AWGAOffsetvalue
10610  MinV = AWGAAmplvalue

10615  TempOneCycle = AWGAwaveform
10616  for i in range(AWGACycles-1):
10617  AWGAwaveform = numpy.concatenate((AWGAwaveform, TempOneCycle))
10618  TempDelay = int(AWGABurstDelay*SamplesPermS) # convert mS to samples
10619  AWGAwaveform = numpy.pad(AWGAwaveform, (TempDelay, 0), 'constant', constant_values=(Mid))
10620  SplitAWGAwaveform()
10621  BAWGAPhaseDelay()

10669 def BAWGAModeLabel():

10680  if HWRevOne == "D":
10681  if AWGAMode.get() == 0:

10684  label_txt = "SIMV"

10691 def UpdateAWGA():
10692  global AWGAAmplvalue, AWGAOffsetvalue
10693  global AWGAFreqvalue, AWGAPhasevalue, AWGAPhaseDelay
10694  global AWGADutyCyclevalue, FSweepMode, AWGARepeatFlag, AWGSync
10695  global AWGAWave, AWGAMode, AWGATerm, AWGAwaveform, AWGAIOMode
10696  global CHA, CHB, AWGSAMPLErate, DevID, devx, HWRevOne, AWG_Amp_Mode # 0 = Min/Max mode, 1 = Amp/Offset
10697  global amp1lab, off1lab, AWGA2X, AWGA2X, AWGBWave, AWGBRepeatFlag
10698  global AWGA_Ext_Gain, AWGA_Ext_Offset, AWGB_Ext_Gain, AWGB_Ext_Offset
10699 
10700  BAWGAAmpl(0)
10701  BAWGAOffset(0)
10702  BAWGAFreq(0)
10703  BAWGAPhase(0)
10704  BAWGADutyCycle(0)
10705  BAWGAShape()
10706 
10707  if AWG_Amp_Mode.get() == 0: # 0 = Min/Max mode, 1 = Amp/Offset
10708  amp1lab.config(text = "Min Ch A" ) # change displayed value
10709  off1lab.config(text = "Max Ch A" ) # change displayed value
10710  else:
10711  amp1lab.config(text = "Amp Ch A" )
10712  off1lab.config(text = "Off Ch A" )
10713 
10714  if AWGAFreqvalue > 0.0:
10715  AWGAperiodvalue = AWGSAMPLErate/AWGAFreqvalue
10716  else:
10717  AWGAperiodvalue = 0.0
10718 
10719  if AWGAPhaseDelay.get() == 0:
10720  if AWGAWave == 'square':
10721  AWGAPhasevalue = AWGAPhasevalue + 270.0
10722  if AWGAPhasevalue > 359:
10723  AWGAPhasevalue = AWGAPhasevalue - 360
10724  if AWGAPhasevalue > 0:
10725  AWGAdelayvalue = AWGAperiodvalue * AWGAPhasevalue / 360.0
10726  else:
10727  AWGAdelayvalue = 0.0
10728  elif AWGAPhaseDelay.get() == 1:
10729  AWGAdelayvalue = AWGAPhasevalue * 100
10730 
10731  if AWGATerm.get() == 0: # Open termination
10732  devx.ctrl_transfer( 0x40, 0x51, 32, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set 2.5 V switch to open
10733  devx.ctrl_transfer( 0x40, 0x51, 33, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set GND switch to open
10734  elif AWGATerm.get() == 1: # 50 Ohm termination to GND
10735  devx.ctrl_transfer( 0x40, 0x51, 32, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set 2.5 V switch to open
10736  devx.ctrl_transfer( 0x40, 0x50, 33, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set GND switch to closed
10737  elif AWGATerm.get() == 2: # 50 Ohm termination to +2.5 Volts
10738  devx.ctrl_transfer( 0x40, 0x50, 32, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set 2.5 V switch to closed
10739  devx.ctrl_transfer( 0x40, 0x51, 33, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set GND switch to open
10740 
10741  if AWGAWave == 'dc':
10742  if AWG_2X.get() == 2:
10743  AWGAWave == 'arbitrary'
10744  CHA.arbitrary(AWGB2X, AWGBRepeatFlag.get())
10745  else:
10746  if AWGAMode.get() == 0: # Source Voltage measure current mode
10747  if AWGAIOMode.get() == 0:
10748  CHA.mode = Mode.SVMI # Put CHA in SVMI mode
10749  else:
10750  CHA.mode = Mode.SVMI_SPLIT # Put CHA in SVMI split mode
10751  CHA.constant(AWGAOffsetvalue)
10752  #
10753  if AWGAMode.get() == 1: # Source current measure voltage mode
10754  if AWGAIOMode.get() == 0:
10755  CHA.mode = Mode.SIMV # Put CHA in SIMV mode
10756  else:
10757  CHA.mode = Mode.SIMV_SPLIT # Put CHA in SIMV split mode
10758  CHA.constant(AWGAOffsetvalue/1000)
10759  #
10760  if AWGAMode.get() == 2: # High impedance mode
10761  if AWGAIOMode.get() == 0:
10762  CHA.mode = Mode.HI_Z # Put CHA in Hi Z mode
10763  else:
10764  CHA.mode = Mode.HI_Z_SPLIT # Put CHA in Hi Z split mode
10765  #
10766  if AWGAIOMode.get() > 0: # Split Input / Output mode
10767  if HWRevOne == "D":
10768  AWGAMode.set(1)
10769  CHA.mode = Mode.SIMV_SPLIT # channel must be in source current mode
10770 #
10771  else:
10772  if AWGAMode.get() == 0: # Source Voltage measure current mode
10773  if AWGAIOMode.get() == 0:
10774  CHA.mode = Mode.SVMI # Put CHA in SVMI mode
10775  else:
10776  CHA.mode = Mode.SVMI_SPLIT # Put CHA in SVMI split mode
10777  if AWGAMode.get() == 1: # Source current measure voltage mode
10778  if AWGAIOMode.get() == 0:
10779  CHA.mode = Mode.SIMV # Put CHA in SIMV mode
10780  else:
10781  CHA.mode = Mode.SIMV_SPLIT # Put CHA in SIMV split mode
10782  AWGAOffsetvalue = AWGAOffsetvalue/1000
10783  AWGAAmplvalue = AWGAAmplvalue/1000
10784  if AWGAMode.get() == 2: # High impedance mode
10785  if AWGAIOMode.get() == 0:
10786  CHA.mode = Mode.HI_Z # Put CHA in Hi Z mode
10787  else:
10788  CHA.mode = Mode.HI_Z_SPLIT # Put CHA in Hi Z split mode
10789  else:
10790  if AWG_Amp_Mode.get() == 1:
10791  MaxV = (AWGAOffsetvalue * AWGA_Ext_Gain.get()) + AWGA_Ext_Offset.get() + (AWGAAmplvalue * AWGA_Ext_Gain.get())
10792  MinV = (AWGAOffsetvalue * AWGA_Ext_Gain.get()) + AWGA_Ext_Offset.get() - (AWGAAmplvalue * AWGA_Ext_Gain.get())
10793  else:
10794  MaxV = AWGAOffsetvalue
10795  MinV = AWGAAmplvalue
10796  try:
10797  if AWGAWave == 'sine':
10798  CHA.sine(MaxV, MinV, AWGAperiodvalue, AWGAdelayvalue)
10799  elif AWGAWave == 'triangle':
10800  CHA.triangle(MaxV, MinV, AWGAperiodvalue, AWGAdelayvalue)
10801  elif AWGAWave == 'sawtooth':
10802  CHA.sawtooth(MaxV, MinV, AWGAperiodvalue, AWGAdelayvalue)
10803  elif AWGAWave == 'square':
10804  CHA.square(MaxV, MinV, AWGAperiodvalue, AWGAdelayvalue, AWGADutyCyclevalue)
10805  elif AWGAWave == 'stairstep':
10806  CHA.stairstep(MaxV, MinV, AWGAperiodvalue, AWGAdelayvalue)
10807  elif AWGAWave == 'arbitrary':
10808  if AWGSync.get() == 0:
10809  AWGARepeatFlag.set(1)
10810  if AWG_2X.get() == 2:
10811  AWGAWave == 'arbitrary'
10812  CHA.arbitrary(AWGB2X, AWGBRepeatFlag.get())
10813  else:
10814  CHA.arbitrary(AWGAwaveform, AWGARepeatFlag.get()) # set repeat flag
10815  except:
10816  donothing()
10817  if AWGAIOMode.get() > 0: # Split Input / Output mode
10818  if HWRevOne == "D":
10819  AWGAMode.set(1)
10820  CHA.mode = Mode.SIMV_SPLIT # channel must be in source current mode

10872 def BAWGBAmpl(temp):
10873  global AWGBAmplEntry, AWGBAmplvalue, AWGBMode, AWG_Amp_Mode # 0 = Min/Max mode, 1 = Amp/Offset
10874  global AWGA_Ext_Gain, AWGA_Ext_Offset, AWGB_Ext_Gain, AWGB_Ext_Offset
10875 
10876  try:
10877  AWGBAmplvalue = float(eval(AWGBAmplEntry.get()))
10878  except:
10879  AWGBAmplEntry.delete(0,"end")
10880  AWGBAmplEntry.insert(0, AWGBAmplvalue)
10881  #
10882  if AWGBMode.get() == 0: # Source Voltage measure current mode
10883  if AWG_Amp_Mode.get() == 0: # 0 = Min/Max
10884  if AWGBAmplvalue > 5.00:
10885  AWGBAmplvalue = 5.00
10886  AWGBAmplEntry.delete(0,"end")
10887  AWGBAmplEntry.insert(0, AWGBAmplvalue)
10888  if AWGBAmplvalue < 0.00:
10889  AWGBAmplvalue = 0.00
10890  AWGBAmplEntry.delete(0,"end")
10891  AWGBAmplEntry.insert(0, AWGBAmplvalue)
10892  elif AWG_Amp_Mode.get() == 1: # 1 = Amp/Offset
10893  if AWGBAmplvalue > (2.5 / AWGB_Ext_Gain.get()):
10894  AWGBAmplvalue = 2.5 / AWGB_Ext_Gain.get()
10895  AWGBAmplEntry.delete(0,"end")
10896  AWGBAmplEntry.insert(0, AWGBAmplvalue)
10897  if AWGBAmplvalue < (-2.50 / AWGB_Ext_Gain.get()):
10898  AWGBAmplvalue = -2.50 / AWGB_Ext_Gain.get()
10899  AWGBAmplEntry.delete(0,"end")
10900  AWGBAmplEntry.insert(0, AWGBAmplvalue)
10901  elif AWGBMode.get() == 1: # Source current measure voltage mode
10902  if AWGBAmplvalue > 200.00:
10903  AWGBAmplvalue = 200.00
10904  AWGBAmplEntry.delete(0,"end")
10905  AWGBAmplEntry.insert(0, AWGBAmplvalue)
10906  if AWGBAmplvalue < -200.00:
10907  AWGBAmplvalue = -200.00
10908  AWGBAmplEntry.delete(0,"end")
10909  AWGBAmplEntry.insert(0, AWGBAmplvalue)

11141  spf = wave.open(AWGBwavFile,'r')
11142  except:
11143  showwarning("WARNING","No such file found or wrong format!", parent=awgwindow)
11144  AWGBwaveform = []

11147  showwarning("WARNING","Only mono files supported!", parent=awgwindow)

11151  if Length > 90000: # limit to first 90K samples
11152  Length = 90000

11154  WAVsignal = numpy.fromstring(signal, 'Int16') # convert strings to Int

11156  AWGBwaveform = (WAVsignal * 2.5 / 32768) + 2.5

11198 def AWGBMakeFourier():
11199  global AWGBwaveform, AWGSAMPLErate, AWGBAmplvalue, AWGBOffsetvalue, AWGBLength, AWGBFreqvalue, awgwindow
11200  global AWG_Amp_Mode # 0 = Min/Max mode, 1 = Amp/Offset
11201  global AWGA2X, AWG_2X, SAMPLErate, BaseSampleRate, duty2lab
11202  global AWGA_Ext_Gain, AWGA_Ext_Offset, AWGB_Ext_Gain, AWGB_Ext_Offset
11203 
11204  Max_term = int(AWGBDutyCyclevalue*100)
11205 
11206  BAWGBAmpl(0)
11207  BAWGBOffset(0)
11208  BAWGBFreq(0)
11209  if AWG_2X.get() == 1:
11210  TempRate = (BaseSampleRate*2)
11211  else:
11212  TempRate = BaseSampleRate
11213  AWGBwaveform = []
11214  AWGBwaveform = numpy.cos(numpy.linspace(0, 2*numpy.pi, TempRate/AWGBFreqvalue)) # the fundamental
11215  k = 3
11216  while k <= Max_term:
11217  # Add odd harmonics up to max_term
11218  Harmonic = (math.sin(k*numpy.pi/2)/k)*(numpy.cos(numpy.linspace(0, k*2*numpy.pi, TempRate/AWGBFreqvalue)))
11219  AWGBwaveform = AWGBwaveform + Harmonic
11220  k = k + 2 # skip even numbers
11221  if AWG_Amp_Mode.get() == 0:
11222  amplitude = (AWGBOffsetvalue-AWGBAmplvalue)/2
11223  offset = (AWGBOffsetvalue+AWGBAmplvalue)/2
11224  else:
11225  amplitude = AWGBAmplvalue*AWGB_Ext_Gain.get()
11226  offset = (AWGBOffsetvalue * AWGB_Ext_Gain.get()) + AWGB_Ext_Offset.get()
11227  AWGBwaveform = (AWGBwaveform * amplitude) + offset # scale and offset the waveform
11228  SplitAWGBwaveform()
11229  duty2lab.config(text="Harmonics")
11230  BAWGBPhaseDelay()
11231  UpdateAwgCont()
11232 #
11233 def AWGBMakeBodeSine():
11234  global AWGBwaveform, AWGSAMPLErate, AWGBAmplvalue, AWGBOffsetvalue, AWGBLength, AWGBperiodvalue
11235  global AWGBDutyCyclevalue, AWGBFreqvalue, duty2lab, AWGBgain, AWGBoffset, AWGBPhaseDelay, AWGBMode
11236  global AWGB2X, AWG_2X, SAMPLErate, BaseSampleRate, AWG_Amp_Mode
11237  global AWGA_Ext_Gain, AWGA_Ext_Offset, AWGB_Ext_Gain, AWGB_Ext_Offset, AWGRecLength
11238 
11239  BAWGBAmpl(0)
11240  BAWGBOffset(0)
11241  BAWGBFreq(0)
11242  BAWGBPhase(0)
11243  BAWGBDutyCycle(0)
11244 
11245  if AWGBFreqvalue < 10.0: # if frequency is less than 10 Hz use libsmu sine function
11246  AWGBShape.set(1)
11247  BAWGBShape()
11248  UpdateAwgCont()
11249  return
11250 
11251  if AWGBFreqvalue > 0.0:
11252  if AWG_2X.get() == 2:
11253  AWGBperiodvalue = (BaseSampleRate*2)/AWGBFreqvalue
11254  else:
11255  AWGBperiodvalue = BaseSampleRate/AWGBFreqvalue
11256  else:
11257  AWGBperiodvalue = 10.0
11258 
11259  if AWGBPhaseDelay.get() == 0:
11260  if AWGBPhasevalue > 0:
11261  AWGBdelayvalue = AWGBperiodvalue * AWGBPhasevalue / 360.0
11262  else:
11263  AWGBdelayvalue = 0.0
11264  elif AWGBPhaseDelay.get() == 1:
11265  AWGBdelayvalue = AWGBPhasevalue * AWGSAMPLErate / 1000
11266  Cycles = int(AWGRecLength/AWGBperiodvalue)
11267  if Cycles < 1:
11268  Cycles = 1
11269  RecLength = int(Cycles * AWGBperiodvalue)
11270  if RecLength % 2 != 0: # make sure record length is even so 2X mode works for all Freq
11271  RecLength = RecLength + 1
11272  AWGBwaveform = []
11273  AWGBwaveform = numpy.cos(numpy.linspace(0, 2*Cycles*numpy.pi, RecLength))
11274 
11275  if AWG_Amp_Mode.get() == 0:
11276  if AWGBMode.get() == 1: # convert to mA
11277  amplitude = (AWGBOffsetvalue-AWGBAmplvalue) / -2000.0
11278  offset = (AWGBOffsetvalue+AWGBAmplvalue) / 2000.0
11279  else:
11280  amplitude = (AWGBOffsetvalue-AWGBAmplvalue) / -2.0
11281  offset = (AWGBOffsetvalue+AWGBAmplvalue) / 2.0
11282  else:
11283  if AWGBMode.get() == 1: # convert to mA
11284  amplitude = AWGBAmplvalue/1000.0
11285  offset = AWGBOffsetvalue/1000.0
11286  else:
11287  amplitude = AWGBAmplvalue*AWGB_Ext_Gain.get()
11288  offset = (AWGBOffsetvalue * AWGB_Ext_Gain.get()) + AWGB_Ext_Offset.get()
11289  AWGBwaveform = (AWGBwaveform * amplitude) + offset # scale and offset the waveform
11290  AWGBwaveform = numpy.roll(AWGBwaveform, int(AWGBdelayvalue))
11291  #
11292  if AWG_2X.get() == 2:
11293  Tempwaveform = []
11294  AWGB2X = []
11295  AWGB2X = AWGBwaveform[::2] # even numbered samples
11296  Tempwaveform = AWGBwaveform[1::2] # odd numbered samples Tempwaveform
11297  AWGBwaveform = Tempwaveform
11298  BAWGBPhaseDelay()
11299  duty2lab.config(text="%")
11300  UpdateAwgCont()

11302 def AWGBMakePWMSine():
11303  global AWGBwaveform, AWGSAMPLErate, AWGBAmplvalue, AWGBOffsetvalue, AWGBLength
11304  global AWGBDutyCyclevalue, AWGBFreqvalue, AWG_Amp_Mode # 0 = Min/Max mode, 1 = Amp/Offset
11305  global AWGB2X, AWG_2X, SAMPLErate, BaseSampleRate
11306  global AWGA_Ext_Gain, AWGA_Ext_Offset, AWGB_Ext_Gain, AWGB_Ext_Offset
11307 
11308  BAWGBAmpl(0)
11309  BAWGBOffset(0)
11310  BAWGBFreq(0)
11311  BAWGBPhase(0)
11312  BAWGBDutyCycle(0)
11313 
11314  if AWGBFreqvalue > 0.0:
11315  if AWG_2X.get() == 2:
11316  AWGBperiodvalue = (BaseSampleRate*2)/AWGBFreqvalue
11317  else:
11318  AWGBperiodvalue = BaseSampleRate/AWGBFreqvalue
11319  else:
11320  AWGBperiodvalue = 0.0
11321  if AWG_Amp_Mode.get() == 1:
11322  MaxV = (AWGBOffsetvalue * AWGB_Ext_Gain.get()) + AWGB_Ext_Offset.get() + (AWGBAmplvalue * AWGB_Ext_Gain.get())
11323  MinV = (AWGBOffsetvalue * AWGB_Ext_Gain.get()) + AWGB_Ext_Offset.get() - (AWGBAmplvalue * AWGB_Ext_Gain.get())
11324  else:
11325  MaxV = AWGBOffsetvalue
11326  MinV = AWGBAmplvalue
11327 
11328  PulseWidth = int(AWGBDutyCyclevalue*100)
11329  PulseSamples = int(AWGBperiodvalue/PulseWidth)
11330  AWGBwaveform = []
11331  for i in range(PulseSamples): #(i = 0; i < cPulse; i++)
11332  v = round(PulseWidth/2*(1+numpy.sin(i*2*numpy.pi/PulseSamples)))
11333  # print(v)
11334  for j in range(PulseWidth): #(j = 0; j < cLength; j++)
11335  if j >= v:
11336  AWGBwaveform.append(MaxV) # j>=v?1:0
11337  else:
11338  AWGBwaveform.append(MinV) # j>=v?1:0
11339  SplitAWGBwaveform()
11340  duty2lab.config(text="PWidth")
11341  UpdateAwgCont()

11343 def AWGBMakeSinc():
11344  global AWGBwaveform, AWGSampleRate, AWGBAmplvalue, AWGBOffsetvalue, AWGBLength, AWGBperiodvalue
11345  global AWGBDutyCyclevalue, AWGBFreqvalue, duty2lab, AWGBgain, AWGBoffset, AWGBPhaseDelay
11346  global AWGB2X, AWG_2X, SAMPLErate, BaseSampleRate, AWG_Amp_Mode # 0 = Min/Max mode, 1 = Amp/Offset
11347  global AWGA_Ext_Gain, AWGA_Ext_Offset, AWGB_Ext_Gain, AWGB_Ext_Offset
11348 
11349  BAWGBAmpl(0)
11350  BAWGBOffset(0)
11351  BAWGBFreq(0)
11352  BAWGBPhase(0)
11353  BAWGBDutyCycle(0)
11354 
11355  if AWGBFreqvalue > 0.0:
11356  if AWG_2X.get() == 1:
11357  AWGBperiodvalue = int((BaseSampleRate*2)/AWGBFreqvalue)
11358  if AWGBperiodvalue % 2 != 0: # make sure record length is even so 2X mode works for all Freq
11359  AWGBperiodvalue = AWGBperiodvalue + 1
11360  else:
11361  AWGBperiodvalue = BaseSampleRate/AWGBFreqvalue
11362  else:
11363  AWGBperiodvalue = 0.0
11364  if AWG_Amp_Mode.get() == 1:
11365  MaxV = (AWGBOffsetvalue * AWGB_Ext_Gain.get()) + AWGB_Ext_Offset.get() + (AWGBAmplvalue * AWGB_Ext_Gain.get())
11366  MinV = (AWGBOffsetvalue * AWGB_Ext_Gain.get()) + AWGB_Ext_Offset.get() - (AWGBAmplvalue * AWGB_Ext_Gain.get())
11367  else:
11368  MaxV = AWGBOffsetvalue
11369  MinV = AWGBAmplvalue
11370 
11371  if AWGBPhaseDelay.get() == 0:
11372  if AWGBPhasevalue > 0:
11373  AWGBdelayvalue = AWGBperiodvalue * AWGBPhasevalue / 360.0
11374  else:
11375  AWGBdelayvalue = 0.0
11376  elif AWGBPhaseDelay.get() == 1:
11377  AWGBdelayvalue = AWGBPhasevalue * SampleRate / 1000
11378 
11379  Cycles = int(AWGBDutyCyclevalue*100)
11380  NCycles = -1 * Cycles
11381  AWGBwaveform = []
11382  AWGBwaveform = numpy.sinc(numpy.linspace(NCycles, Cycles, SAMPLErate/AWGBFreqvalue))
11383  amplitude = (MaxV-MinV) / 2.0
11384  offset = (MaxV+MinV) / 2.0
11385  AWGBwaveform = (AWGBwaveform * amplitude) + offset # scale and offset the waveform
11386  Cycles = int(37500/AWGBperiodvalue)
11387  if Cycles < 1:
11388  Cycles = 1
11389  if Cycles > 1:
11390  Extend = int((Cycles-1.0)*AWGBperiodvalue/2.0)
11391  AWGBwaveform = numpy.pad(AWGBwaveform, (Extend,Extend), 'wrap')
11392  AWGBwaveform = numpy.roll(AWGBwaveform, int(AWGBdelayvalue))
11393  SplitAWGBwaveform()
11394  duty2lab.config(text="Cycles")
11395  BAWGBPhaseDelay()

11398 def AWGBMakeSSQ():
11399  global AWGBwaveform, AWGBAmplvalue, AWGBOffsetvalue, AWGBLength, AWGBPhaseDelay
11400  global AWGBFreqvalue, AWGBperiodvalue, AWGSAMPLErate, AWGBDutyCyclevalue, AWGBPhasevalue
11401  global AWG_Amp_Mode # 0 = Min/Max mode, 1 = Amp/Offset
11402  global AWGBBurstFlag, AWGBCycles, AWGBBurstDelay
11403  global AWGB2X, AWG_2X, SAMPLErate, BaseSampleRate
11404  global AWGA_Ext_Gain, AWGA_Ext_Offset, AWGB_Ext_Gain, AWGB_Ext_Offset
11405 
11406  BAWGBAmpl(0)
11407  BAWGBOffset(0)
11408  BAWGBFreq(0)
11409  BAWGBPhase(0)
11410  BAWGBDutyCycle(0)
11411 
11412  if AWGBFreqvalue > 0.0:
11413  if AWG_2X.get() == 2:
11414  AWGBperiodvalue = (BaseSampleRate*2)/AWGBFreqvalue
11415  SamplesPermS = int((BaseSampleRate*2)/1000) # 200
11416  else:
11417  AWGBperiodvalue = BaseSampleRate/AWGBFreqvalue
11418  SamplesPermS = int(BaseSampleRate/1000) # 100
11419  else:
11420  AWGBperiodvalue = 0.0
11421  if AWG_Amp_Mode.get() == 1:
11422  MaxV = (AWGBOffsetvalue * AWGB_Ext_Gain.get()) + AWGB_Ext_Offset.get() + (AWGBAmplvalue * AWGB_Ext_Gain.get())
11423  MinV = (AWGBOffsetvalue * AWGB_Ext_Gain.get()) + AWGB_Ext_Offset.get() - (AWGBAmplvalue * AWGB_Ext_Gain.get())
11424  else:
11425  MaxV = AWGBOffsetvalue
11426  MinV = AWGBAmplvalue
11427  AWGBwaveform = []
11428  SlopeValue = int(AWGBPhasevalue*SamplesPermS)
11429  if SlopeValue <= 0:
11430  SlopeValue = 1
11431  PulseWidth = int(AWGBperiodvalue * AWGBDutyCyclevalue)
11432  if PulseWidth <=0:
11433  PulseWidth = 1
11434  Remainder = int((AWGBperiodvalue - PulseWidth - SlopeValue)/2)
11435  if Remainder <= 0:
11436  Remainder = 1
11437  PulseWidth = PulseWidth - SlopeValue
11438  if PulseWidth <=0:
11439  PulseWidth = 1
11440  StepAmp = (MaxV - MinV)/2
11441  StepOff = (MaxV + MinV)/2
11442  AWGBwaveform = StepAmp * (numpy.cos(numpy.linspace(0, 2*numpy.pi, SlopeValue*2))) + StepOff
11443  MidArray = numpy.ones(PulseWidth) * MinV
11444  AWGBwaveform = numpy.insert(AWGBwaveform, SlopeValue, MidArray)
11445  AWGBwaveform = numpy.pad(AWGBwaveform, (Remainder, Remainder), 'edge')
11446  if AWGBBurstFlag.get() == 1:
11447  TempOneCycle = AWGBwaveform
11448  for i in range(AWGBCycles-1):
11449  AWGBwaveform = numpy.concatenate((AWGBwaveform, TempOneCycle))
11450  TempDelay = int(AWGBBurstDelay*SamplesPermS) # convert mS to samples
11451  AWGBwaveform = numpy.pad(AWGBwaveform, (TempDelay, 0), 'edge')
11452  SplitAWGBwaveform()
11453  duty2lab.config(text="%")
11454  phaseblab.config(text = "Rise Time")
11455  UpdateAwgCont()

11668  if AWGBFreqvalue > 0.0:

11721 def AWGBMakeImpulse():

11734 
11735  if AWGBFreqvalue > 0.0:
11736  if AWG_2X.get() == 2:
11737  AWGBperiodvalue = (BaseSampleRate*2)/AWGBFreqvalue
11738  SamplesPermS = int((BaseSampleRate*2)/1000) # 200
11739  else:
11740  AWGBperiodvalue = BaseSampleRate/AWGBFreqvalue
11741  SamplesPermS = int(BaseSampleRate/1000) # 100
11742  else:
11743  AWGBperiodvalue = 0.0
11744  if AWG_Amp_Mode.get() == 1:
11745  MaxV = (AWGBOffsetvalue * AWGB_Ext_Gain.get()) + AWGB_Ext_Offset.get() + (AWGBAmplvalue * AWGB_Ext_Gain.get())
11746  MinV = (AWGBOffsetvalue * AWGB_Ext_Gain.get()) + AWGB_Ext_Offset.get() - (AWGBAmplvalue * AWGB_Ext_Gain.get())
11747  else:
11748  MaxV = AWGBOffsetvalue
11749  MinV = AWGBAmplvalue
11750  AWGBwaveform = []
11751  PulseWidth = int(AWGBperiodvalue * AWGBDutyCyclevalue / 2)
11752  if AWGBPhaseDelay.get() == 0:
11753  DelayValue = int(AWGBperiodvalue*(AWGBPhasevalue/360))
11754  elif AWGBPhaseDelay.get() == 1:
11755  DelayValue = int(AWGBPhasevalue*SamplesPermS)
11756  for i in range(DelayValue-PulseWidth):
11757  AWGBwaveform.append((MinV+MaxV)/2)
11758  for i in range(PulseWidth):
11759  AWGBwaveform.append(MaxV)
11760  for i in range(PulseWidth):
11761  AWGBwaveform.append(MinV)
11762  DelayValue = int(AWGBperiodvalue-DelayValue)
11763  for i in range(DelayValue-PulseWidth):
11764  AWGBwaveform.append((MinV+MaxV)/2)
11765  if AWGBBurstFlag.get() == 1:
11766  TempOneCycle = AWGBwaveform
11767  for i in range(AWGBCycles-1):
11768  AWGBwaveform = numpy.concatenate((AWGBwaveform, TempOneCycle))
11769  TempDelay = int(AWGBBurstDelay*SamplesPermS) # convert mS to samples
11770  AWGBwaveform = numpy.pad(AWGBwaveform, (TempDelay, 0), 'edge')
11771  SplitAWGBwaveform()
11772  duty2lab.config(text = "Duty Cycle")
11773  BAWGBPhaseDelay()
11774  UpdateAwgCont()
11775

11794  else:

11797  if AWGBAmplvalue > AWGBOffsetvalue:

11799  MaxV = AWGBAmplvalue

11801  MaxV = AWGBOffsetvalue

11819 def AWGBMakeUGNoise():

11830  if AWGBFreqvalue > 0.0:
11831  if AWG_2X.get() == 2:
11832  AWGBperiodvalue = (BaseSampleRate*2)/AWGBFreqvalue
11833  SamplesPermS = int((BaseSampleRate*2)/1000) # 200
11834  else:
11835  AWGBperiodvalue = BaseSampleRate/AWGBFreqvalue
11836  SamplesPermS = int(BaseSampleRate/1000) # 100
11837  else:

11841  MaxV = AWGBAmplvalue

11844  MinV = AWGBAmplvalue

11882 def UpdateAWGB():
11883  global AWGBAmplvalue, AWGBOffsetvalue, AWGA2X, AWG_2X
11884  global AWGBFreqvalue, AWGBPhasevalue, AWGBPhaseDelay
11885  global AWGBDutyCyclevalue, FSweepMode, AWGBRepeatFlag, AWGSync
11886  global AWGBWave, AWGBMode, AWGBTerm, AWGBwaveform, AWGBIOMode
11887  global CHA, CHB, AWGSAMPLErate, DevID, devx, HWRevOne
11888  global amp2lab, off2lab, AWG_Amp_Mode # 0 = Min/Max mode, 1 = Amp/Offset
11889  global AWGA2X, AWGB2X, AWGAWave, AWGARepeatFlag
11890  global AWGA_Ext_Gain, AWGA_Ext_Offset, AWGB_Ext_Gain, AWGB_Ext_Offset
11891 
11892  if AWG_Amp_Mode.get() == 0: # 0 = Min/Max mode, 1 = Amp/Offset
11893  amp2lab.config(text = "Min Ch B" ) # change displayed value
11894  off2lab.config(text = "Max Ch B" ) # change displayed value
11895  else:
11896  amp2lab.config(text = "Amp Ch B" )
11897  off2lab.config(text = "Off Ch B" )
11898 #
11899  if AWG_2X.get() == 1:
11900  AWGBWave = 'arbitrary'
11901  if AWGBFreqvalue > 0.0:
11902  AWGBperiodvalue = AWGSAMPLErate/AWGBFreqvalue
11903  else:
11904  AWGBperiodvalue = 0.0
11905 #
11906  if AWGBPhaseDelay.get() == 0:
11907  if AWGBWave == 'square':
11908  AWGBPhasevalue = AWGBPhasevalue + 270.0
11909  if AWGBPhasevalue > 359:
11910  AWGBPhasevalue = AWGBPhasevalue - 360
11911  if AWGBPhasevalue > 0:
11912  AWGBdelayvalue = AWGBperiodvalue * AWGBPhasevalue / 360.0
11913  else:
11914  AWGBdelayvalue = 0.0
11915  elif AWGBPhaseDelay.get() == 1:
11916  AWGBdelayvalue = AWGBPhasevalue * 100
11917 #
11918  if AWGBTerm.get() == 0: # Open termination
11919  devx.ctrl_transfer( 0x40, 0x51, 37, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set 2.5 V switch to open
11920  devx.ctrl_transfer( 0x40, 0x51, 38, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set GND switch to open
11921  elif AWGBTerm.get() == 1: # 50 Ohm termination to GND
11922  devx.ctrl_transfer( 0x40, 0x51, 37, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set 2.5 V switch to open
11923  devx.ctrl_transfer( 0x40, 0x50, 38, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set GND switch to closed
11924  elif AWGBTerm.get() == 2: # 50 Ohm termination to +2.5 Volts
11925  devx.ctrl_transfer( 0x40, 0x50, 37, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set 2.5 V switch to closed
11926  devx.ctrl_transfer( 0x40, 0x51, 38, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set GND switch to open
11927 
11928  if AWGBWave == 'dc':
11929  if AWG_2X.get() == 1:
11930  AWGBWave == 'arbitrary'
11931  CHB.arbitrary(AWGA2X, AWGARepeatFlag.get())
11932  else:
11933  if AWGBMode.get() == 0: # Source Voltage measure current mode
11934  if AWGBIOMode.get() == 0:
11935  CHB.mode = Mode.SVMI # Put CHB in SVMI mode
11936  else:
11937  CHB.mode = Mode.SVMI_SPLIT # Put CHB in SVMI split mode
11938  CHB.constant(AWGBOffsetvalue)
11939  if AWGBMode.get() == 1: # Source current measure Voltage mode
11940  if AWGBIOMode.get() == 0:
11941  CHB.mode = Mode.SIMV # Put CHB in SIMV mode
11942  else:
11943  CHB.mode = Mode.SIMV_SPLIT # Put CHB in SIMV split mode
11944  CHB.constant(AWGBOffsetvalue/1000)
11945  if AWGBMode.get() == 2: # Hi impedance mode
11946  if AWGBIOMode.get() == 0:
11947  CHB.mode = Mode.HI_Z # Put CHB in Hi Z mode
11948  else:
11949  CHB.mode = Mode.HI_Z_SPLIT # Put CHB in Hi Z split mode
11950 #
11951  if AWGBIOMode.get() > 0: # Split Input / Output mode
11952  if HWRevOne == "D":
11953  AWGBMode.set(1)
11954  CHB.mode = Mode.SIMV_SPLIT # channel must be in source current mode
11955 #
11956  else:
11957  if AWGBMode.get() == 0: # Source Voltage measure current mode
11958  if AWGBIOMode.get() == 0:
11959  CHB.mode = Mode.SVMI # Put CHB in SVMI mode
11960  else:
11961  CHB.mode = Mode.SVMI_SPLIT # Put CHB in SVMI split mode
11962  if AWGBMode.get() == 1: # Source current measure Voltage mode
11963  if AWGBIOMode.get() == 0:
11964  CHB.mode = Mode.SIMV # Put CHB in SIMV mode
11965  else:
11966  CHB.mode = Mode.SIMV_SPLIT # Put CHB in SIMV split mode
11967  AWGBOffsetvalue = AWGBOffsetvalue/1000
11968  AWGBAmplvalue = AWGBAmplvalue/1000
11969  if AWGBMode.get() == 2: # Hi impedance mode
11970  if AWGBIOMode.get() == 0:
11971  CHB.mode = Mode.HI_Z # Put CHB in Hi Z mode
11972  else:
11973  CHB.mode = Mode.HI_Z_SPLIT # Put CHB in Hi Z split mode
11974  else:
11975  if AWG_Amp_Mode.get() == 1:
11976  MaxV = (AWGBOffsetvalue * AWGB_Ext_Gain.get()) + AWGB_Ext_Offset.get() + (AWGBAmplvalue * AWGB_Ext_Gain.get())
11977  MinV = (AWGBOffsetvalue * AWGB_Ext_Gain.get()) + AWGB_Ext_Offset.get() - (AWGBAmplvalue * AWGB_Ext_Gain.get())
11978  else:
11979  MaxV = AWGBOffsetvalue
11980  MinV = AWGBAmplvalue
11981  try: # keep going even if low level library returns an error
11982  if AWGBWave == 'sine':
11983  CHB.sine(MaxV, MinV, AWGBperiodvalue, AWGBdelayvalue)
11984  elif AWGBWave == 'triangle':
11985  CHB.triangle(MaxV, MinV, AWGBperiodvalue, AWGBdelayvalue)
11986  elif AWGBWave == 'sawtooth':
11987  CHB.sawtooth(MaxV, MinV, AWGBperiodvalue, AWGBdelayvalue)
11988  elif AWGBWave == 'square':
11989  CHB.square(MaxV, MinV, AWGBperiodvalue, AWGBdelayvalue, AWGBDutyCyclevalue)
11990  elif AWGBWave == 'stairstep':
11991  CHB.stairstep(MaxV, MinV, AWGBperiodvalue, AWGBdelayvalue)
11992  elif AWGBWave == 'arbitrary':
11993  if AWGSync.get() == 0:
11994  AWGBRepeatFlag.set(1)
11995  if AWG_2X.get() == 1:
11996  AWGBWave == 'arbitrary'
11997  CHB.arbitrary(AWGA2X, AWGARepeatFlag.get())
11998  else:
11999  CHB.arbitrary(AWGBwaveform, AWGBRepeatFlag.get()) # set repeat flag
12000  except:
12001  donothing()
12002  if AWGBIOMode.get() > 0: # Split Input / Output mode
12003  if HWRevOne == "D":
12004  AWGBMode.set(1)
12005  CHB.mode = Mode.SIMV_SPLIT # channel must be in source current mode
12006 #
12007 def UpdateAwgCont():
12008  global session, CHA, CHB, AWGSync
12009  # if running and in continuous streaming mode temp stop, flush buffer and restart to change AWG settings
12010  if (RUNstatus.get() == 1) and AWGSync.get() == 0:
12011  if session.continuous:
12012  session.end()
12013  BAWGEnab() # set-up new AWG settings
12014  time.sleep(0.01) # wait awhile here for some reason
12015  session.start(0)

12041 def BAWGSync():

12043 
12044  if (RUNstatus.get() == 1): # do this only if running
12045  if IAScreenStatus.get() > 0 and IADisp.get() > 0:
12046  AWGSync.set(1)
12047  return
12048  if AWGSync.get() == 0:
12049  #UpdateAwgCont()
12050  session.flush()
12051  CHA.mode = Mode.HI_Z_SPLIT # Put CHA in Hi Z mode
12052  CHB.mode = Mode.HI_Z_SPLIT # Put CHB in Hi Z mode
12053  BAWGEnab()
12054  session.start(0)
12055  time.sleep(0.02) # wait awhile here for some reason
12056  elif session.continuous:
12057  session.end()
12058  session.flush()
12059  CHA.mode = Mode.HI_Z_SPLIT # Put CHA in Hi Z mode
12060  CHB.mode = Mode.HI_Z_SPLIT # Put CHB in Hi Z mode

12214 def BCSVfile(): # Store the trace as CSV file [frequency, magnitude or dB value]
12215  global FSweepAdB, FSweepBdB, FSweepAPh, FSweepBPh, FStep, FBins, bodewindow

12220  TRACEsize = len(FSweepAdB) # Set the trace length
12221  elif ShowCA_VdB.get() == 1:
12222  TRACEsize = len(FSweepBdB)
12223  if TRACEsize == 0: # If no trace, skip rest of this routine
12224  return()
12225 # ask if save as magnitude or dB
12226  dB = askyesno("Mag or dB: ","Save amplidude data as dB (Yes) or Mag (No):\n", parent=bodewindow)
12227 # Yes 1 = dB, No 0 = Mag
12228  # Make the file name and open it
12229  tme = strftime("%Y%b%d-%H%M%S", gmtime()) # The time
12230  filename = "Bode-" + tme
12231  filename = filename + ".csv"
12232  # open file to save data
12233  filename = asksaveasfilename(initialfile = filename, defaultextension = ".csv",
12234  filetypes=[("Comma Separated Values", "*.csv")], parent=bodewindow)
12235  DataFile = open(filename,'a') # Open output file
12236  HeaderString = 'Frequency-#, '
12237  if ShowCA_VdB.get() == 1:
12238  if dB == 1:
12239  HeaderString = HeaderString + 'CA-dB, '
12240  if dB == 0:
12241  HeaderString = HeaderString + 'CA-Mag, '
12242  if ShowCB_VdB.get() == 1:
12243  if dB == 1:
12244  HeaderString = HeaderString + 'CB-dB, '
12245  if dB == 0:
12246  HeaderString = HeaderString + 'CB-Mag, '
12247  if ShowCA_P.get() == 1:
12248  HeaderString = HeaderString + 'Phase A-B, '
12249  if ShowCB_P.get() == 1:
12250  HeaderString = HeaderString + 'Phase B-A, '
12251  HeaderString = HeaderString + '\n'
12252  DataFile.write( HeaderString )
12253 
12254  n = 0
12255  while n < len(FSweepAdB):
12256  F = FBins[FStep[n]] # look up frequency bin in list of bins
12257  txt = str(F)
12258  if ShowCA_VdB.get() == 1:
12259  V = 10 * math.log10(float(FSweepAdB[n])) + 17 # Add 17 dB for max value of +10 dB
12260  if dB == 0:
12261  V = 10.0**(V/20.0)
12262  txt = txt + "," + str(V)
12263  if ShowCB_VdB.get() == 1:
12264  V = 10 * math.log10(float(FSweepBdB[n])) + 17 # Add 17 dB for max value of +10 dB
12265  if dB == 0:
12266  V = 10.0**(V/20.0)
12267  txt = txt + "," + str(V)
12268  if ShowCA_P.get() == 1:
12269  RelPhase = FSweepAPh[n]#-FSweepBPh[n]
12270  if RelPhase > 180:
12271  RelPhase = RelPhase - 360
12272  elif RelPhase < -180:
12273  RelPhase = RelPhase + 360
12274  txt = txt + "," + str(RelPhase)
12275  if ShowCB_P.get() == 1:
12276  RelPhase = FSweepBPh[n]#-FSweepAPh[n]
12277  if RelPhase > 180:
12278  RelPhase = RelPhase - 360
12279  elif RelPhase < -180:
12280  RelPhase = RelPhase + 360
12281  txt = txt + "," + str(RelPhase)
12282  txt = txt + "\n"
12283  DataFile.write(txt)
12284  n = n + 1
12285 
12286  DataFile.close() # Close the file
12287

12484 def BStartBP():
12485  global RUNstatus, LoopNum, PowerStatus, devx, PwrBt, bodewindow, session, AWGSync
12486  global ShowCA_VdB, ShowCB_P, ShowCB_VdB, ShowCB_P, ShowMathBP, contloop, discontloop
12487  global FBins, FStep, NSteps, FSweepMode, HScaleBP, CutDC
12488  global AWGAMode, AWGAShape, AWGBMode, AWGBShape
12489  global StartBodeEntry, StopBodeEntry, SweepStepBodeEntry, DevID, FWRevOne
12490  global AWGAFreqEntry, AWGBFreqEntry, Reset_Freq, AWGAIOMode, AWGBIOMode
12491  global Two_X_Sample, ADC_Mux_Mode, AWG_2X, ZEROstuffing, SAMPLErate
12492  global BeginIndex, EndIndex
12493 
12494  if DevID == "No Device":
12495  showwarning("WARNING","No Device Plugged In!")
12496  elif FWRevOne == 0.0:
12497  showwarning("WARNING","Out of data Firmware!")
12498  else:
12499  if PowerStatus == 0:
12500  PowerStatus = 1
12501  PwrBt.config(style="Pwr.TButton",text="PWR-On")
12502  devx.ctrl_transfer( 0x40, 0x51, 49, 0, 0, 0, 100) # turn on analog power
12503 
12504  if ShowCA_VdB.get() == 0 and ShowCB_VdB.get() == 0 and ShowMathBP.get() == 0:
12505  showwarning("WARNING","Select at least one trace first", parent=bodewindow)
12506  return()
12507  #
12508  if ZEROstuffing.get() < 3:
12509  ZEROstuffing.set(3)
12510  CutDC.set(1) # set to remove DC
12511  try:
12512  EndFreq = float(StopBodeEntry.get())
12513  except:
12514  StopBodeEntry.delete(0,"end")
12515  StopBodeEntry.insert(0,10000)
12516  EndFreq = 10000
12517  if FWRevOne > 2.16:
12518  if EndFreq >= 20000:
12519  Two_X_Sample.set(1)
12520  FBins = numpy.linspace(0, 100000, num=16384)
12521  else:
12522  Two_X_Sample.set(0)
12523  FBins = numpy.linspace(0, 50000, num=16384)
12524  ADC_Mux_Mode.set(0)
12525  SetADC_Mux()
12526  try:
12527  BeginFreq = float(StartBodeEntry.get())
12528  except:
12529  StartBodeEntry.delete(0,"end")
12530  StartBodeEntry.insert(0,100)
12531  BeginFreq = 100
12532  #
12533  if FSweepMode.get() == 1:
12534  if AWGAMode.get() == 2:
12535  AWGAMode.set(0) # Set AWG A to SVMI
12536  AWGAShape.set(18) # Set Shape to Sine
12537  if Two_X_Sample.get() == 1:
12538  AWGBIOMode.set(1)
12539  AWGBMode.set(0)
12540  else:
12541  AWGBMode.set(2) # Set AWG B to Hi-Z
12542  AWG_2X.set(0)
12543  BAWG2X()
12544  Reset_Freq = AWGAFreqEntry.get()
12545  if FSweepMode.get() == 2:
12546  if AWGBMode.get() == 2:
12547  AWGBMode.set(0) # Set AWG B to SVMI
12548  AWGBShape.set(18) # Set Shape to Sine
12549  if Two_X_Sample.get() == 1:
12550  AWGAIOMode.set(1)
12551  AWGAMode.set(0)
12552  else:
12553  AWGAMode.set(2) # Set AWG A to Hi-Z
12554  AWG_2X.set(0)
12555  BAWG2X()
12556  Reset_Freq = AWGBFreqEntry.get()
12557  if FSweepMode.get() == 3: # using external Minigen
12558  AWGAMode.set(2) # Set AWG A to Hi-Z
12559  AWGBMode.set(2) # Set AWG B to Hi-Z
12560  try:
12561  NSteps.set(float(SweepStepBodeEntry.get()))
12562  except:
12563  SweepStepBodeEntry.delete(0,"end")
12564  SweepStepBodeEntry.insert(0, NSteps.get())
12565  #
12566  if FSweepMode.get() > 0:
12567  BAWGAModeLabel() # make sure AWG screen labels reflect any changes to the modes
12568  BAWGBModeLabel()
12569  LoopNum.set(1)
12570  NyquistFreq = SAMPLErate/2
12571  BeginIndex = int((BeginFreq/NyquistFreq)*16384)
12572  EndIndex = int((EndFreq/NyquistFreq)*16384)
12573  if NSteps.get() < 5:
12574  NSteps.set(5)
12575  if HScaleBP.get() == 1:
12576  LogFStop = math.log10(EndIndex)
12577  try:
12578  LogFStart = math.log10(BeginIndex)
12579  except:
12580  LogFStart = 1.0
12581  FStep = numpy.logspace(LogFStart, LogFStop, num=NSteps.get(), base=10.0)
12582  else:
12583  FStep = numpy.linspace(BeginIndex, EndIndex, num=NSteps.get())
12584  BStart()
12585  # UpdateBodeAll() # Always Update

12714 
12715 def DoFFT(): # Fast Fourier transformation
12716  global FFTBuffA, FFTBuffB, AWGAwaveform, AWGBwaveform
12717  global ShowC1_VdB, ShowC1_P, ShowC2_VdB, ShowC2_P, ShowAWGASA, ShowAWGBSA
12718  global FFTmemoryA, FFTresultA, FFTresultAB, PhaseAB
12719  global FFTmemoryB, FFTresultB, FFTresultAWGA, FFTresultAWGB
12720  global FSweepAdB, FSweepBdB, FSweepAPh, FSweepBPh
12721  global PhaseA, PhaseB, PhaseMemoryA, PhaseMemoryB
12722  global FFTwindowshape, FFTbandwidth
12723  global AWGSAMPLErate, StartFreqEntry, StopFreqEntry, StartBodeEntry
12724  global SMPfft, LoopNum, IA_Ext_Conf
12725  global STARTsample, STOPsample, CutDC
12726  global TRACEaverage, FreqTraceMode, FSweepMode
12727  global TRACEresetFreq, ZEROstuffing
12728  global SpectrumScreenStatus, IAScreenStatus, BodeScreenStatus
12729  global NetworkScreenStatus, NSweepSeriesR, NSweepSeriesX, NSweepSeriesMag, NSweepSeriesAng
12730  global NSweepParallelR, NSweepParallelC, NSweepParallelL, NSweepSeriesC, NSweepSeriesL
12731 
12732  # T1 = time.time() # For time measurement of FFT routine
12733  REX = []
12734  PhaseA = []
12735  PhaseB = []
12736  # Convert list to numpy array REX for faster Numpy calculations
12737  # Take the first fft samples
12738  REX = numpy.array(FFTBuffA[0:SMPfft]) # Make a numpy arry of the list
12739 
12740  # Set Analog level display value MAX value is 5 volts for ALM1000
12741  REX = REX / 5.0
12742 
12743  # Do the FFT window function
12744  REX = REX * FFTwindowshape[0:len(REX)] # The windowing shape function only over the samples
12745 
12746  # Zero stuffing of array for better interpolation of peak level of signals
12747  ZEROstuffingvalue = int(2 ** ZEROstuffing.get())
12748  fftsamples = ZEROstuffingvalue * SMPfft # Add zero's to the arrays
12749 
12750  # Save previous trace in memory for max or average trace
12751  FFTmemoryA = FFTresultA
12752  if FreqTraceMode.get() == 3:
12753  PhaseMemoryA = PhaseA
12754 
12755  # FFT with numpy
12756  ALL = numpy.fft.fft(REX, n=fftsamples) # Do FFT + zerostuffing till n=fftsamples with NUMPY ALL = Real + Imaginary part
12757  PhaseA = numpy.angle(ALL, deg=True) # calculate angle
12758  ALL = numpy.absolute(ALL) # Make absolute SQR(REX*REX + IMX*IMX) for VOLTAGE!
12759  ALL = ALL * ALL # Convert from Voltage to Power (P = (V*V) / R; R = 1)
12760 
12761  le = int(len(ALL) / 2) # Only half is used, other half is mirror
12762  ALL = ALL[0:le] # So take only first half of the array
12763  PhaseA = PhaseA[0:le]
12764  Totalcorr = float(ZEROstuffingvalue)/ fftsamples # For VOLTAGE!
12765  Totalcorr = Totalcorr * Totalcorr # For POWER!
12766  FFTresultA = Totalcorr * ALL
12767 #
12768  REX = []
12769  # Convert list to numpy array REX for faster Numpy calculations
12770  # Take the first fft samples
12771  REX = numpy.array(FFTBuffB[0:SMPfft]) # Make a numpy arry of the list
12772 
12773  # Set level display value MAX value is 5 volts for ALM1000
12774  REX = REX / 5.0
12775 
12776  # Do the FFT window function
12777  try:
12778  REX = REX * FFTwindowshape # The windowing shape function only over the samples
12779  except:
12780  return
12781  # Zero stuffing of array for better interpolation of peak level of signals
12782  ZEROstuffingvalue = int(2 ** ZEROstuffing.get())
12783  fftsamples = ZEROstuffingvalue * SMPfft # Add zero's to the arrays
12784 
12785  # Save previous trace in memory for max or average trace
12786  FFTmemoryB = FFTresultB
12787  if FreqTraceMode.get() == 3:
12788  PhaseMemoryB = PhaseB
12789  # FFT with numpy
12790  ALL = numpy.fft.fft(REX, n=fftsamples) # Do FFT + zerostuffing till n=fftsamples with NUMPY ALL = Real + Imaginary part
12791  PhaseB = numpy.angle(ALL, deg=True) # calculate angle
12792  ALL = numpy.absolute(ALL) # Make absolute SQR(REX*REX + IMX*IMX) for VOLTAGE!
12793  ALL = ALL * ALL # Convert from Voltage to Power (P = (U*U) / R; R = 1)
12794 
12795  le = int(len(ALL) / 2 ) # Only half is used, other half is mirror
12796  ALL = ALL[0:le] # So take only first half of the array
12797  PhaseB = PhaseB[0:le]
12798  Totalcorr = float(ZEROstuffingvalue)/ fftsamples # For VOLTAGE!
12799  Totalcorr = Totalcorr * Totalcorr # For POWER!
12800  FFTresultB = Totalcorr * ALL
12801 #
12802  if IA_Ext_Conf.get() == 1: # calculate fft for voltage A-B for use if IA set to config 2
12803  REX = []

12814

13053 def MakeFreqTrace(): # Update the grid and trace
13054  global FFTmemoryA, FFTresultA
13055  global FFTmemoryB, FFTresultB
13056  global FFTresultAWGA, FFTresultAWGB, ShowAWGASA, ShowAWGBSA
13057  global PhaseA, PhaseB, PhaseMemoryA, PhaseMemoryB
13058  global FSweepAdB, FSweepBdB, FSweepAPh, FSweepBPh, FStep
13059  global ShowC1_VdB, ShowC1_P, ShowC2_VdB, ShowC2_P, ShowMathSA
13060  global PeakxA, PeakyA, PeakxB, PeakyB, PeakdbA, PeakdbB
13061  global PeakxM, PeakyM, PeakMdb, PeakfreqM, PeakIndexA, PeakIndexB
13062  global PeakfreqA, PeakfreqB, Two_X_Sample
13063  global DBdivindex # Index value
13064  global DBdivlist # dB per division list
13065  global DBlevel # Reference level
13066  global GRHF,GRWF # Screenheight, Screenwidth
13067  global AWGSAMPLErate, HScale, Fsample, SAMPLErate, BaseSampleRate
13068  global StartFreqEntry, StopFreqEntry, PhCenFreqEntry, RelPhaseCenter
13069  global STARTsample, STOPsample, LoopNum, FSweepMode
13070  global FreqTraceMode
13071  global T1Fline, T2Fline, TFMline, T1Pline, T2Pline, TAFline, TBFline
13072  global Vdiv # Number of vertical divisions
13073  global X0LF, Y0TF # Left top X value, Left top Y value
13074 
13075  # Set the TRACEsize variable
13076  TRACEsize = 0
13077  try:
13078  StartFrequency = float(StartFreqEntry.get())
13079  except:
13080  StartFreqEntry.delete(0,"end")
13081  StartFreqEntry.insert(0,100)
13082  StartFrequency = 100
13083  try:
13084  StopFrequency = float(StopFreqEntry.get())
13085  except:
13086  StopFreqEntry.delete(0,"end")
13087  StopFreqEntry.insert(0,50000)
13088  StopFrequency = 50000
13089  if StartFrequency > StopFrequency :
13090  StopFreqEntry.delete(0,"end")
13091  StopFreqEntry.insert(0,50000)
13092  StopFrequency = 50000
13093  if StopFrequency < StartFrequency :
13094  StopFreqEntry.delete(0,"end")
13095  StopFreqEntry.insert(0,50000)
13096  StopFrequency = 50000
13097  try:
13098  Phasecenter = int(PhCenFreqEntry.get())
13099  RelPhaseCenter.set(Phasecenter)
13100  except:
13101  PhCenFreqEntry.delete(0,"end")
13102  PhCenFreqEntry.insert(0,0)
13103  RelPhaseCenter.set(0)
13104  Phasecenter = 0
13105  if ShowC1_VdB.get() == 1 or ShowMathSA.get() > 0:
13106  TRACEsize = len(FFTresultA) # Set the trace length
13107  elif ShowC2_VdB.get() == 1 or ShowMathSA.get() > 0:
13108  TRACEsize = len(FFTresultB)
13109  elif ShowAWGASA.get() > 0:
13110  TRACEsize = len(FFTresultAWGA)
13111  elif ShowAWGBSA.get() > 0:
13112  TRACEsize = len(FFTresultAWGB)
13113  #print(TRACEsize)
13114  if TRACEsize == 0: # If no trace, skip rest of this routine
13115  return()
13116  if FSweepMode.get() > 0 and LoopNum.get() == NSteps.get():
13117  PhaseA = PhaseMemoryA
13118  PhaseB = PhaseMemoryB
13119  # Vertical conversion factors (level dBs) and border limits
13120  Yconv = float(GRHF) / (Vdiv.get() * DBdivlist[DBdivindex.get()]) # Conversion factors, Yconv is the number of screenpoints per dB
13121  Yc = float(Y0TF) + Yconv * (DBlevel.get()) # Yc is the 0 dBm position, can be outside the screen!
13122  Ymin = Y0TF # Minimum position of screen grid (top)
13123  Ymax = Y0TF + GRHF # Maximum position of screen grid (bottom)
13124  Yphconv = float(GRHF) / 360
13125  Yp = float(Y0TF) + Yphconv + 180
13126  # Horizontal conversion factors (frequency Hz) and border limits
13127  Fpixel = (StopFrequency - StartFrequency) / GRWF # Frequency step per screen pixel
13128  Fsample = float(SAMPLErate / 2) / (TRACEsize - 1) # Frequency step per sample
13129  LogFStop = math.log10(StopFrequency)
13130  try:
13131  LogFStart = math.log10(StartFrequency)
13132  except:
13133  LogFStart = 0.0
13134  LogFpixel = (LogFStop - LogFStart) / GRWF
13135  STARTsample = StartFrequency / Fsample # First sample in FFTresult[] that is used
13136  STARTsample = int(math.ceil(STARTsample)) # First within screen range
13137 
13138  STOPsample = StopFrequency / Fsample # Last sample in FFTresult[] that is used
13139  STOPsample = int(math.floor(STOPsample)) # Last within screen range, math.floor actually not necessary, part of int
13140 
13141  MAXsample = TRACEsize # Just an out of range check
13142  if STARTsample > (MAXsample - 1):
13143  STARTsample = MAXsample - 1
13144 
13145  if STOPsample > MAXsample:
13146  STOPsample = MAXsample
13147 
13148  T1Fline = []
13149  T2Fline = []
13150  TAFline = []
13151  TBFline = []
13152  T1Pline = []
13153  T2Pline = []
13154  TFMline = []
13155  n = STARTsample
13156  PeakIndexA = PeakIndexB = n
13157  PeakdbA = PeakdbB = PeakMdb = -200 # PeakdbB
13158  while n <= STOPsample:
13159  F = n * Fsample
13160  if HScale.get() == 1:
13161  try:
13162  LogF = math.log10(F) # convet to log Freq
13163  x = X0LF + (LogF - LogFStart)/LogFpixel
13164  except:
13165  x = X0LF
13166  else:
13167  x = X0LF + (F - StartFrequency) / Fpixel
13168  if ShowC1_VdB.get() == 1:
13169  T1Fline.append(int(x + 0.5))
13170  try:
13171  dbA = (10 * math.log10(float(FFTresultA[n])) + 17) # Convert power to DBs, except for log(0) error
13172  ya = Yc - Yconv * dbA # Add 17 dB for max value of +10 dB ALSO in CSV file routine!
13173  except:
13174  ya = Ymax
13175  if (ya < Ymin):
13176  ya = Ymin
13177  if (ya > Ymax):
13178  ya = Ymax
13179  if dbA > PeakdbA:
13180  PeakdbA = dbA
13181  PeakyA = int(ya + 0.5)
13182  PeakxA = int(x + 0.5)
13183  PeakfreqA = F
13184  PeakIndexA = n
13185  T1Fline.append(int(ya + 0.5))
13186  if ShowC2_VdB.get() == 1:
13187  T2Fline.append(int(x + 0.5))
13188  try:
13189  dbB = (10 * math.log10(float(FFTresultB[n])) + 17) # Add 17 dB for max value of +10 dB ALSO in CSV file routine!
13190  yb = Yc - Yconv * dbB
13191  except:
13192  yb = Ymax
13193  if (yb < Ymin):
13194  yb = Ymin
13195  if (yb > Ymax):
13196  yb = Ymax
13197  if dbB > PeakdbB:
13198  PeakdbB = dbB
13199  PeakyB = int(yb + 0.5)
13200  PeakxB = int(x + 0.5)
13201  PeakfreqB = F
13202  PeakIndexB = n
13203  T2Fline.append(int(yb + 0.5))
13204  if ShowAWGASA.get() > 0:
13205  TAFline.append(int(x + 0.5))
13206  try:
13207  dbA = (10 * math.log10(float(FFTresultAWGA[n])) + 17) # Convert power to DBs, except for log(0) error
13208  ya = Yc - Yconv * dbA # Add 17 dB for max value of +10 dB ALSO in CSV file routine!
13209  except:
13210  ya = Ymax
13211  if (ya < Ymin):
13212  ya = Ymin
13213  if (ya > Ymax):
13214  ya = Ymax
13215  TAFline.append(int(ya + 0.5))
13216  if ShowAWGBSA.get() > 0:
13217  TBFline.append(int(x + 0.5))
13218  try:
13219  dbA = (10 * math.log10(float(FFTresultAWGB[n])) + 17) # Convert power to DBs, except for log(0) error
13220  ya = Yc - Yconv * dbA # Add 17 dB for max value of +10 dB ALSO in CSV file routine!
13221  except:
13222  ya = Ymax
13223  if (ya < Ymin):
13224  ya = Ymin
13225  if (ya > Ymax):
13226  ya = Ymax
13227  TBFline.append(int(ya + 0.5))
13228  if ShowC1_P.get() == 1:
13229  T1Pline.append(int(x + 0.5))
13230  if FSweepMode.get() > 0:
13231  RelPhase = PhaseMemoryA[n]-PhaseMemoryB[n]
13232  else:
13233  RelPhase = PhaseA[n]-PhaseB[n]
13234  RelPhase = RelPhase - Phasecenter
13235  if RelPhase > 180:
13236  RelPhase = RelPhase - 360
13237  elif RelPhase < -180:
13238  RelPhase = RelPhase + 360
13239  if Two_X_Sample.get() == 0:
13240  PhErr = 0.0018 * n * Fsample # calculate pahse error due half sample period offset
13241  RelPhase = RelPhase + PhErr - 12.0
13242  else:
13243  RelPhase = RelPhase - 9.0
13244  ya = Yp - Yphconv * RelPhase
13245  T1Pline.append(int(ya + 0.5))
13246  if ShowC2_P.get() == 1:
13247  T2Pline.append(int(x + 0.5))
13248  if FSweepMode.get() > 0:
13249  RelPhase = PhaseMemoryB[n]-PhaseMemoryA[n]
13250  else:
13251  RelPhase = PhaseB[n]-PhaseA[n]
13252  RelPhase = RelPhase - Phasecenter
13253  if RelPhase > 180:
13254  RelPhase = RelPhase - 360
13255  elif RelPhase < -180:
13256  RelPhase = RelPhase + 360
13257  if Two_X_Sample.get() == 0:
13258  PhErr = 0.0018 * n * Fsample # calculate pahse error due half sample period offset
13259  RelPhase = RelPhase - PhErr - 12.0
13260  else:
13261  RelPhase = RelPhase - 9.0
13262  ya = Yp - Yphconv * RelPhase
13263  T2Pline.append(int(ya + 0.5))
13264  if ShowMathSA.get() > 0:
13265  TFMline.append(int(x + 0.5))
13266  dbA = (10 * math.log10(float(FFTresultA[n])) + 17) # Convert power to DBs, except for log(0) error
13267  dbB = (10 * math.log10(float(FFTresultB[n])) + 17) # Add 17 dB for max value of +10 dB ALSO in CSV file routine!
13268  if ShowMathSA.get() == 1:
13269  MdB = dbA - dbB
13270  elif ShowMathSA.get() == 2:
13271  MdB = dbB - dbA
13272  yb = Yc - Yconv * MdB
13273  if (yb < Ymin):
13274  yb = Ymin
13275  if (yb > Ymax):
13276  yb = Ymax
13277  if MdB > PeakMdb:
13278  PeakMdb = MdB
13279  PeakyM = int(yb + 0.5)
13280  PeakxM = int(x + 0.5)
13281  PeakfreqM = F
13282  TFMline.append(int(yb + 0.5))
13283  n = n + 1
13284 # make Bode Plot Traces
13285 def MakeBodeTrace(): # Update the grid and trace
13286  global FSweepAdB, FSweepBdB, FSweepAPh, FSweepBPh, FStep, FBins

13308  # Set the TRACEsize variable
13309  TRACEsize = 0
13310  if ShowCA_VdB.get() == 1 or ShowMathBP.get() > 0:
13311  TRACEsize = len(FStep) # Set the trace length
13312  elif ShowCB_VdB.get() == 1 or ShowMathBP.get() > 0:
13313  TRACEsize = len(FStep)
13314  if TRACEsize == 0: # If no trace, skip rest of this routine
13315  return()
13316  #
13317  try:
13318  EndFreq = float(StopBodeEntry.get())
13319  except:
13320  StopBodeEntry.delete(0,"end")
13321  StopBodeEntry.insert(0,10000)
13322  EndFreq = 10000
13323  try:
13324  BeginFreq = float(StartBodeEntry.get())
13325  except:
13326  StartBodeEntry.delete(0,"end")
13327  StartBodeEntry.insert(0,100)
13328  BeginFreq = 100
13329  try:
13330  Phasecenter = int(PhCenBodeEntry.get())
13331  RelPhaseCenter.set(Phasecenter)
13332  except:
13333  PhCenBodeEntry.delete(0,"end")
13334  PhCenBodeEntry.insert(0,0)
13335  RelPhaseCenter.set(0)
13336  Phasecenter = 0
13337  try:
13338  Impedcenter = int(ImCenBodeEntry.get())
13339  ImpedanceCenter.set(Impedcenter)
13340  except:
13341  ImCenBodeEntry.delete(0,"end")
13342  ImCenBodeEntry.insert(0,0)
13343  ImpedanceCenter.set(0)
13344  Impedcenter = 0
13345  #
13346  HalfSAMPLErate = SAMPLErate/2
13347  BeginIndex = int((BeginFreq/HalfSAMPLErate)*16384)
13348  EndIndex = int((EndFreq/HalfSAMPLErate)*16384)
13349  CurrentFreqX = X0LBP + 14
13350  if FSweepMode.get() > 0 and len(FSweepAdB) > 4:
13351  # Vertical conversion factors (level dBs) and border limits
13352  Yconv = float(GRHBP) / (Vdiv.get() * DBdivlist[DBdivindexBP.get()]) # Conversion factors, Yconv is the number of screenpoints per dB
13353  Yc = float(Y0TBP) + Yconv * (DBlevelBP.get()) # Yc is the 0 dBm position, can be outside the screen!
13354  Ymin = Y0TBP # Minimum position of screen grid (top)
13355  Ymax = Y0TBP + GRHBP # Maximum position of screen grid (bottom)
13356  Yphconv = float(GRHBP) / 360 # degrees per pixel
13357  Yp = float(Y0TBP) + Yphconv + 180
13358  x1 = X0LBP + 14
13359  # Horizontal conversion factors (frequency Hz) and border limits
13360  Fpixel = (EndFreq - BeginFreq) / GRWBP # Frequency step per screen pixel
13361  LogFStop = math.log10(EndFreq)
13362  try:
13363  LogFStart = math.log10(BeginFreq)
13364  except:
13365  LogFStart = 0.0
13366  LogFpixel = (LogFStop - LogFStart) / GRWBP
13367  TAFline = []
13368  TBFline = []
13369  TAPline = []
13370  TBPline = []
13371  TIARline = []
13372  TIAXline = []
13373  TIAMagline = []
13374  TIAAngline = []
13375  TBPMline = []
13376  PeakdbA = -200
13377  PeakdbB = -200
13378  PeakMdb = -200
13379  n = 0
13380  for n in range(len(FSweepAdB)): # while n < len(FStep):
13381  if n < len(FStep): # check if n has gone out off bounds because user did something dumb
13382  F = FBins[int(FStep[n])] # look up frequency bin in list of bins
13383  else:
13384  F = FBins[int(FStep[0])]
13385  if F >= BeginFreq and F <= EndFreq:
13386  if HScaleBP.get() == 1:
13387  try:
13388  LogF = math.log10(F) # convet to log Freq
13389  x = x1 + (LogF - LogFStart)/LogFpixel
13390  except:
13391  x = x1
13392  else:
13393  x = x1 + (F - BeginFreq) / Fpixel
13394  CurrentFreqX = x
13395  if ShowCA_VdB.get() == 1:
13396  TAFline.append(int(x + 0.5))
13397  try:
13398  dbA = (10 * math.log10(float(FSweepAdB[n])) + 17) # Convert power to DBs, except for log(0) error
13399  ya = Yc - Yconv * dbA # Add 17 dB for max value of +10 dB ALSO in CSV file routine!
13400  except:
13401  ya = Ymax
13402  if (ya < Ymin):
13403  ya = Ymin
13404  if (ya > Ymax):
13405  ya = Ymax
13406  if dbA > PeakdbA:
13407  PeakdbA = dbA
13408  PeakyA = int(ya + 0.5)
13409  PeakxA = int(x + 0.5)
13410  PeakfreqA = F
13411  TAFline.append(int(ya + 0.5))
13412  if ShowCB_VdB.get() == 1:
13413  TBFline.append(int(x + 0.5))
13414  try:
13415  dbB = (10 * math.log10(float(FSweepBdB[n])) + 17) # Add 17 dB for max value of +10 dB ALSO in CSV file routine!
13416  yb = Yc - Yconv * dbB
13417  except:
13418  yb = Ymax
13419  if (yb < Ymin):
13420  yb = Ymin
13421  if (yb > Ymax):
13422  yb = Ymax
13423  if dbB > PeakdbB:
13424  PeakdbB = dbB
13425  PeakyB = int(yb + 0.5)
13426  PeakxB = int(x + 0.5)
13427  PeakfreqB = F
13428  TBFline.append(int(yb + 0.5))
13429  if ShowCA_P.get() == 1:
13430  TAPline.append(int(x + 0.5))
13431  RelPhase = FSweepAPh[n] - FSweepBPh[n]
13432  RelPhase = RelPhase - Phasecenter
13433  if RelPhase > 180:
13434  RelPhase = RelPhase - 360
13435  elif RelPhase < -180:
13436  RelPhase = RelPhase + 360
13437  if Two_X_Sample.get() == 0:
13438  PhErr = 0.0018 * F # calculate phase error due half sample period offset
13439  RelPhase = RelPhase + PhErr - PhaseOffset1x
13440  else:
13441  RelPhase = RelPhase - PhaseOffset2x
13442  ya = Yp - Yphconv * RelPhase
13443  TAPline.append(int(ya + 0.5))
13444  if ShowCB_P.get() == 1:
13445  TBPline.append(int(x + 0.5))
13446  RelPhase = FSweepBPh[n] - FSweepAPh[n]
13447  RelPhase = RelPhase - Phasecenter
13448  if RelPhase > 180:
13449  RelPhase = RelPhase - 360
13450  elif RelPhase < -180:
13451  RelPhase = RelPhase + 360
13452  if Two_X_Sample.get() == 0:
13453  PhErr = 0.0018 * F # calculate phase error due half sample period offset
13454  RelPhase = RelPhase - PhErr - PhaseOffset1x
13455  else:
13456  RelPhase = RelPhase - PhaseOffset2x
13457  ya = Yp - Yphconv * RelPhase
13458  TBPline.append(int(ya + 0.5))
13459  if ShowMathBP.get() > 0:
13460  TBPMline.append(int(x + 0.5))
13461  dbA = (10 * math.log10(float(FSweepAdB[n])) + 17) # Convert power to DBs, except for log(0) error
13462  dbB = (10 * math.log10(float(FSweepBdB[n])) + 17) # Add 17 dB for max value of +10 dB ALSO in CSV file routine!
13463  if ShowMathBP.get() == 1:
13464  MdB = dbA - dbB
13465  elif ShowMathBP.get() == 2:
13466  MdB = dbB - dbA
13467  yb = Yc - Yconv * MdB
13468  if (yb < Ymin):
13469  yb = Ymin
13470  if (yb > Ymax):
13471  yb = Ymax
13472  if MdB > PeakMdb:
13473  PeakMdb = MdB
13474  PeakyM = int(yb + 0.5)
13475  PeakxM = int(x + 0.5)
13476  PeakfreqM = F
13477  TBPMline.append(int(yb + 0.5))
13478 # draw impedance trace if necessary
13479  if NetworkScreenStatus.get() > 0:
13480  ycenter = Y0TBP + (GRHBP/2)
13481  OhmsperPixel = float(ResScale.get())*Vdiv.get()/GRHBP
13482  n = 0
13483  for n in range(len(NSweepSeriesR)): # while n < len(FStep):
13484  if n < len(FStep): # check if n has gone out off bounds because user did something dumb
13485  F = FBins[int(FStep[n])] # look up frequency bin in list of bins
13486  else:
13487  F = FBins[int(FStep[0])]
13488  if F >= BeginFreq and F <= EndFreq:
13489  if HScaleBP.get() == 1:
13490  try:
13491  LogF = math.log10(F) # convet to log Freq
13492  x = x1 + (LogF - LogFStart)/LogFpixel
13493  except:
13494  x = x1
13495  else:
13496  x = x1 + (F - BeginFreq) / Fpixel
13497  if Show_Rseries.get() == 1:
13498  TIARline.append(int(x + 0.5))
13499  y1 = ycenter - ((NSweepSeriesR[n]-Impedcenter) / OhmsperPixel)
13500  if (y1 < Ymin):
13501  y1 = Ymin
13502  if (y1 > Ymax):
13503  y1 = Ymax
13504  TIARline.append(y1)
13505  if Show_Xseries.get() == 1:
13506  TIAXline.append(int(x + 0.5))
13507  y1 = ycenter - ((NSweepSeriesX[n]-Impedcenter) / OhmsperPixel)
13508  if (y1 < Ymin):
13509  y1 = Ymin
13510  if (y1 > Ymax):
13511  y1 = Ymax
13512  TIAXline.append(y1)
13513  if Show_Magnitude.get() == 1:
13514  TIAMagline.append(int(x + 0.5))
13515  y1 = ycenter - ((NSweepSeriesMag[n]-Impedcenter) / OhmsperPixel)
13516  if (y1 < Ymin):
13517  y1 = Ymin
13518  if (y1 > Ymax):
13519  y1 = Ymax
13520  TIAMagline.append(y1)
13521  if Show_Angle.get() == 1:
13522  TIAAngline.append(int(x + 0.5))
13523  y1 = ycenter - Yphconv * (NSweepSeriesAng[n]-Phasecenter)
13524  if (y1 < Ymin):
13525  y1 = Ymin
13526  if (y1 > Ymax):
13527  y1 = Ymax
13528  TIAAngline.append(y1)

13619  if NetworkScreenStatus.get() > 0:
13620  if Show_Rseries.get() == 1 or Show_Xseries.get() == 1 or Show_Magnitude.get() == 1:
13621  RperDiv = float(ResScale.get())
13622  Vaxis_value = ( (RperDiv * Vdiv.get()/2) - (i * RperDiv) ) + Impedcenter
13623  if Vaxis_value > 500 or Vaxis_value < -500:
13624  Vaxis_value = Vaxis_value/1000.0
13625  if Vaxis_value > 5 or Vaxis_value < -5:

13627  else:

13629  else:
13630  Vaxis_label = ' {0:.0f} '.format(Vaxis_value)
13631  Bodeca.create_text(x1-23, y, text=Vaxis_label, fill=COLORtrace5, anchor="e", font=("arial", FontSize ))
13632  i = i + 1

13636  y2 = Y0TBP + GRHBP

13869 #
13870 def DoImpedance():
13871 
13872 # Input Variables
13873  global PeakdbA, PeakdbB, PeakRelPhase, PeakdbAB
13874  #(VZ/VA)from vector voltmeter
13875  # global VVangle # angle in degrees between VZ and VA
13876  global RsystemEntry # resistance of series resistor or power divider
13877 # Computed outputs
13878  # global VVangleCosine # cosine of vector voltmeter angle
13879  global ImpedanceMagnitude # in ohms
13880  global ImpedanceAngle # in degrees
13881  global ImpedanceRseries, ImpedanceXseries # in ohms
13882  global IA_Ext_Conf
13883 
13884  DEG2RAD = (math.pi / 180.0)
13885  SMALL = 1E-20
13886  try:
13887  ResValue = float(RsystemEntry.get())
13888  except:
13889  ResValue = 1000.0
13890 
13891  VA = math.pow(10,(PeakdbA/20))
13892  VB = math.pow(10,(PeakdbB/20))
13893  VVangleCosine = math.cos(math.radians(PeakRelPhase))
13894  if IA_Ext_Conf.get() == 1:
13895  VAB = math.pow(10,(PeakdbAB/20))
13896  VZ = VAB # VZ=VA-VB
13897  # VI = VB
13898  else:
13899  VZ = VB # VZ=VB
13900  VI = math.sqrt(VA**2 + VZ**2 - 2*VA*VZ*VVangleCosine)
13901  costheta = (VA**2 + VI**2 - VZ**2)/(2 * VA * VI)
13902  Za = ResValue * VA / VI
13903  ImpedanceRseries = Za * costheta - ResValue
13904  ImpedanceMagnitude = ResValue * VZ / VI
13905  # don't try to take square root of a negative number)
13906  ImpedanceXseries = math.sqrt(abs(ImpedanceMagnitude**2 - ImpedanceRseries**2))
13907 
13908  if(PeakRelPhase < 0.0):
13909  ImpedanceXseries = -ImpedanceXseries
13910  if IA_Ext_Conf.get() == 1:
13911  ImpedanceRseries = -ImpedanceRseries
13912  ImpedanceAngle = math.atan2(ImpedanceXseries, ImpedanceRseries) / DEG2RAD
13913 #
13914 def MakeIATrace(): # Update the grid and trace
13915  global FFTmemoryA, FFTresultA, FFTresultAB, PhaseAB
13916  global FFTmemoryB, FFTresultB
13917  global PhaseA, PhaseB, PhaseMemoryA, PhaseMemoryB
13918  global PeakxA, PeakyA, PeakxB, PeakyB, PeakdbA, PeakdbB, PeakRelPhase, PeakdbAB
13919  global PeakxM, PeakyM, PeakMdb, PeakfreqM, PeakphaseA, PeakphaseB
13920  global PeakfreqA, PeakfreqB, GainCorEntry, PhaseCorEntry, PhaseCorrection
13921  global DBdivindex # Index value
13922  global DBdivlist # dB per division list
13923  global DBlevel # Reference level
13924  global GRHIA # Screenheight
13925  global GRWIA # Screenwidth
13926  global AWGSAMPLErate, SAMPLErate, BaseSampleRate
13927  global STARTsample, STOPsample, LoopNum, FSweepMode
13928  global TRACEmode, Two_X_Sample, IA_Ext_Conf
13929  global T1Vline, T2Vline, TMline, T1Pline, T2Pline
13930  global Vdiv # Number of vertical divisions
13931  global X0LIA # Left top X value
13932  global Y0TIA # Left top Y value
13933  global ImpedanceMagnitude # in ohms
13934  global ImpedanceAngle # in degrees
13935  global ImpedanceRseries, ImpedanceXseries # in ohms
13936 
13937  # Set the TRACEsize variable
13938  TRACEsize = len(FFTresultA) # Set the trace length
13939  Fsample = float(SAMPLErate / 2) / (TRACEsize - 1)
13940  # Horizontal conversion factors (frequency Hz) and border limits
13941  STARTsample = 0 # First sample in FFTresult[] that is used
13942  STARTsample = int(math.ceil(STARTsample)) # First within screen range
13943  if Two_X_Sample.get() == 0:
13944  STOPsample = 45000 / Fsample # Last sample in FFTresult[] that is used
13945  else:
13946  STOPsample = 90000 / Fsample
13947  STOPsample = int(math.floor(STOPsample)) # Last within screen range, math.floor actually not necessary, part of int
13948 #
13949  try:
13950  GainCorrection = float(eval(GainCorEntry.get()))
13951  except:
13952  GainCorEntry.delete(0,END)
13953  GainCorEntry.insert(0, GainCorrection)
13954 
13955  try:
13956  PhaseCorrection = float(eval(PhaseCorEntry.get()))
13957  except:
13958  PhaseCorEntry.delete(0,END)
13959  PhaseCorEntry.insert(0, PhaseCorrection)
13960 
13961  MAXsample = TRACEsize # Just an out of range check
13962  if STARTsample > (MAXsample - 1):
13963  STARTsample = MAXsample - 1
13964 
13965  if STOPsample > MAXsample:
13966  STOPsample = MAXsample
13967 
13968  n = STARTsample
13969  PeakfreqA = PeakfreqB = PeakfreqM = F = n * Fsample
13970  PeakphaseA = PhaseA[n]
13971  PeakphaseB = PhaseB[n]
13972  #PeakphaseAB = PhaseAB[n]
13973  PeakSample = n
13974 
13975  PeakdbA = (10 * math.log10(float(FFTresultA[n])) + 17)
13976  PeakdbB = (10 * math.log10(float(FFTresultB[n])) + 17)
13977  PeakMdb = PeakdbA - PeakdbB
13978  if IA_Ext_Conf.get() == 1:
13979  PeakdbAB = (10 * math.log10(float(FFTresultAB[n])) + 17)
13980  while n <= STOPsample:
13981  F = n * Fsample
13982  try:
13983  dbA = (10 * math.log10(float(FFTresultA[n])) + 17) # Convert power to DBs, except for log(0) error
13984  except:
13985  dbA = -200
13986  if dbA > PeakdbA:
13987  PeakdbA = dbA
13988  PeakfreqA = F
13989  PeakphaseA = PhaseA[n]
13990  PeakSample = n
13991 
13992  try:
13993  dbB = (10 * math.log10(float(FFTresultB[n])) + 17) # Add 17 dB for max value of +10 dB ALSO in CSV file routine!
13994  except:
13995  dbB = -200
13996  if dbB > PeakdbB:
13997  PeakdbB = dbB
13998  PeakfreqB = F
13999  PeakphaseB = PhaseB[n]
14000 
14001  if IA_Ext_Conf.get() == 1:
14002  try:
14003  dbAB = (10 * math.log10(float(FFTresultAB[n])) + 17) # Add 17 dB for max value of +10 dB ALSO in CSV file routine!
14004  except:
14005  dbAB = -200
14006  if dbAB > PeakdbAB:
14007  PeakdbAB = dbAB
14008  PeakphaseAB = PhaseAB[n]
14009  RelPhase = PhaseA[n]-PhaseB[n]
14010  if RelPhase > 180:
14011  RelPhase = RelPhase - 360
14012  elif RelPhase < -180:
14013  RelPhase = RelPhase + 360
14014  if Two_X_Sample.get() == 0:
14015  PhErr = 0.0018 * n * Fsample # calculate pahse error due half sample period offset
14016  RelPhase = RelPhase + PhErr - 12.0
14017  else:
14018  RelPhase = RelPhase - 9.0
14019  n = n + 1
14020  if IA_Ext_Conf.get() == 1:
14021  PeakRelPhase = PeakphaseAB-PeakphaseA
14022  else:
14023  PeakRelPhase = PeakphaseB-PeakphaseA
14024 #
14025  if PeakRelPhase > 180:
14026  PeakRelPhase = PeakRelPhase - 360
14027  elif PeakRelPhase < -180:
14028  PeakRelPhase = PeakRelPhase + 360
14029  if Two_X_Sample.get() == 0:
14030  PhErr = 0.0018 * PeakSample * Fsample # calculate pahse error due half sample period offset
14031  PeakRelPhase = PeakRelPhase + PhaseCorrection - PhErr # - 12
14032  else:
14033  PeakRelPhase = PeakRelPhase + PhaseCorrection
14034  PeakdbB = PeakdbB + GainCorrection
14035  DoImpedance()
14036 
14038 def MakeIAScreen(): # Update the screen with traces and text

14089  while (i <= Vdiv.get()):
14090  x0 = xcenter - ( i * Radius )
14091  x1 = xcenter + ( i * Radius )
14092  y0 = ycenter - ( i * Radius )
14093  y1 = ycenter + ( i * Radius )
14094  axisvalue = float(ResScale.get()) * i
14095  if axisvalue >= 1000.0 or axisvalue <= -1000.0:

14097  ResTxt = '{0:.1f}'.format(axisvalue)
14098  axis_label = str(ResTxt) + "K"
14099  else:
14100  ResTxt = '{0:.0f}'.format(axisvalue)
14101  axis_label = str(ResTxt)

14103  IAca.create_line(xcenter, y0, xright, y0, fill=COLORgrid, width=GridWidth.get(), dash=(4,3))

14105  #

14108  IAca.create_line(x0, ycenter, x1, ycenter, fill=COLORgrid, width=GridWidth.get())

14118  else:
14119  # Draw horizontal grid lines

14121  j = 0
14122  x1 = X0LIA
14123  x2 = X0LIA + TRadius * 2

14137  axis_label = str(ResTxt) + "K"
14138  else:
14139  ResTxt = '{0:.0f}'.format(axisvalue)
14140  axis_label = str(ResTxt)
14141  IAca.create_text(x1-3, y, text=axis_label, fill=COLORtrace6, anchor="e", font=("arial", FontSize ))
14142  i = i + 1
14143  j = j + 1
14144  # Draw vertical grid lines
14145  i = 0 - Vdiv.get()
14146  j = 0
14147  y1 = Y0TIA
14148  y2 = Y0TIA + TRadius * 2
14149  ycenter = y1 + (TRadius)
14150  # "\n".join(axis_label)
14151  while (i <= Vdiv.get()): #

14153  Dline = [x,y1,x,y2]
14154  if i == 0 or i == Vdiv.get() or i == -Vdiv.get():
14155  IAca.create_line(Dline, fill=COLORgrid, width=GridWidth.get())
14156  else:
14157  IAca.create_line(Dline, dash=(4,3), fill=COLORgrid, width=GridWidth.get())
14158  axisvalue = float(ResScale.get()) * i
14159  if axisvalue >= 1000.0 or axisvalue <= -1000.0:
14160  axisvalue = axisvalue / 1000

14162  axis_label = str(ResTxt) + "K"
14163  else:
14164  ResTxt = '{0:.0f}'.format(axisvalue)
14165  axis_label = str(ResTxt)
14166  IAca.create_text(x, y2+3, text=axis_label, fill=COLORtrace1, anchor="n", font=("arial", FontSize ))
14167  i = i + 1
14168  j = j + 1
14169 # Draw traces

14174 #
