14178  elif x1 < -500:
14179  x1 = xcenter - xright
14180  IAca.create_line(xcenter, ycenter, x1, ycenter, fill=COLORtrace1, arrow="last", width=TRACEwidth.get())
14181  y1 = ycenter - ( ImpedanceXseries / OhmsperPixel )
14182  if y1 > 1500:
14183  y1 = xright
14184  elif y1 < -500:
14185  y1 = ycenter - xright
14186  xmag = x1
14187  ymag = y1
14188  IAca.create_line(xcenter, ycenter, xcenter, y1, fill=COLORtrace6, arrow="last", width=TRACEwidth.get())
14189  MagRadius = ImpedanceMagnitude / OhmsperPixel
14190  y1 = ycenter - MagRadius*math.sin(math.radians(ImpedanceAngle))
14191  if y1 > 1500:
14192  y1 = xright
14193  elif y1 < -500:
14194  y1 = ycenter - xright
14195  x1 = xcenter + MagRadius*math.cos(math.radians(ImpedanceAngle))
14196  if x1 > 1500:
14197  x1 = xright
14198  elif x1 < -500:
14199  x1 = xcenter - xright
14200  IAca.create_line(xcenter, ycenter, x1, y1, fill=COLORtrace2, arrow="last", width=TRACEwidth.get())
14201 #
14202  TIAMline = []
14203  if len(NSweepSeriesMag) > 2:
14204  index = 0
14205  while index < len(NSweepSeriesMag):
14206  MagRadius = NSweepSeriesMag[index] / OhmsperPixel
14207  y1 = ycenter - MagRadius*math.sin(math.radians(NSweepSeriesAng[index]))
14208  if y1 > 1500:
14209  y1 = xright
14210  elif y1 < -500:
14211  y1 = ycenter - xright
14212  x1 = xcenter + MagRadius*math.cos(math.radians(NSweepSeriesAng[index]))
14213  if x1 > 1500:
14214  x1 = xright
14215  elif x1 < -500:
14216  x1 = xcenter - xright
14217  TIAMline.append(x1)
14218  TIAMline.append(y1)
14219  index = index + 1
14220  IAca.create_line(TIAMline, fill=COLORtrace5, smooth=SmoothBool, splinestep=5, width=TRACEwidth.get())
14221 # display warning if input out of range
14222  if OverRangeFlagA == 1:
14223  x = X0LIA+GRWIA+10
14224  y = Y0TIA+GRHIA-40
14225  IAca.create_rectangle(x-6, y-6, x+6, y+6, fill="#ff0000")
14226  IAca.create_text (x+12, y, text="CHA Over Range", anchor=W, fill="#ff0000", font=("arial", FontSize+4 ))
14227  if OverRangeFlagB == 1:
14228  x = X0LIA+GRWIA+10
14229  y = Y0TIA+GRHIA-10
14230  IAca.create_rectangle(x-6, y-6, x+6, y+6, fill="#ff0000")
14231  IAca.create_text (x+12, y, text="CHB Over Range", anchor=W, fill="#ff0000", font=("arial", FontSize+4 ))
14232  # General information on top of the grid
14233 
14234  txt = " Sample rate: " + str(SAMPLErate)
14235  txt = txt + " FFT samples: " + str(SMPfft)
14236 
14237  txt = txt + " " + FFTwindowname
14238 
14239  x = X0LIA
14240  y = 12
14241  idTXT = IAca.create_text (x, y, text=txt, anchor=W, fill=COLORtext)
14242  #
14243  x = X0LIA + GRWIA + 4
14244  y = 24
14245  txt = "Gain " + ' {0:.2f} '.format(PeakdbB-PeakdbA) + " dB"
14246  TXT9 = IAca.create_text (x, y, text=txt, anchor=W, fill=COLORtext, font=("arial", FontSize+6 ))
14247  y = y + 24
14248  txt = "Phase " + ' {0:.2f} '.format(PeakRelPhase) + " Degrees"
14249  TXT10 = IAca.create_text (x, y, text=txt, anchor=W, fill=COLORtext, font=("arial", FontSize+6 ))
14250  y = y + 24
14251  txt = "Freq " + ' {0:.1f} '.format(PeakfreqA) + " Hertz"
14252  TXT11 = IAca.create_text (x, y, text=txt, anchor=W, fill=COLORtext, font=("arial", FontSize+6 ))
14253  y = y + 24
14254  txt = "Impedance Magnitude"
14255  TXT1 = IAca.create_text (x, y, text=txt, anchor=W, fill=COLORtext, font=("arial", FontSize+6 ))
14256  y = y + 24
14257  txt = ' {0:.1f} '.format(ImpedanceMagnitude)
14258  TXT2 = IAca.create_text (x, y, text=txt, anchor=W, fill=COLORtext, font=("arial", FontSize+6 ))
14259  y = y + 24
14260  txt = "Impedance Angle"
14261  TXT3 = IAca.create_text (x, y, text=txt, anchor=W, fill=COLORtext, font=("arial", FontSize+6 ))
14262  y = y + 24
14263  txt = ' {0:.1f} '.format(ImpedanceAngle)
14264  TXT4 = IAca.create_text (x, y, text=txt, anchor=W, fill=COLORtext, font=("arial", FontSize+6 ))
14265  y = y + 24
14266  txt = "Impedance R series"
14267  TXT5 = IAca.create_text (x, y, text=txt, anchor=W, fill=COLORtext, font=("arial", FontSize+6 ))
14268  y = y + 24
14269  txt = ' {0:.1f} '.format(ImpedanceRseries)
14270  TXT6 = IAca.create_text (x, y, text=txt, anchor=W, fill=COLORtext, font=("arial", FontSize+6 ))
14271  y = y + 24
14272  txt = "Impedance X series"
14273  TXT7 = IAca.create_text (x, y, text=txt, anchor=W, fill=COLORtext, font=("arial", FontSize+6 ))
14274  y = y + 24
14275  txt = ' {0:.1f} '.format(ImpedanceXseries)
14276  TXT8 = IAca.create_text (x, y, text=txt, anchor=W, fill=COLORtext, font=("arial", FontSize+6 ))
14277 #
14278  Cseries = 0.0
14279  Cparallel = 0.0
14280  Lseries = 0.0
14281  Lparallel = 0.0
14282  Rparallel = 0.0
14283  if ImpedanceXseries < 0: # calculate series capacitance
14284  y = y + 24
14285  try:
14286  Cseries = -1 / ( 2 * math.pi * PeakfreqA * ImpedanceXseries ) # in farads
14287  except:
14288  Cseries = 0
14289  Qseries = 1/(2*math.pi*PeakfreqA*Cseries*ImpedanceRseries)
14290  Cparallel = Cseries * (Qseries**2 / (1+Qseries**2))
14291  Cparallel = Cparallel * 1E6 # convert to micro Farads
14292  Rparallel = ImpedanceRseries * (1+Qseries**2)
14293  Cseries = Cseries * 1E6 # convert to micro Farads
14294  if DisplaySeries.get() == 0:
14295  txt = "Series Capacitance"
14296  IAca.create_text (x, y, text=txt, anchor=W, fill=COLORtext, font=("arial", FontSize+4 ))
14297  y = y + 20
14298  if Cseries < 1:
14299  Ctext = Cseries * 1E3
14300  if Ctext < 1:
14301  Ctext = Ctext * 1E3
14302  CtextDis = Ctext + float(CapZeroEntry.get())
14303  txt = ' {0:.1f} '.format(CtextDis) + "pF"
14304  else:
14305  txt = ' {0:.3f} '.format(Ctext) + "nF"
14306  else:
14307  txt = ' {0:.3f} '.format(Cseries) + "uF"
14308  IAca.create_text (x, y, text=txt, anchor=W, fill=COLORtext, font=("arial", FontSize+4 ))
14309  else:
14310  txt = "Parallel"
14311  IAca.create_text (x, y, text=txt, anchor=W, fill=COLORtext, font=("arial", FontSize+4 ))
14312  y = y + 20
14313  if Cparallel < 1:
14314  Ctext = Cparallel * 1E3
14315  if Ctext < 1:
14316  Ctext = Ctext * 1E3
14317  txt = "Capacitance " + ' {0:.1f} '.format(Ctext) + "pF"
14318  else:
14319  txt = "Capacitance " + ' {0:.3f} '.format(Ctext) + "nF"
14320  else:
14321  txt = "Capacitance " + ' {0:.3f} '.format(Cparallel) + "uF"
14322  IAca.create_text (x, y, text=txt, anchor=W, fill=COLORtext, font=("arial", FontSize+4 ))
14323  y = y + 20
14324  txt = "Resistance" + ' {0:.1f} '.format(Rparallel) + "ohms"
14325  IAca.create_text (x, y, text=txt, anchor=W, fill=COLORtext, font=("arial", FontSize+4 ))
14326  y = y + 20
14327  dissp = abs(ImpedanceRseries/ImpedanceXseries) * 100 # Dissipation factor is ratio of XR to XC in percent
14328  txt = 'D = {0:.2f} '.format(dissp) + " %"
14329  IAca.create_text (x, y, text=txt, anchor=W, fill=COLORtext, font=("arial", FontSize+4 ))
14330 
14331  elif ImpedanceXseries > 0: # calculate series inductance
14332  y = y + 24
14333  try:
14334  Lseries = ImpedanceXseries / ( 2 * 3.14159 * PeakfreqA ) # in henry
14335  except:
14336  Lseries = 0
14337  Qseries = (2*math.pi*PeakfreqA*Lseries)/ImpedanceRseries
14338  if Qseries == 0.0: # Check if divide by zero
14339  Qseries = 0.00001
14340  Lparallel = Lseries * ((1+Qseries**2) / Qseries**2)
14341  Lparallel = Lparallel * 1E3 # convert to millihenry
14342  Rparallel = ImpedanceRseries * (1+Qseries**2)
14343  Lseries = Lseries * 1E3 # in millihenry
14344  if DisplaySeries.get() == 0:
14345  txt = "Series Inductance"
14346  IAca.create_text (x, y, text=txt, anchor=W, fill=COLORtext, font=("arial", FontSize+4 ))
14347  y = y + 22
14348  if Lseries < 1:
14349  Ltext = Lseries * 1E3
14350  txt = ' {0:.2f} '.format(Ltext) + "uH"
14351  else:
14352  txt = ' {0:.2f} '.format(Lseries) + "mH"
14353  IAca.create_text(x, y, text=txt, anchor=W, fill=COLORtext, font=("arial", FontSize+4 ))
14354  else:
14355  txt = "Parallel"
14356  IAca.create_text (x, y, text=txt, anchor=W, fill=COLORtext, font=("arial", FontSize+4 ))
14357  y = y + 20
14358  if Lparallel < 1:
14359  Ltext = Lparallel * 1E3
14360  txt = "Inductance " + ' {0:.2f} '.format(Ltext) + "uH"
14361  else:
14362  txt = "Inductance " + ' {0:.2f} '.format(Lparallel) + "mH"
14363  IAca.create_text(x, y, text=txt, anchor=W, fill=COLORtext, font=("arial", FontSize+4 ))
14364  y = y + 20
14365  txt = "Resistance" + ' {0:.1f} '.format(Rparallel) + "ohms"
14366  IAca.create_text (x, y, text=txt, anchor=W, fill=COLORtext, font=("arial", FontSize+4 ))
14367  y = y + 20
14368  qf = abs(ImpedanceXseries/ImpedanceRseries) * 100 # Quality Factor is ratio of XL to XR
14369  txt = 'Q = {0:.2f} '.format(qf)
14370  IAca.create_text (x, y, text=txt, anchor=W, fill=COLORtext, font=("arial", FontSize+4 ))
14371  #
14372  if LoopNum.get() > 1:
14373  if NetworkScreenStatus.get() > 0:
14374  NSweepSeriesR.append(ImpedanceRseries)
14375  NSweepSeriesX.append(ImpedanceXseries)
14376  NSweepSeriesMag.append(ImpedanceMagnitude) # in ohms
14377  NSweepSeriesAng.append(ImpedanceAngle) # in degrees
14378  NSweepParallelR.append(Rparallel)
14379  NSweepParallelC.append(Cparallel) # in uF
14380  NSweepParallelL.append(Lparallel) # in mH
14381  NSweepSeriesC.append(Cseries) # in uF
14382  NSweepSeriesL.append(Lseries) # in mH
14383  # Start and stop frequency and trace mode
14384  if Two_X_Sample.get() == 0:
14385  txt = "0.0 to 45000 Hz"
14386  else:
14387  txt = "0.0 to 90000 Hz"
14388  txt = txt + " FFT Bandwidth =" + ' {0:.2f} '.format(FFTbandwidth)
14389 
14390  x = X0LIA
14391  y = Y0TIA+GRHIA-13
14392  idTXT = IAca.create_text (x, y, text=txt, anchor=W, fill=COLORtext)
14393  txt = " "
14394  if FreqTraceMode.get() == 1:
14395  txt ="Normal mode "
14396 
14397  if FreqTraceMode.get() == 2:
14398  txt = "Peak hold mode "
14399 
14400  if FreqTraceMode.get() == 3:
14401  txt = "Power average mode (" + str(TRACEaverage.get()) + ") "
14402 
14403  if ZEROstuffing.get() > 0:
14404  txt = txt + "Zero Stuffing = " + str(ZEROstuffing.get())
14405  # Runstatus and level information
14406  if (RUNstatus.get() == 0):
14407  txt = txt + " Stopped "
14408  else:
14409  txt = txt + " Running "
14410  y = Y0TIA+GRHIA
14411  IDtxt = IAca.create_text (x, y, text=txt, anchor=W, fill=COLORtext)

14677 def NqPCaresize(event):
14678  global NqPca, GRWNqP, XOLNqP, GRHNqP, Y0TNqP, CANVASwidthNqP, CANVASheightNqP, FontSize
14679 
14680  CANVASwidthNqP = event.width - 4
14681  CANVASheightNqP = event.height - 4
14682  GRWNqP = CANVASwidthNqP - (2 * X0LNqP) # new grid width
14683  GRHNqP = CANVASheightNqP - Y0TNqP - int(1.25 * FontSize) # 10 new grid height
14684  UpdateNqPAll()
14685 
14687 def MakeNqPScreen():
14688  global NqPca, GRWNqP, XOLNqP, GRHNqP, Y0TNqP, CANVASwidthNqP, CANVASheightNqP, COLORtrace1
14689  global COLORgrid, GridWidth, SmoothCurvesBP, SmoothBool, DBlevelBP, DBdivlist, DBdivindexBP
14690  global FSweepAdB, FSweepBdB, FSweepBPh, FSweepAPh, ShowMathBP, NqPline, Two_X_Sample, TRACEwidth
14691  global Vdiv, FBins, FStep
14692  global FontSize
14693 
14694  # Delete all items on the canvas
14695  NqPca.delete(ALL) # remove all items
14696  SmoothBool = SmoothCurvesBP.get()
14697  # Draw circular grid lines
14698  i = 1
14699  xcenter = GRWNqP/2
14700  ycenter = GRHNqP/2
14701  Radius = (GRWNqP-X0LNqP)/(1 + Vdiv.get() * 2) # 11
14702  dBperPixel = float(DBdivlist[DBdivindexBP.get()])/Radius
14703  TRadius = Radius * Vdiv.get() # 5
14704  x1 = X0LNqP
14705  x2 = X0LNqP + GRWNqP
14706  xright = 10 + xcenter + ( Vdiv.get() * Radius ) # 5
14707  while (i <= Vdiv.get()):
14708  x0 = xcenter - ( i * Radius )
14709  x1 = xcenter + ( i * Radius )
14710  y0 = ycenter - ( i * Radius )
14711  y1 = ycenter + ( i * Radius )
14712  dBaxis_value = (DBlevelBP.get() - (i * DBdivlist[DBdivindexBP.get()]))
14713  NqPca.create_oval( x0, y0, x1, y1, outline=COLORgrid, width=GridWidth.get())
14714  NqPca.create_line(xcenter, y0, xright, y0, fill=COLORgrid, width=GridWidth.get(), dash=(4,3))
14715  NqPca.create_text(xright, y0, text=str(dBaxis_value), fill=COLORgrid, anchor="w", font=("arial", FontSize+2 ))
14716  #
14717  i = i + 1
14718  NqPca.create_line(xcenter, y0, xcenter, y1, fill=COLORgrid, width=GridWidth.get())
14719  NqPca.create_line(x0, ycenter, x1, ycenter, fill=COLORgrid, width=GridWidth.get())
14720  RAngle = math.radians(45)
14721  y = TRadius*math.sin(RAngle)
14722  x = TRadius*math.cos(RAngle)
14723  NqPca.create_line(xcenter-x, ycenter-y, xcenter+x, ycenter+y, fill=COLORgrid, width=GridWidth.get())
14724  NqPca.create_line(xcenter+x, ycenter-y, xcenter-x, ycenter+y, fill=COLORgrid, width=GridWidth.get())
14725  NqPca.create_text(x0, ycenter, text="180", fill=COLORgrid, anchor="e", font=("arial", FontSize+2 ))
14726  NqPca.create_text(x1, ycenter, text="0.0", fill=COLORgrid, anchor="w", font=("arial", FontSize+2 ))
14727  NqPca.create_text(xcenter, y0, text="90", fill=COLORgrid, anchor="s", font=("arial", FontSize+2 ))
14728  NqPca.create_text(xcenter, y1, text="-90", fill=COLORgrid, anchor="n", font=("arial", FontSize+2 ))
14729  # xcenter = xcenter + (DBlevelBP.get()/dBperPixel)
14730 # Draw traces
14731  NqPline = []
14732  if len(FSweepAdB) > 4:
14733  for index in range(len(FSweepAdB)): # while n < len(FStep):
14734  if index < len(FStep): # check if n has gone out off bounds because user did something dumb
14735  F = FBins[int(FStep[index])] # look up frequency bin in list of bins
14736  else:
14737  F = FBins[int(FStep[0])]
14738  # Mag value
14739  dbA = (10 * math.log10(float(FSweepAdB[index])) + 17) # Convert power to DBs, except for log(0) error
14740  dbB = (10 * math.log10(float(FSweepBdB[index])) + 17) # Add 17 dB for max value of +10 dB ALSO in CSV file routine!
14741  if ShowMathBP.get() == 1:
14742  MdB = dbA - dbB
14743  elif ShowMathBP.get() == 2:
14744  MdB = dbB - dbA
14745  MagRadius = (-MdB / dBperPixel) + (DBlevelBP.get()/dBperPixel)
14746  # Phase Value
14747  RelPhase = FSweepBPh[index] - FSweepAPh[index]
14748  if RelPhase > 180:
14749  RelPhase = RelPhase - 360
14750  elif RelPhase < -180:
14751  RelPhase = RelPhase + 360
14752  if Two_X_Sample.get() == 0:
14753  PhErr = 0.0018 * F # calculate phase error due half sample period offset
14754  RelPhase = RelPhase - PhErr # - PhaseOffset1x # - 12.0
14755  else:
14756  RelPhase = RelPhase # - PhaseOffset2x # - 9.0
14757  y1 = ycenter - MagRadius*math.sin(math.radians(RelPhase))
14758  if y1 > 1500:
14759  y1 = xright
14760  elif y1 < -500:
14761  y1 = ycenter - xright
14762  x1 = xcenter + MagRadius*math.cos(math.radians(RelPhase ))
14763  if x1 > 1500:
14764  x1 = xright
14765  elif x1 < -500:
14766  x1 = xcenter - xright
14767  NqPline.append(x1)
14768  NqPline.append(y1)
14769  NqPca.create_line(NqPline, fill=COLORtrace1, smooth=SmoothBool, splinestep=5, width=TRACEwidth.get())
14770 #

14804 def NiCCaresize(event):
14805  global NiCca, GRWNiC, XOLNiC, GRHNiC, Y0TNiC, CANVASwidthNic, CANVASheightNic, FontSize
14806 
14807  CANVASwidthNic = event.width - 4
14808  CANVASheightNic = event.height - 4
14809  GRWNiC = CANVASwidthNic - int(2.25 * FontSize) - X0LNiC # 18 new grid width
14810  GRHNiC = CANVASheightNic - int(7.5 * FontSize) # 60 new grid height
14811  UpdateNiCAll()
14812 
14814 def MakeNiCScreen():
14815  global NiCline, NiCca, CANVASwidthNic, CANVASheightNic, X0LNiC, GRWNiC, Y0TNiC, GRHNiC, X0TNiC
14816  global COLORzeroline, GridWidth, COLORgrid, FSweepAdB, FSweepBdB, Two_X_Sample, ShowMathBP
14817  global FSweepBPh, FSweepAPh, SmoothCurvesBP, SmoothBool, DBlevelBP, DBdivlist, DBdivindexBP
14818  global Vdiv, FBins, FStep, PhCenBodeEntry, RelPhaseCenter
14819  global FontSize
14820 
14821  Ymin = Y0TNiC # Minimum position of XY grid (top)
14822  Ymax = Y0TNiC + GRHNiC # Maximum position of XY grid (bottom)
14823  Xmin = X0LNiC # Minimum position of XY grid (left)
14824  Xmax = X0LNiC + GRWNiC # Maximum position of XY grid (right)
14825  try:
14826  Phasecenter = int(PhCenBodeEntry.get())
14827  RelPhaseCenter.set(Phasecenter)
14828  except:
14829  PhCenBodeEntry.delete(0,"end")
14830  PhCenBodeEntry.insert(0,0)
14831  RelPhaseCenter.set(0)
14832  Phasecenter = 0
14833  # Delete all items on the screen
14834  MarkerNum = 0
14835  SmoothBool = SmoothCurvesBP.get()
14836  NiCca.delete(ALL) # remove all items
14837  # Draw horizontal grid lines Rel Gain Magnitude
14838  i = 0
14839  x1 = X0LNiC
14840  x2 = X0TNiC = X0LNiC + GRWNiC
14841  mg_siz = GRWNiC/10.0
14842  mg_inc = mg_siz/5.0
14843  DegPerDiv = 360 / 10
14844  while (i < Vdiv.get()+1):
14845  dBaxis_value = (DBlevelBP.get() - (i * DBdivlist[DBdivindexBP.get()]))
14846  y = Y0TNiC + i * GRHNiC/Vdiv.get()
14847  Dline = [x1,y,x2,y]
14848  if dBaxis_value == 0:
14849  NiCca.create_line(Dline, fill=COLORzeroline, width=GridWidth.get()) # Blue line at center of grid
14850  k = 0
14851  while (k < 10):
14852  l = 1
14853  while (l < 5): # add tick marks
14854  Dline = [x1+k*mg_siz+l*mg_inc,y-5,x1+k*mg_siz+l*mg_inc,y+5]
14855  NiCca.create_line(Dline, fill=COLORgrid, width=GridWidth.get())
14856  l = l + 1
14857  k = k + 1
14858  else:
14859  NiCca.create_line(Dline, fill=COLORgrid, width=GridWidth.get())
14860  dBaxis_label = str(dBaxis_value)
14861  NiCca.create_text(x1-3, y, text=dBaxis_label, fill=COLORtrace1, anchor="e", font=("arial", FontSize ))
14862 
14863  i = i + 1
14864  # Draw vertical grid lines (phase -180 to 180 10 div)
14865  i = 0
14866  y1 = Y0TNiC
14867  y2 = Y0TNiC + GRHNiC
14868  mg_siz = GRHNiC/10.0
14869  mg_inc = mg_siz/5.0
14870  #
14871  while (i < 11):
14872  x = X0LNiC + i * GRWNiC/10.0
14873  Dline = [x,y1,x,y2]
14874  axis_value = Phasecenter - 180 + (i * DegPerDiv)
14875  axis_label = str(axis_value)
14876  if ( axis_value == 0):
14877  NiCca.create_line(Dline, fill=COLORzeroline, width=GridWidth.get()) # Blue vertical line at center of grid
14878  k = 0
14879  while (k < 10):
14880  l = 1
14881  while (l < 5): # add tick marks
14882  Dline = [x-5,y1+k*mg_siz+l*mg_inc,x+5,y1+k*mg_siz+l*mg_inc]
14883  NiCca.create_line(Dline, fill=COLORgrid, width=GridWidth.get())
14884  l = l + 1
14885  k = k + 1
14886  else:
14887  NiCca.create_line(Dline, fill=COLORgrid, width=GridWidth.get())
14888  NiCca.create_text(x, y2+3, text=axis_label, fill=COLORtrace3, anchor="n", font=("arial", FontSize ))
14889  i = i + 1
14890  # Draw traces
14891  # Vertical conversion factors (level dBs) and border limits
14892  Yconv = float(GRHNiC) / (Vdiv.get() * DBdivlist[DBdivindexBP.get()]) # Conversion factors, Yconv is the number of screenpoints per dB
14893  Yc = float(Y0TNiC) + Yconv * (DBlevelBP.get()) # Yc is the 0 dBm position, can be outside the screen!
14894  Xphconv = float(GRWNiC / 360.0) # degrees per pixel
14895  Xp = float(X0LNiC) + Xphconv * 180.0
14896  x1 = X0LNiC + 14
14897  # Horizontal conversion factors (phase deg) and border limits
14898  NiCline = []
14899  if len(FSweepAdB) > 4:
14900  index = 0
14901  for index in range(len(FSweepAdB)): # while n < len(FStep):
14902  if index < len(FStep): # check if n has gone out off bounds because user did something dumb
14903  F = FBins[int(FStep[index])] # look up frequency bin in list of bins
14904  else:
14905  F = FBins[int(FStep[0])]
14906  # Mag value
14907  dbA = (10 * math.log10(float(FSweepAdB[index])) + 17) # Convert power to DBs, except for log(0) error
14908  dbB = (10 * math.log10(float(FSweepBdB[index])) + 17) # Add 17 dB for max value of +10 dB ALSO in CSV file routine!
14909  if ShowMathBP.get() == 1:
14910  MdB = dbA - dbB
14911  elif ShowMathBP.get() == 2:
14912  MdB = dbB - dbA
14913  yb = Yc - Yconv * MdB
14914  if (yb < Ymin):
14915  yb = Ymin
14916  if (yb > Ymax):
14917  yb = Ymax
14918  # Phase Value
14919  RelPhase = FSweepBPh[index] - FSweepAPh[index]
14920  RelPhase = RelPhase - Phasecenter
14921  if RelPhase > 180:
14922  RelPhase = RelPhase - 360
14923  elif RelPhase < -180:
14924  RelPhase = RelPhase + 360
14925  if Two_X_Sample.get() == 0:
14926  PhErr = 0.0018 * F # calculate phase error due half sample period offset
14927  RelPhase = RelPhase - PhErr # - PhaseOffset1x # - 12.0
14928  else:
14929  RelPhase = RelPhase # - PhaseOffset2x
14930  xa = Xp + Xphconv * RelPhase
14931  if (xa < Xmin):
14932  xa = Ymin
14933  if (xa > Xmax):
14934  xa = Xmax
14935  NiCline.append(int(xa + 0.5))
14936  NiCline.append(int(yb + 0.5))
14937  NiCca.create_line(NiCline, fill=COLORtrace1, smooth=SmoothBool, splinestep=5, width=TRACEwidth.get())
14938 #

15211 # Resize Phase Analizer window
15212 def PhACaresize(event):
15213  global PhAca, GRWPhA, XOLPhA, GRHPhA, Y0TPhA, CANVASwidthPhA, CANVASheightPhA, FontSize
15214 
15215  CANVASwidthPhA = event.width - 4
15216  CANVASheightPhA = event.height - 4
15217  GRWPhA = CANVASwidthPhA - (2 * X0LPhA) - int(21.25 * FontSize) # 170 new grid width
15218  GRHPhA = CANVASheightPhA - Y0TPhA - int(2.25 * FontSize) # 10 new grid height
15219  UpdatePhAAll()

15233 #
15234 # Place holder
15235 def MakePhATrace(): # Update the grid and trace
15236  global VAresult, VBresult, IAresult, IBresult, VABresult, PhaseIA, PhaseIB, PhaseVA, PhaseVB, PhaseVAB
15237  global VMAresult, VMBresult, VMCresult, VMDresult, PhaseVMD, PhaseVMA, PhaseVMB, PhaseVMC
15238  global PeakVA, PeakVB, PeakIA, PeakIB, PeakVAB
15239  global PeakVMA, PeakVMB, PeakVMC, PeakVMD
15240  global PeakfreqVA, PeakfreqVB, PeakfreqIA, PeakfreqIB
15241  global PeakphaseVA, PeakphaseVB, PeakphaseIA, PeakphaseIB, PeakphaseVAB
15242  global PeakphaseVMA, PeakphaseVMB, PeakphaseVMC, PeakphaseVMD
15243  global PeakfreqVMA, PeakfreqVMB, PeakfreqVMC, PeakfreqVMD
15244  global GRHPhA # Screenheight
15245  global GRWPhA # Screenwidth
15246  global AWGSAMPLErate, SAMPLErate, BaseSampleRate
15247  global STARTsample, STOPsample, LoopNum, FSweepMode
15248  global TRACEmode, Two_X_Sample, MuxScreenStatus, MuxChan, ChopMuxMode
15249  global Vdiv # Number of vertical divisions
15250  global X0LPhA # Left top X value
15251  global Y0TPhA # Left top Y value
15252 
15253  # Set the TRACEsize variable
15254  if len(VAresult) < 32:
15255  return
15256  TRACEsize = len(VAresult) # Set the trace length
15257  Fsample = float(SAMPLErate / 2) / (TRACEsize - 1)
15258  # Horizontal conversion factors (frequency Hz) and border limits
15259  STARTsample = 0 # First sample in FFTresult[] that is used
15260  STARTsample = int(math.ceil(STARTsample)) # First within screen range
15261  if Two_X_Sample.get() == 0:
15262  STOPsample = 45000 / Fsample # Last sample in FFTresult that is used
15263  else:
15264  STOPsample = 90000 / Fsample
15265  STOPsample = int(math.floor(STOPsample)) # Last within screen range, math.floor actually not necessary, part of int
15266 #
15267 
15268  MAXsample = TRACEsize # Just an out of range check
15269  if STARTsample > (MAXsample - 1):
15270  STARTsample = MAXsample - 1
15271 
15272  if STOPsample > MAXsample:
15273  STOPsample = MAXsample
15274 
15275  n = STARTsample +1
15276  PeakVA = PeakVB = PeakIA = PeakIB = PeakVAB = 0.0
15277  PeakfreqVA = PeakfreqVB = PeakfreqIA = PeakfreqIB = F = n * Fsample
15278  PeakphaseVA = PhaseVA[n]
15279  if MuxScreenStatus.get() == 0:
15280  PeakphaseVB = PhaseVB[n]
15281  else:
15282  PeakphaseVMA = PeakphaseVMB = PeakphaseVMC = PeakphaseVMD = 0.0
15283  PeakphaseIA = PhaseIA[n]
15284  PeakphaseIB = PhaseIB[n]
15285  PeakSampleVB = PeakSampleVA = PeakSampleIA = PeakSampleIB = n
15286  if MuxChan == 0 or ChopMuxMode.get() > 0: #
15287  PeakVMA = 0
15288  PeakphaseVMA = PhaseVMA[n]
15289  PeakSampleVMA = 0
15290  PeakfreqVMA = PeakfreqVA
15291  if MuxChan == 1 or ChopMuxMode.get() > 0: #
15292  PeakVMB = 0
15293  PeakphaseVMB = PhaseVMB[n]
15294  PeakSampleVMB = 0
15295  PeakfreqVMB = PeakfreqVA
15296  if MuxChan == 2 or ChopMuxMode.get() > 0: #
15297  PeakVMC = 0
15298  PeakphaseVMC = PhaseVMC[n]
15299  PeakSampleVMC = 0
15300  PeakfreqVMC = PeakfreqVA
15301  if MuxChan == 3 or ChopMuxMode.get() > 0: #
15302  PeakVMD = 0
15303  PeakphaseVMD = PhaseVMD[n]
15304  PeakSampleVMD = 0
15305  PeakfreqVMD = PeakfreqVA
15306 
15307  while n <= STOPsample: # search for peaks
15308  F = n * Fsample
15309  try:
15310  VA = float(VAresult[n]) #
15311  except:
15312  VA = 0.0
15313  if VA > PeakVA:
15314  PeakVA = VA
15315  PeakfreqVA = F
15316  PeakphaseVA = PhaseVA[n]
15317  PeakSampleVA = n
15318 
15319  if MuxScreenStatus.get() == 0:
15320  try:
15321  VAB = float(VABresult[n]) #
15322  except:
15323  VAB = 0.0
15324  if VAB > PeakVAB:
15325  PeakVAB = VAB
15326  PeakfreqVAB = F
15327  PeakphaseVAB = PhaseVAB[n]
15328  PeakSampleVAB = n
15329 
15330  try:
15331  VB = float(VBresult[n]) #
15332  except:
15333  VB = 0.0
15334  if VB > PeakVB:
15335  PeakVB = VB
15336  PeakfreqVB = F
15337  PeakphaseVB = PhaseVB[n]
15338  PeakSampleVB = n
15339  else:
15340  if MuxChan == 0 or ChopMuxMode.get() > 0: #
15341  try:
15342  VMA = float(VMAresult[n]) #
15343  except:
15344  VMA = 0.0
15345  if VMA > PeakVMA:
15346  PeakVMA = VMA
15347  PeakfreqVMA = F
15348  PeakphaseVMA = PhaseVMA[n]
15349  PeakSampleVMA = n
15350  if MuxChan == 1 or ChopMuxMode.get() > 0: #
15351  try:
15352  VMB = float(VMBresult[n]) #
15353  except:
15354  VMB = 0.0
15355  if VMB > PeakVMB:
15356  PeakVMB = VMB
15357  PeakfreqVMB = F
15358  PeakphaseVMB = PhaseVMB[n]
15359  PeakSampleVMB = n
15360  if MuxChan == 2 or ChopMuxMode.get() > 0: #
15361  try:
15362  VMC = float(VMCresult[n]) #
15363  except:
15364  VMC = 0.0
15365  if VMC > PeakVMC:
15366  PeakVMC = VMC
15367  PeakfreqVMC = F
15368  PeakphaseVMC = PhaseVMC[n]
15369  PeakSampleVMC = n
15370  if MuxChan == 3 or ChopMuxMode.get() > 0: #
15371  try:
15372  VMD = float(VMDresult[n]) #
15373  except:
15374  VMD = 0.0
15375  if VMD > PeakVMD:
15376  PeakVMD = VMD
15377  PeakfreqVMD = F
15378  PeakphaseVMD = PhaseVMD[n]
15379  PeakSampleVMD = n
15380  try:
15381  IA = float(IAresult[n]) #
15382  except:
15383  IA = 0.0
15384  if IA > PeakIA:
15385  PeakIA = IA
15386  PeakfreqIA = F
15387  PeakphaseIA = PhaseIA[n]
15388  PeakSampleIA = n
15389 
15390  try:
15391  IB = float(IBresult[n]) #
15392  except:
15393  IB = 0.0
15394  if IB > PeakIB:
15395  PeakIB = IB
15396  PeakfreqIB = F
15397  PeakphaseIB = PhaseIB[n]
15398  PeakSampleIB = n
15399 
15400  n = n + 1
15401  # Check to see that V and I peaks are in same frequency bin?
15402  if PeakSampleVA != PeakSampleIA:
15403  PeakphaseIA = PhaseIA[PeakSampleVA]
15404  PeakIA = IAresult[PeakSampleVA]
15405  if PeakSampleVB != PeakSampleIB and MuxScreenStatus.get() == 0:
15406  PeakphaseIB = PhaseIB[PeakSampleVB]
15407  PeakIB = IBresult[PeakSampleVB]
15408 #
15409 # Draw the Phase Analyzer screen
15410 def MakePhAScreen(): # Update the screen with traces and text
15411  global PeakVA, PeakVB, PeakIA, PeakIB
15412  global PeakfreqVA, PeakfreqVB, PeakfreqIA, PeakfreqIB
15413  global PeakphaseVA, PeakphaseVB, PeakphaseIA, PeakphaseIB
15414  global PeakVMA, PeakVMB, PeakVMC, PeakVMD
15415  global PeakphaseVMA, PeakphaseVMB, PeakphaseVMC, PeakphaseVMD
15416  global PeakfreqVMA, PeakfreqVMB, PeakfreqVMC, PeakfreqVMD
15417  global CAVphase, CBVphase, CAIphase, CBIphase, CABVphase
15418  global CMAphase, CMBphase, CMCphase, CMDphase
15419  global CANVASheightPhA, CANVASwidthPhA, PhAca, TRACEwidth, GridWidth
15420  global COLORsignalband, COLORtext, COLORgrid # The colors
15421  global COLORtrace1, COLORtrace2, COLORtrace3, COLORtrace4, COLORtrace5, COLORtrace6, COLORtrace7
15422  global FFTwindow, FFTbandwidth, ZEROstuffing, FFTwindowname
15423  global X0LPhA # Left top X value
15424  global Y0TPhA # Left top Y value
15425  global GRWPhA # Screenwidth
15426  global GRHPhA # Screenheight
15427  global FontSize, MuxScreenStatus, MuxChan, Mulx, ChopMuxMode
15428  global RUNstatus # 0 stopped, 1 start, 2 running, 3 stop now, 4 stop and restart
15429  global AWGSAMPLErate, SAMPLErate, BaseSampleRate, OverRangeFlagA, OverRangeFlagB
15430  global SMPfft # number of FFT samples
15431  global TRACEaverage # Number of traces for averageing
15432  global FreqTraceMode # 1 normal 2 max 3 average
15433  global Vdiv, VScale, IScale # Number of vertical divisions
15434  global vat_btn, vbt_btn, iat_btn, ibt_btn, vabt_btn
15435  global AWGBMode, AWGBIOMode, ShowPB_A, ShowPB_B, ShowPB_C, ShowPB_D
15436  global ShowC1_V, ShowC2_V, ShowC1_I, ShowC2_I, CHA_RC_HP, CHB_RC_HP
15437  global DCV1, DCV2, MinV1, MaxV1, MinV2, MaxV2, CHAHW, CHALW, CHADCy, CHAperiod, CHAfreq
15438  global DCI1, DCI2, MinI1, MaxI1, MinI2, MaxI2, CHBHW, CHBLW, CHBDCy, CHBperiod, CHBfreq
15439  global InOffA, InGainA, InOffB, InGainB
15440  global CurOffA, CurOffB, CurGainA, CurGainB
15441  # Analog Mux channel measurement variables
15442  global DCVMuxA, MinVMuxA, MaxVMuxA, MidVMuxA, PPVMuxA, SVMuxA
15443  global DCVMuxB, MinVMuxB, MaxVMuxB, MidVMuxB, PPVMuxB, SVMuxB
15444  global DCVMuxC, MinVMuxC, MaxVMuxC, MidVMuxC, PPVMuxC, SVMuxC
15445  global DCVMuxD, MinVMuxD, MaxVMuxD, MidVMuxD, PPVMuxD, SVMuxD
15446  global SV1, SI1, SV2, SI2, CHABphase, SVA_B
15447  global MeasDCV1, MeasMinV1, MeasMaxV1, MeasMidV1, MeasPPV1
15448  global MeasDCI1, MeasMinI1, MeasMaxI1, MeasMidI1, MeasPPI1
15449  global MeasDCV2, MeasMinV2, MeasMaxV2, MeasMidV2, MeasPPV2
15450  global MeasDCI2, MeasMinI2, MeasMaxI2, MeasMidI2, MeasPPI2
15451  global MeasRMSV1, MeasRMSI1, MeasRMSV2, MeasRMSI2, MeasPhase, MeasRMSVA_B
15452  global MeasAHW, MeasALW, MeasADCy, MeasAPER, MeasAFREQ
15453  global MeasBHW, MeasBLW, MeasBDCy, MeasBPER, MeasBFREQ
15454 
15455  # Delete all items on the screen
15456  PhAca.delete(ALL) # remove all items
15457  # SmoothBool = SmoothCurvesBP.get()
15458  # Draw circular grid lines
15459  i = 1
15460  xcenter = GRWPhA/2
15461  ycenter = (GRHPhA/2) + 14
15462  Radius = (GRWPhA-X0LPhA)/(1 + Vdiv.get()*2) # 11
15463  VoltsperPixel = float(VScale.get())/Radius
15464  mAperPixel = float(IScale.get())/Radius
15465  TRadius = Radius * Vdiv.get() # 5
15466  x1 = X0LPhA
15467  x2 = X0LPhA + GRWPhA
15468  xright = 10 + xcenter + ( Vdiv.get() * Radius ) # 5
15469  while (i <= Vdiv.get()):
15470  x0 = xcenter - ( i * Radius )
15471  x1 = xcenter + ( i * Radius )
15472  y0 = ycenter - ( i * Radius )
15473  y1 = ycenter + ( i * Radius )
15474  VTxt = '{0:.2f}'.format(float(VScale.get()) * i)
15475  ITxt = '{0:.2f}'.format(float(IScale.get()) * i)
15476  TOffset = xright+(4*FontSize)
15477  PhAca.create_oval( x0, y0, x1, y1, outline=COLORgrid, width=GridWidth.get())
15478  PhAca.create_line(xcenter, y0, xright, y0, fill=COLORgrid, width=GridWidth.get(), dash=(4,3))
15479  PhAca.create_text(xright, y0, text=str(VTxt), fill=COLORtrace1, anchor="w", font=("arial", FontSize+2 ))
15480  if iat_btn.config('text')[-1] == 'ON' or ibt_btn.config('text')[-1] == 'ON':
15481  PhAca.create_text(TOffset, y0, text=str(ITxt), fill=COLORtrace3, anchor="w", font=("arial", FontSize+2 ))
15482  #
15483  i = i + 1
15484  PhAca.create_line(xcenter, y0, xcenter, y1, fill=COLORgrid, width=GridWidth.get())
15485  PhAca.create_line(x0, ycenter, x1, ycenter, fill=COLORgrid, width=GridWidth.get())
15486  RAngle = math.radians(45)
15487  y = TRadius*math.sin(RAngle)
15488  x = TRadius*math.cos(RAngle)
15489  PhAca.create_line(xcenter-x, ycenter-y, xcenter+x, ycenter+y, fill=COLORgrid, width=GridWidth.get())
15490  PhAca.create_line(xcenter+x, ycenter-y, xcenter-x, ycenter+y, fill=COLORgrid, width=GridWidth.get())
15491  PhAca.create_text(x0, ycenter, text="180", fill=COLORgrid, anchor="e", font=("arial", FontSize+2 ))
15492  PhAca.create_text(x1, ycenter, text="0.0", fill=COLORgrid, anchor="w", font=("arial", FontSize+2 ))

16093 def PlotPhAFromFile():
16094  global CANVASheightPhA, CANVASwidthPhA, PhAca, TRACEwidth, GridWidth, PhAPlotMode
16095  global COLORsignalband, COLORtext, COLORgrid, SmoothCurves # The colors
16096  global COLORtrace1, COLORtrace2, COLORtrace3, COLORtrace4, COLORtrace5, COLORtrace6, COLORtrace7
16097  global GRWPhA, GRHPhA, X0LPhA, Vdiv, VScale, IScale
16098 # open file to read data from
16099  filename = askopenfilename(defaultextension = ".csv", filetypes=[("Comma Separated Values", "*.csv")])
16100  i = 1
16101  xcenter = GRWPhA/2
16102  ycenter = (GRHPhA/2) + 14
16103  Radius = (GRWPhA-X0LPhA)/(1 + Vdiv.get()*2) # 11
16104  VoltsperPixel = float(VScale.get())/Radius
16105  mAperPixel = float(IScale.get())/Radius
16106  TRadius = Radius * Vdiv.get() # 5
16107  x1 = X0LPhA
16108  x2 = X0LPhA + GRWPhA
16109  PhATrace = []
16110 # Read values from CVS file
16111  try:
16112  CSVFile = open(filename)
16113  dialect = csv.Sniffer().sniff(CSVFile.read(2048))
16114  CSVFile.seek(0)
16115  csv_f = csv.reader(CSVFile, dialect)
16116  for row in csv_f:
16117  try:
16118  PeakMag = float(row[0])
16119  PeakPhase = float(row[1])
16120  if row[2] == "CA-I" or row[2] == "CB-I":
16121  MagRadius = PeakMag / mAperPixel
16122  else:
16123  MagRadius = PeakMag / VoltsperPixel
16124 
16125  y1 = ycenter - MagRadius*math.sin(math.radians(PeakPhase))
16126  if y1 > 1500:
16127  y1 = xright
16128  elif y1 < -500:
16129  y1 = ycenter - xright
16130  x1 = xcenter + MagRadius*math.cos(math.radians(PeakPhase))
16131  if x1 > 1500:
16132  x1 = xright
16133  elif x1 < -500:
16134  x1 = xcenter - xright
16135  if PhAPlotMode.get() == 0:
16136  PhAca.create_line(xcenter, ycenter, x1, y1, fill=COLORtrace5, arrow="last", width=TRACEwidth.get())
16137  else:
16138  PhATrace.append(x1)
16139  PhATrace.append(y1)
16140  except:
16141  print( 'skipping non-numeric row')
16142  if PhAPlotMode.get() == 1:
16143  PhAca.create_line(PhATrace, fill=COLORtrace5, smooth=SmoothCurves.get(), splinestep=5, width=TRACEwidth.get())
16144  CSVFile.close()
16145  except:
16146  showwarning("WARNING","No such file found or wrong format!")

16149 def STOREcsvfile(): # Store the trace as CSV file [frequency, magnitude or dB value]
16150  global FFTmemoryA, FFTresultA
16151  global FFTmemoryB, FFTresultB
16152  global PhaseA, PhaseB, freqwindow
16153  global AWGSAMPLErate, SAMPLErate, BaseSampleRate, ShowC1_VdB, ShowC2_VdB
16154 
16155  # Set the TRACEsize variable
16156  if ShowC1_VdB.get() == 1:
16157  TRACEsize = len(FFTresultA) # Set the trace length
16158  elif ShowC2_VdB.get() == 1:
16159  TRACEsize = len(FFTresultB)
16160  if TRACEsize == 0: # If no trace, skip rest of this routine
16161  return()
16162 # ask if save as magnitude or dB
16163  dB = askyesno("Mag or dB: ","Save amplidude data as dB (Yes) or Mag (No):\n", parent=freqwindow)
16164  # Make the file name and open it
16165  tme = strftime("%Y%b%d-%H%M%S", gmtime()) # The time
16166  filename = "Spectrum-" + tme
16167  filename = filename + ".csv"
16168  # open file to save data
16169  filename = asksaveasfilename(initialfile = filename, defaultextension = ".csv",
16170  filetypes=[("Comma Separated Values", "*.csv")], parent=freqwindow)
16171  DataFile = open(filename,'a') # Open output file
16172  HeaderString = 'Frequency-#, '
16173  if ShowC1_VdB.get() == 1:
16174  if dB == 1:
16175  HeaderString = HeaderString + 'CA-dB, '
16176  if dB == 0:
16177  HeaderString = HeaderString + 'CA-Mag, '
16178  if ShowC2_VdB.get() == 1:
16179  if dB == 1:
16180  HeaderString = HeaderString + 'CB-dB, '
16181  if dB == 0:
16182  HeaderString = HeaderString + 'CB-Mag, '
16183  if ShowC1_P.get() == 1:
16184  HeaderString = HeaderString + 'Phase A-B, '
16185  if ShowC2_P.get() == 1:
16186  HeaderString = HeaderString + 'Phase B-A, '
16187  HeaderString = HeaderString + '\n'
16188  DataFile.write( HeaderString )
16189 
16190  Fsample = float(SAMPLErate / 2) / (TRACEsize - 1) # Frequency step per sample
16191 
16192  n = 0
16193  while n < TRACEsize:
16194  F = n * Fsample
16195  txt = str(F)
16196  if ShowC1_VdB.get() == 1:
16197  V = 10 * math.log10(float(FFTresultA[n])) + 17 # Add 17 dB for max value of +10 dB
16198  if dB == 0:
16199  V = 10.0**(V/20.0)
16200  txt = txt + "," + str(V)
16201  if ShowC2_VdB.get() == 1:
16202  V = 10 * math.log10(float(FFTresultB[n])) + 17 # Add 17 dB for max value of +10 dB
16203  if dB == 0:
16204  V = 10.0**(V/20.0)
16205  txt = txt + "," + str(V)
16206  if ShowC1_P.get() == 1:
16207  RelPhase = PhaseA[n]-PhaseB[n]
16208  if RelPhase > 180:
16209  RelPhase = RelPhase - 360
16210  elif RelPhase < -180:
16211  RelPhase = RelPhase + 360
16212  txt = txt + "," + str(RelPhase)
16213  if ShowC2_P.get() == 1:
16214  RelPhase = PhaseB[n]-PhaseA[n]
16215  if RelPhase > 180:
16216  RelPhase = RelPhase - 360
16217  elif RelPhase < -180:
16218  RelPhase = RelPhase + 360
16219  txt = txt + "," + str(RelPhase)
16220  txt = txt + "\n"
16221  DataFile.write(txt)
16222  n = n + 1
16223 
16224  DataFile.close() # Close the file

16227 def MakeFreqScreen(): # Update the screen with traces and text
16228  global CANVASheightF, CANVASwidthF, SmoothCurvesSA
16229  global PeakxA, PeakyA, PeakxB, PeakyB, PeakdbA, PeakdbB
16230  global PeakxM, PeakyM, PeakMdb, PeakfreqM
16231  global PeakfreqA, PeakfreqB, PeakfreqRA, PeakfreqRB
16232  global PeakxRA, PeakyRA, PeakxRB, PeakyRB, PeakdbRA, PeakdbRB
16233  global PeakxRM, PeakyRM, PeakRMdb, PeakfreqRM, PeakIndexA, PeakIndexB, Fsample
16234  global COLORgrid # The colors
16235  global COLORsignalband, COLORtext
16236  global COLORtrace1, COLORtrace2
16237  global FSweepMode, LoopNum, MarkerFreqNum, TRACEwidth, GridWidth
16238  global DBdivindex # Index value
16239  global DBdivlist # dB per division list
16240  global DBlevel # Reference level
16241  global FFTwindow, FFTbandwidth, ZEROstuffing, FFTwindowname
16242  global X0LF # Left top X value
16243  global Y0TF # Left top Y value
16244  global GRWF # Screenwidth
16245  global GRHF # Screenheight
16246  global FontSize
16247  global RUNstatus # 0 stopped, 1 start, 2 running, 3 stop now, 4 stop and restart
16248  global AWGSAMPLErate, SAMPLErate, BaseSampleRate, SingleShotSA, HScale, HarmonicMarkers
16249  global SMPfft # number of FFT samples
16250  global StartFreqEntry, StopFreqEntry, PhCenFreqEntry, RelPhaseCenter
16251  global ShowC1_P, ShowC2_P, ShowRA_VdB, ShowRB_VdB, ShowMarker
16252  global ShowRA_P, ShowRB_P, ShowMathSA, FreqDisp, ShowAWGASA, ShowAWGBSA
16253  global ShowFCur, ShowdBCur, FCursor, dBCursor
16254  global T1Fline, T2Fline, T1Pline, T1FRline, T2FRline, TFMline, TFRMline
16255  global T1PRline, T2PRline, TAFline, TBFline
16256  global TRACEaverage # Number of traces for averageing
16257  global FreqTraceMode # 1 normal 2 max 3 average
16258  global Vdiv # Number of vertical divisions
16259 
16260  # Delete all items on the screen
16261  MarkerFreqNum = 0
16262  Freqca.delete(ALL) # remove all items
16263  try:
16264  StartFrequency = float(StartFreqEntry.get())
16265  except:
16266  StartFreqEntry.delete(0,"end")
16267  StartFreqEntry.insert(0,100)
16268  StartFrequency = 100
16269  try:
16270  StopFrequency = float(StopFreqEntry.get())
16271  except:
16272  StopFreqEntry.delete(0,"end")
16273  StopFreqEntry.insert(0,10000)
16274  StopFrequency = 10000
16275  try:
16276  Phasecenter = int(PhCenFreqEntry.get())
16277  RelPhaseCenter.set(Phasecenter)
16278  except:
16279  PhCenFreqEntry.delete(0,"end")
16280  PhCenFreqEntry.insert(0,0)
16281  RelPhaseCenter.set(0)
16282  Phasecenter = 0
16283  # Draw horizontal grid lines
16284  i = 0
16285  x1 = X0LF
16286  x2 = X0LF + GRWF
16287  while (i <= Vdiv.get()):
16288  y = Y0TF + i * GRHF/Vdiv.get()
16289  Dline = [x1,y,x2,y]
16290  if i == 0 or i == Vdiv.get():
16291  Freqca.create_line(Dline, fill=COLORgrid, width=GridWidth.get())
16292  else:
16293  Freqca.create_line(Dline, dash=(4,3), fill=COLORgrid, width=GridWidth.get())
16294  Vaxis_value = (DBlevel.get() - (i * DBdivlist[DBdivindex.get()]))
16295  Vaxis_label = str(Vaxis_value)
16296  Freqca.create_text(x1-3, y, text=Vaxis_label, fill=COLORtrace1, anchor="e", font=("arial", FontSize ))
16297  if ShowC1_P.get() == 1 or ShowC2_P.get() == 1:
16298  Vaxis_value = ( 180 - ( i * (360 / Vdiv.get())))
16299  Vaxis_value = Vaxis_value + Phasecenter
16300  Vaxis_label = str(Vaxis_value)
16301  Freqca.create_text(x2+3, y, text=Vaxis_label, fill=COLORtrace3, anchor="w", font=("arial", FontSize ))
16302  i = i + 1
16303  # Draw vertical grid lines
16304  i = 0
16305  y1 = Y0TF
16306  y2 = Y0TF + GRHF
16307  if HScale.get() == 1:
16308  F = 1.0
16309  LogFStop = math.log10(StopFrequency)
16310  try:
16311  LogFStart = math.log10(StartFrequency)
16312  except:
16313  LogFStart = 0.0
16314  LogFpixel = (LogFStop - LogFStart) / GRWF
16315  # draw left and right edges
16316  while F <= StopFrequency:
16317  if F >= StartFrequency:
16318  try:
16319  LogF = math.log10(F) # convet to log Freq
16320  x = X0LF + (LogF - LogFStart)/LogFpixel
16321  except:
16322  x = X0LF
16323  Dline = [x,y1,x,y2]
16324  if F == 1 or F == 10 or F == 100 or F == 1000 or F == 10000 or F == 100000:
16325  Freqca.create_line(Dline, fill=COLORgrid, width=GridWidth.get())
16326  axis_label = str(F)
16327  Freqca.create_text(x, y2+3, text=axis_label, fill=COLORgrid, anchor="n", font=("arial", FontSize ))
16328  else:
16329  Freqca.create_line(Dline, dash=(4,3), fill=COLORgrid, width=GridWidth.get())
16330 
16331  if F < 10:
16332  F = F + 1
16333  elif F < 100:
16334  F = F + 10
16335  elif F < 1000:
16336  F = F + 100
16337  elif F < 1000:
16338  F = F + 100
16339  elif F < 10000:
16340  F = F + 1000
16341  elif F < 100000:
16342  F = F + 10000
16343  elif F < 200000:
16344  F = F + 10000
16345  else:
16346  Freqdiv = (StopFrequency - StartFrequency) / 10
16347  while (i < 11):
16348  x = X0LF + i * GRWF/10.0
16349  Dline = [x,y1,x,y2]
16350  if i == 0 or i == 10:
16351  Freqca.create_line(Dline, fill=COLORgrid, width=GridWidth.get())
16352  else:
16353  Freqca.create_line(Dline, dash=(4,3), fill=COLORgrid, width=GridWidth.get())
16354  axis_value = (StartFrequency + (i * Freqdiv))
16355  axis_label = str(axis_value)
16356  Freqca.create_text(x, y2+3, text=axis_label, fill=COLORgrid, anchor="n", font=("arial", FontSize ))
16357  i = i + 1
16358  # Draw X - Y cursors if needed
16359  Yconv = float(GRHF) / (Vdiv.get() * DBdivlist[DBdivindex.get()]) # Conversion factors, Yconv is the number of screenpoints per dB
16360  Yc = float(Y0TF) + Yconv * (DBlevel.get()) # Yc is the 0 dBm position, can be outside the screen!
16361  Fpixel = (StopFrequency - StartFrequency) / GRWF # Frequency step per screen pixel
16362  if ShowFCur.get() > 0:
16363  Dline = [FCursor, Y0TF, FCursor, Y0TF+GRHF]
16364  Freqca.create_line(Dline, dash=(3,4), fill=COLORtrigger, width=GridWidth.get())
16365  # Horizontal conversion factors (frequency Hz) and border limits
16366  if HScale.get() == 1:
16367  LogFStop = math.log10(StopFrequency)
16368  try:
16369  LogFStart = math.log10(StartFrequency)
16370  except:
16371  LogFStart = 0.0
16372  LogFpixel = (LogFStop - LogFStart) / GRWF
16373  xfreq = 10**(((FCursor-X0LF)*LogFpixel) + LogFStart)
16374  else:
16375  Fpixel = (StopFrequency - StartFrequency) / GRWF # Frequency step per screen pixel
16376  xfreq = ((FCursor-X0LF)*Fpixel)+StartFrequency
16377  XFString = ' {0:.2f} '.format(xfreq)
16378  V_label = XFString + " Hz"
16379  Freqca.create_text(FCursor+1, Y0TF+GRHF+6, text=V_label, fill=COLORtext, anchor="n", font=("arial", FontSize ))
16380  #Freqca.create_text(FCursor+1, dBCursor-5, text=V_label, fill=COLORtext, anchor="w", font=("arial", FontSize ))
16381 #
16382  if ShowdBCur.get() > 0:

16537 def INITIALIZEstart():
16538  global SMPfft, FFTwindow
16539  global SMPfftpwrTwo, BodeDisp
16540  global TRACEresetFreq, FreqTraceMode, LoopNum, FSweepMode, FSweepCont
16541 
16542  # First some subroutines to set specific variables
16543  if BodeDisp.get() == 0:
16544  if FFTwindow.get() != 8:
16545  SMPfft = 2 ** int(SMPfftpwrTwo.get()) # Calculate the number of FFT samples from SMPfftpwrtwo
16546 
16547  CALCFFTwindowshape()
16548  if FreqTraceMode.get() == 1 and TRACEresetFreq == False:
16549  TRACEresetFreq = True # Clear the memory for averaging or peak
16550  if FreqTraceMode.get() == 2 and LoopNum.get() == 1 and FSweepMode.get() > 0 and FSweepCont.get() == 0 and BodeDisp.get() >0:
16551  TRACEresetFreq = True # Clear the memory for peak hold when using sweep generator

16553 def CALCFFTwindowshape(): # Make the FFTwindowshape for the windowing function
16554  global FFTbandwidth # The FFT bandwidth
16555  global FFTwindow # Which FFT window number is selected
16556  global FFTwindowname # The name of the FFT window function
16557  global FFTwindowshape # The window shape
16558  global AWGSAMPLErate, SAMPLErate, BaseSampleRate # The sample rate
16559  global SMPfft # Number of FFT samples
16560  global LastWindow, LastSMPfft
16561 
16562  if LastWindow == FFTwindow.get() and LastSMPfft == SMPfft:
16563  # recalculate window only if something changed
16564  return
16565  # FFTname and FFTbandwidth in milliHz
16566  FFTwindowname = "No such window"
16567  FFTbw = 0
16568 
16569  if FFTwindow.get() == 0:
16570  FFTwindowname = " Rectangular (no) window (B=1) "
16571  FFTbw = 1.0
16572 
16573  if FFTwindow.get() == 1:
16574  FFTwindowname = " Cosine window (B=1.24) "
16575  FFTbw = 1.24
16576 
16577  if FFTwindow.get() == 2:
16578  FFTwindowname = " Triangular window (B=1.33) "
16579  FFTbw = 1.33
16580 
16581  if FFTwindow.get() == 3:
16582  FFTwindowname = " Hann window (B=1.5) "
16583  FFTbw = 1.5
16584 
16585  if FFTwindow.get() == 4:
16586  FFTwindowname = " Blackman window (B=1.73) "
16587  FFTbw = 1.73
16588 
16589  if FFTwindow.get() == 5:
16590  FFTwindowname = " Nuttall window (B=2.02) "
16591  FFTbw = 2.02
16592 
16593  if FFTwindow.get() == 6:
16594  FFTwindowname = " Flat top window (B=3.77) "
16595  FFTbw = 3.77
16596 
16597  if FFTwindow.get() == 7:
16598  FFTwindowname = FFTUserWindowString
16599  FFTbw = 0.0
16600  try:
16601  FFTwindowshape = eval(FFTUserWindowString)
16602  except:
16603  FFTwindowshape = numpy.ones(SMPfft) # Initialize with ones
16604  print( "Filling FFT window with Ones")
16605  elif FFTwindow.get() == 8: # window shape array read from csv file
16606  FFTwindowname = "Window Shape From file"
16607  FFTbw = 0.0
16608  else:
16609  FFTbandwidth = int(FFTbw * SAMPLErate / float(SMPfft))
16610  # Calculate the shape
16611  FFTwindowshape = numpy.ones(SMPfft) # Initialize with ones
16612  n = 0
16613  while n < SMPfft:
16614  # Cosine window function - medium-dynamic range B=1.24
16615  if FFTwindow.get() == 1:
16616  w = math.sin(math.pi * n / (SMPfft - 1))
16617  FFTwindowshape[n] = w * 1.571
16618  # Triangular non-zero endpoints - medium-dynamic range B=1.33
16619  if FFTwindow.get() == 2:
16620  w = (2.0 / SMPfft) * ((SMPfft/ 2.0) - abs(n - (SMPfft - 1) / 2.0))
16621  FFTwindowshape[n] = w * 2.0
16622  # Hann window function - medium-dynamic range B=1.5
16623  if FFTwindow.get() == 3:
16624  w = 0.5 - 0.5 * math.cos(2 * math.pi * n / (SMPfft - 1))
16625  FFTwindowshape[n] = w * 2.000
16626  # Blackman window, continuous first derivate function - medium-dynamic range B=1.73
16627  if FFTwindow.get() == 4:
16628  w = 0.42 - 0.5 * math.cos(2 * math.pi * n / (SMPfft - 1)) + 0.08 * math.cos(4 * math.pi * n / (SMPfft - 1))
16629  FFTwindowshape[n] = w * 2.381
16630  # Nuttall window, continuous first derivate function - high-dynamic range B=2.02
16631  if FFTwindow.get() == 5:
16632  w = 0.355768 - 0.487396 * math.cos(2 * math.pi * n / (SMPfft - 1)) + 0.144232 * math.cos(4 * math.pi * n / (SMPfft - 1))- 0.012604 * math.cos(6 * math.pi * n / (SMPfft - 1))
16633  FFTwindowshape[n] = w * 2.811
16634  # Flat top window, medium-dynamic range, extra wide bandwidth B=3.77
16635  if FFTwindow.get() == 6:
16636  w = 1.0 - 1.93 * math.cos(2 * math.pi * n / (SMPfft - 1)) + 1.29 * math.cos(4 * math.pi * n / (SMPfft - 1))- 0.388 * math.cos(6 * math.pi * n / (SMPfft - 1)) + 0.032 * math.cos(8 * math.pi * n / (SMPfft - 1))
16637  FFTwindowshape[n] = w * 1.000
16638  n = n + 1
16639  LastWindow = FFTwindow.get()
16640  LastSMPfft = SMPfft
16641 
16642 def BUserFFTwindow():
16643  global FFTUserWindowString, freqwindow
16644 
16645  TempString = FFTUserWindowString
16646  FFTUserWindowString = askstring("User FFT Window", "Current User Window: " + FFTUserWindowString + "\n\nNew Window:\n", initialvalue=FFTUserWindowString, parent=freqwindow)
16647  if (FFTUserWindowString == None): # If Cancel pressed, then None
16648  FFTUserWindowString = TempString

16650 def BFileFFTwindow():
16651  global FFTwindowshape, SMPfft, LastSMPfft, FFTwindow, LastWindow
16652 
16653  # Read values from CVS file
16654  filename = askopenfilename(defaultextension = ".csv", filetypes=[("CSV files", "*.csv")], parent=freqwindow)
16655  try:
16656  CSVFile = open(filename)
16657  csv_f = csv.reader(CSVFile)
16658  FFTwindowshape = []
16659  for row in csv_f:
16660  try:
16661  FFTwindowshape.append(float(row[0]))
16662  except:
16663  print( 'skipping non-numeric row')
16664  FFTwindowshape = numpy.array(FFTwindowshape)
16665  CSVFile.close()
16666  SMPfft = len(FFTwindowshape)
16667  LastSMPfft = SMPfft
16668  LastWindow = FFTwindow.get()
16669  print( SMPfft)
16670  except:
16671  showwarning("WARNING","No such file found or wrong format!")

16684 def onCanvasFreqClickScroll(event):

16687  ShiftKeyDwn = event.state & 1
16688  if ShowFCur.get() > 0 and ShiftKeyDwn == 0:
16689  # respond to Linux or Windows wheel event
16690  if event.num == 5 or event.delta == -120:
16691  FCursor -= 1
16692  if event.num == 4 or event.delta == 120:
16693  FCursor += 1
16694  elif ShowdBCur.get() > 0 or ShiftKeyDwn == 1:
16695  # respond to Linux or Windows wheel event

16697  dBCursor += 1
16698  if event.num == 4 or event.delta == 120:
16699  dBCursor -= 1
16700  if RUNstatus.get() == 0:
16701  UpdateFreqScreen()

16703 def onCanvasFreqLeftClick(event):
16704  global X0LF # Left top X value
16705  global Y0TF # Left top Y value
16706  global GRWF # Screenwidth
16707  global GRHF # Screenheight
16708  global FontSize
16709  global Freqca, MarkerLoc, SAMPLErate, BaseSampleRate
16710  global COLORgrid, COLORtext, HScale, ShowC1_VdB, ShowC2_VdB
16711  global COLORtrace1, COLORtrace2, StartFreqEntry, StopFreqEntry
16712  global AWGSAMPLErate, RUNstatus, COLORtext, MarkerFreqNum, PrevdBV, PrevF
16713 
16714  if (RUNstatus.get() == 0):
16715  MarkerFreqNum = MarkerFreqNum + 1
16716  COLORmarker = COLORgrid
16717  if ShowC1_VdB.get() == 1:
16718  COLORmarker = COLORtrace1
16719  elif ShowC2_VdB.get() == 1:
16720  COLORmarker = COLORtrace2
16721  try:
16722  StartFrequency = float(StartFreqEntry.get())
16723  except:
16724  StartFreqEntry.delete(0,"end")
16725  StartFreqEntry.insert(0,100)
16726  StartFrequency = 100
16727  try:
16728  StopFrequency = float(StopFreqEntry.get())
16729  except:
16730  StopFreqEntry.delete(0,"end")
16731  StopFreqEntry.insert(0,100)
16732  StopFrequency = 100
16733  # draw X at marker point and number
16734  Freqca.create_line(event.x-4, event.y-4,event.x+4, event.y+5, fill=COLORmarker)
16735  Freqca.create_line(event.x+4, event.y-4,event.x-4, event.y+5, fill=COLORmarker)
16736  Freqca.create_text(event.x+4, event.y, text=str(MarkerFreqNum), fill=COLORmarker, anchor="w", font=("arial", FontSize ))
16737  # Vertical conversion factors (level dBs) and border limits
16738  Yconv = float(GRHF) / (Vdiv.get() * DBdivlist[DBdivindex.get()]) # Conversion factors, Yconv is the number of screenpoints per dB
16739  Yc = float(Y0TF) + Yconv * (DBlevel.get()) # Yc is the 0 dBm position, can be outside the screen!
16740  Yphconv = float(GRHF) / 360
16741  Yp = float(Y0TF) + Yphconv + 180
16742  # Horizontal conversion factors (frequency Hz) and border limits
16743  if HScale.get() == 1:
16744  LogFStop = math.log10(StopFrequency)
16745  try:
16746  LogFStart = math.log10(StartFrequency)
16747  except:
16748  LogFStart = 0.0
16749  LogFpixel = (LogFStop - LogFStart) / GRWF
16750  xfreq = 10**(((event.x-X0LF)*LogFpixel) + LogFStart)
16751  else:
16752  Fpixel = (StopFrequency - StartFrequency) / GRWF # Frequency step per screen pixel
16753  xfreq = ((event.x-X0LF)*Fpixel)+StartFrequency
16754 
16755  yvdB = ((Yc-event.y)/Yconv)
16756  VdBString = ' {0:.1f} '.format(yvdB)
16757  XFString = ' {0:.2f} '.format(xfreq)
16758  V_label = str(MarkerFreqNum) + " " + XFString + " Hz, " + VdBString + " dBV"
16759  if MarkerFreqNum > 1:
16760  DeltaV = ' {0:.3f} '.format(yvdB-PrevdBV)
16761  DeltaF = ' {0:.2f} '.format(xfreq-PrevF)
16762  V_label = V_label + " Delta " + DeltaF + " Hz, " + DeltaV + " dBV"
16763  x = X0LF + 5
16764  y = Y0TF + 3 + (MarkerFreqNum*10)
16765  Justify = 'w'
16766  if MarkerLoc == 'UR' or MarkerLoc == 'ur':
16767  x = X0LF + GRWF - 5
16768  y = Y0TF + 3 + (MarkerFreqNum*10)
16769  Justify = 'e'
16770  if MarkerLoc == 'LL' or MarkerLoc == 'll':
16771  x = X0LF + 5
16772  y = Y0TF + GRHF + 3 - (MarkerFreqNum*10)
16773  Justify = 'w'
16774  if MarkerLoc == 'LR' or MarkerLoc == 'lr':
16775  x = X0LF + GRWF - 5
16776  y = Y0TF + GRHF + 3 - (MarkerFreqNum*10)
16777  Justify = 'e'
16778  Freqca.create_text(x, y, text=V_label, fill=COLORmarker, anchor=Justify, font=("arial", FontSize ))
16779  PrevdBV = yvdB
16780  PrevF = xfreq

16905  BdBCursor += 1
16906  if event.num == 4 or event.delta == 120:
16907  BdBCursor -= 1

16909  UpdateBodeScreen()

16911 def onCanvasBodeLeftClick(event):
16912  global X0LBP # Left top X value
16913  global Y0TBP # Left top Y value
16914  global GRWBP # Screenwidth
16915  global GRHBP # Screenheight
16916  global FontSize
16917  global Bodeca, MarkerLoc, SAMPLErate
16918  global COLORgrid, COLORtext, HScaleBP, ShowCA_VdB, ShowCB_VdB, DBdivindexBP
16919  global COLORtrace1, COLORtrace2, COLORtrace6, StartBodeEntry, StopBodeEntry, DBlevelBP
16920  global AWGSAMPLErate, RUNstatus, COLORtext, MarkerFreqNum, PrevdBV, PrevF, Vdiv
16921 
16922  if (RUNstatus.get() == 0):
16923  MarkerFreqNum = MarkerFreqNum + 1
16924  COLORmarker = COLORtrace6 # COLORgrid
16925  if ShowCA_VdB.get() == 1:
16926  COLORmarker = COLORtrace1
16927  elif ShowCB_VdB.get() == 1:
16928  COLORmarker = COLORtrace2
16929  try:
16930  EndFreq = float(StopBodeEntry.get())
16931  except:
16932  StopBodeEntry.delete(0,"end")
16933  StopBodeEntry.insert(0,10000)
16934  EndFreq = 10000
16935  try:
16936  BeginFreq = float(StartBodeEntry.get())
16937  except:
16938  StartBodeEntry.delete(0,"end")
16939  StartBodeEntry.insert(0,100)
16940  BeginFreq = 100
16941  # draw X at marker point and number
16942  Bodeca.create_line(event.x-4, event.y-4,event.x+4, event.y+5, fill=COLORmarker)
16943  Bodeca.create_line(event.x+4, event.y-4,event.x-4, event.y+5, fill=COLORmarker)
16944  Bodeca.create_text(event.x+4, event.y, text=str(MarkerFreqNum), fill=COLORmarker, anchor="w", font=("arial", FontSize ))
16945  # Vertical conversion factors (level dBs) and border limits
16946  Yconv = float(GRHBP) / (Vdiv.get() * DBdivlist[DBdivindexBP.get()]) # Conversion factors, Yconv is the number of screenpoints per dB
16947  Yc = float(Y0TBP) + Yconv * (DBlevelBP.get()) # Yc is the 0 dBm position, can be outside the screen!
16948  Yphconv = float(GRHBP) / 360
16949  Yp = float(Y0TBP) + Yphconv + 180
16950  x1 = X0LBP + 14
16951  x2 = x1 + GRWBP
16952  # Horizontal conversion factors (frequency Hz) and border limits
16953  if HScaleBP.get() == 1:
16954  LogFStop = math.log10(EndFreq)
16955  try:
16956  LogFStart = math.log10(BeginFreq)
16957  except:
16958  LogFStart = 0.0
16959  LogFpixel = (LogFStop - LogFStart) / GRWBP
16960  xfreq = 10**(((event.x-x1)*LogFpixel) + LogFStart)
16961  else:
16962  Fpixel = (EndFreq - BeginFreq) / GRWBP # Frequency step per screen pixel
16963  xfreq = ((event.x-x1)*Fpixel)+BeginFreq
16964 
16965  yvdB = ((Yc-event.y)/Yconv)
16966  VdBString = ' {0:.1f} '.format(yvdB)
16967  XFString = ' {0:.2f} '.format(xfreq)
16968  V_label = str(MarkerFreqNum) + " " + XFString + " Hz, " + VdBString + " dBV"
16969  if MarkerFreqNum > 1:
16970  DeltaV = ' {0:.3f} '.format(yvdB-PrevdBV)
16971  DeltaF = ' {0:.2f} '.format(xfreq-PrevF)
16972  V_label = V_label + " Delta " + DeltaF + " Hz, " + DeltaV + " dBV"
16973  x = x1 + 5
16974  y = Y0TBP + 3 + (MarkerFreqNum*10)
16975  Justify = 'w'
16976  if MarkerLoc == 'UR' or MarkerLoc == 'ur':
16977  x = x2 - 5
16978  y = Y0TBP + 3 + (MarkerFreqNum*10)
16979  Justify = 'e'
16980  if MarkerLoc == 'LL' or MarkerLoc == 'll':
16981  x = x1 + 5
16982  y = Y0TBP + GRHBP + 3 - (MarkerFreqNum*10)
16983  Justify = 'w'
16984  if MarkerLoc == 'LR' or MarkerLoc == 'lr':
16985  x = x2 - 5
16986  y = Y0TBP + GRHBP + 3 - (MarkerFreqNum*10)
16987  Justify = 'e'
16988  Bodeca.create_text(x, y, text=V_label, fill=COLORmarker, anchor=Justify, font=("arial", FontSize ))
16989  PrevdBV = yvdB
16990  PrevF = xfreq
16991 #

17093 def onTextScroll(event): # Use mouse wheel to scroll entry values, august 7
17094  button = event.widget
17095  cursor_position = button.index(INSERT) # get current cursor position
17096  Pos = cursor_position
17097  OldVal = button.get() # get current entry string
17098  OldValfl = float(OldVal) # and its value
17099  NewVal = OldValfl
17100  Len = len(OldVal)
17101  Dot = OldVal.find (".") # find decimal point position
17102  Decimals = Len - Dot - 1
17103  if Dot == -1 : # no point
17104  Decimals = 0
17105  Step = 10**(Len - Pos)
17106  elif Pos <= Dot : # no point left of position
17107  Step = 10**(Dot - Pos)
17108  else:
17109  Step = 10**(Dot - Pos + 1)
17110  # respond to Linux or Windows wheel event
17111  if event.num == 5 or event.delta == -120:
17112  NewVal = OldValfl - Step
17113  if event.num == 4 or event.delta == 120:
17114  NewVal = OldValfl + Step
17115  FormatStr = "{0:." + str(Decimals) + "f}"
17116  NewStr = FormatStr.format(NewVal)
17117  NewDot = NewStr.find (".")
17118  NewPos = Pos + NewDot - Dot
17119  if Decimals == 0 :
17120  NewLen = len(NewStr)
17121  NewPos = Pos + NewLen - Len
17122  button.delete(0, END) # remove old entry
17123  button.insert(0, NewStr) # insert new entry
17124  button.icursor(NewPos) # resets the insertion cursor

17142 # Use Arriw keys to inc dec entry values
17143 def onTextKey(event):
17144  button = event.widget
17145  cursor_position = button.index(INSERT) # get current cursor position
17146  Pos = cursor_position
17147  OldVal = button.get() # get current entry string
17148  OldValfl = float(OldVal) # and its value
17149  Len = len(OldVal)
17150  Dot = OldVal.find (".") # find decimal point position
17151  Decimals = Len - Dot - 1
17152  if Dot == -1 : # no point
17153  Decimals = 0
17154  Step = 10**(Len - Pos)
17155  elif Pos <= Dot : # no point left of position
17156  Step = 10**(Dot - Pos)
17157  else:
17158  Step = 10**(Dot - Pos + 1)
17159  if platform.system() == "Windows":
17160  if event.keycode == 38: # increment digit for up arrow key
17161  NewVal = OldValfl + Step
17162  elif event.keycode == 40: # decrement digit for down arrow
17163  NewVal = OldValfl - Step
17164  else:
17165  return
17166  elif platform.system() == "Linux":
17167  if event.keycode == 111: # increment digit for up arrow key
17168  NewVal = OldValfl + Step
17169  elif event.keycode == 116: # decrement digit for down arrow
17170  NewVal = OldValfl - Step
17171  else:
17172  return
17173  elif platform.system() == "Darwin":
17174  if event.keycode == 0x7D: # increment digit for up arrow key
17175  NewVal = OldValfl + Step
17176  elif event.keycode == 0x7E: # decrement digit for down arrow
17177  NewVal = OldValfl - Step
17178  else:
17179  return
17180  else:
17181  return
17182 #
17183  FormatStr = "{0:." + str(Decimals) + "f}"
17184  NewStr = FormatStr.format(NewVal)
17185  NewDot = NewStr.find (".")
17186  NewPos = Pos + NewDot - Dot
17187  if Decimals == 0 :
17188  NewLen = len(NewStr)
17189  NewPos = Pos + NewLen - Len
17190  button.delete(0, END) # remove old entry
17191  button.insert(0, NewStr) # insert new entry
17192  button.icursor(NewPos) # resets the insertion cursor
17193 #
17194 #
17195 def onSpinBoxScroll(event):
17196  spbox = event.widget
17197  if sys.version_info[0] == 3 and sys.version_info[1] > 6: # Spin Boxes do this automatically in Python > 3.6 apparently
17198  return
17199  if event.num == 4 or event.delta > 0: # if event.delta > 0: # increment digit
17200  spbox.invoke('buttonup')
17201  if event.num == 5 or event.delta < 0:
17202  spbox.invoke('buttondown')

17544 def BAWG2X():
17545  global AWG_2X, devx, AWGAIOMode, AWGBIOMode, BisCompA
17546 
17547  ReMakeAWGwaves()
17548  if AWG_2X.get() == 0: # configure board for both AWG channels at 1X sampling
17549  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, 0x24, 0x0, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set to addr DAC A
17550  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, 0x25, 0x1, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set to addr DAC B
17551  elif AWG_2X.get() == 1: # configure board for single AWG channel A at 2X sampling
17552  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, 0x24, 0x0, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set to addr DAC A
17553  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, 0x25, 0x0, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set t0 addr DAC A
17554  if AWGBIOMode.get() == 0: # if channel b is not in split I/O mode turn off output
17555  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, 0x51, 40, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set IN3 switch to open
17556  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, 0x51, 52, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set IN3 switch to open
17557  BisCompA.set(0)
17558  elif AWG_2X.get() == 2: # configure board for single AWG channel B at 2X sampling
17559  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, 0x24, 0x1, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set to addr DAC B
17560  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, 0x25, 0x1, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set to addr DAC B
17561  if AWGAIOMode.get() == 0: # if channel a is not in split I/O mode turn off output
17562  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, 0x51, 35, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set IN3 switch to open
17563  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, 0x51, 51, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set IN3 switch to open
17564  BisCompA.set(0)
17565 #
17566 def DestroyAWGScreen():
17567  global awgwindow, AWGScreenStatus
17568 
17569  # AWGScreenStatus.set(0)
17570  awgwindow.iconify()

17769 def SetDualMuxMode():
17770  global AWGAIOMode, AWGBIOMode, ShowC1_V, DualMuxMode, CHAlab, CHAofflab
17771  global CHB_Clab, CHB_Dlab, CHB_Cofflab, CHB_Dofflab, CHB_cbc, CHB_cbd
17772 
17773  if DualMuxMode.get() == 1:
17774  AWGAIOMode.set(1) # force awg A split I/O mode
17775  AWGBIOMode.set(1) # force awg B split I/O mode
17776  ShowC1_V.set(0) # force A voltage trace off
17777  CHB_cbc.config(text="CA-C")
17778  CHB_cbd.config(text="CA-D")
17779  CHB_Clab.config(text="CA-C V/Div")
17780  CHB_Dlab.config(text="CA-D V/Div")
17781  CHB_Cofflab.config(text="CA-C Pos")
17782  CHB_Dofflab.config(text="CA-D Pos")
17783  BAWGEnab() # update AWG settings
17784  # Gray out main Channel A controls
17785  CHAlab.config(style="SGray.TButton")
17786  CHAofflab.config(style="SGray.TButton")
17787  else:
17788  ShowC1_V.set(1) # force A voltage trace on
17789  CHB_cbc.config(text="CB-C")
17790  CHB_cbd.config(text="CB-D")
17791  CHB_Clab.config(text="CB-C V/Div")
17792  CHB_Dlab.config(text="CB-D V/Div")
17793  CHB_Cofflab.config(text="CB-C Pos")
17794  CHB_Dofflab.config(text="CB-D Pos")
17795  # Reset main Channel A control colors
17796  CHAlab.config(style="Rtrace1.TButton")
17797  CHAofflab.config(style="Rtrace1.TButton")
17798 #
17799 def SetChopMuxMode():
17800  global ChopMuxMode, AWGAIOMode, AWGBIOMode, AWGAMode, AWGAAmplEntry, AWGAOffsetEntry, AWGAFreqEntry
17801  global AWGAPhaseEntry, SAMPLErate, ShowC1_V, ShowC2_V, TgInput
17802 
17803  if ChopMuxMode.get() > 0: # set AWG A to a square wave at 25 KHz 0.5 to 4.5 V, mode = SVMI_SPLIT
17804  AWGAIOMode.set(1) # force awg A split I/O mode
17805  AWGAMode.set(0) # force awg A mode to SVMI
17806  BAWGAModeLabel()
17807  AWGAShape.set(4) # force awg A to square shape
17808  AWGAAmplEntry.delete(0,"end")
17809  AWGAAmplEntry.insert(0,0.5) # force awg A Min value to 0.5 V
17810  AWGAOffsetEntry.delete(0,"end")
17811  AWGAOffsetEntry.insert(0,4.5) # force awg A Max value to 4.5 V
17812  AWGAFreqEntry.delete(0,"end")
17813  AWGAFreqEntry.insert(0,SAMPLErate/4) # force awg A Freg value to 25000 (1/4 base sample rate)
17814  AWGAPhaseEntry.delete(0,"end")
17815  AWGAPhaseEntry.insert(0,0) # force awg A Phase value to 0
17816  ReMakeAWGwaves()
17817  AWGBIOMode.set(1) # force awg A split I/O mode
17818  BAWGBModeLabel()
17819  ShowC1_V.set(0) # force A voltage trace off
17820  ShowC2_V.set(0) # force B voltage trace off
17821  TgInput.set(0) # force main Trigger source to none
17822  CHAlab.config(style="SGray.TButton")
17823  CHAofflab.config(style="SGray.TButton")
17824  else:
17825  CHAlab.config(style="Rtrace1.TButton")
17826  CHAofflab.config(style="Rtrace1.TButton")
17827

17851 def BodeCaresize(event):
17852  global Bodeca, GRWBP, XOLBP, GRHBP, Y0TBP, CANVASwidthBP, CANVASheightBP, FontSize

17854  CANVASwidthBP = event.width - 4
17855  CANVASheightBP = event.height - 4

17860 def BStepSync():
17861  global FStepSync, DevOne
17862 
17863  if FStepSync.get() == 0:
17864  Tval = devx.ctrl_transfer( 0xc0, 0x91, 0, 0, 0, 1, 100) # set PIO-0 to Z
17865  elif FStepSync.get() == 1:
17866  devx.ctrl_transfer( 0x40, 0x50, 0, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set PIO-0 to 0
17867  elif FStepSync.get() == 2:
17868  devx.ctrl_transfer( 0x40, 0x51, 0, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set PIO-0 to 1
17869 #
17870 def BSweepSync():
17871  global FSweepSync, DevOne
17872 
17873  if FSweepSync.get() == 0:
17874  Tval = devx.ctrl_transfer( 0xc0, 0x91, 1, 0, 0, 1, 100) # set PIO-1 to Z
17875  elif FSweepSync.get() == 1:
17876  devx.ctrl_transfer( 0x40, 0x50, 1, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set PIO-1 to 0
17877  elif FSweepSync.get() == 2:
17878  devx.ctrl_transfer( 0x40, 0x51, 1, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set PIO-1 to 1
17879 #
17880 def BDSweepFromFile():
17881  global BDSweepFile, FileSweepFreq, FileSweepAmpl
17882 
17883  if BDSweepFile.get() > 0:
17884  # Read values from CVS file
17885  filename = askopenfilename(defaultextension = ".csv", filetypes=[("CSV files", "*.csv")], parent = bodewindow)
17886  try:
17887  CSVFile = open(filename)
17888  csv_f = csv.reader(CSVFile)
17889  FileSweepFreq = []
17890  FileSweepAmpl = []
17891  for row in csv_f:
17892  try:
17893  FileSweepFreq.append(float(row[0]))
17894  FileSweepAmpl.append(float(row[1]))
17895  except:
17896  print( 'skipping non-numeric row')
17897  FileSweepFreq = numpy.array(FileSweepFreq)
17898  FileSweepAmpl = numpy.array(FileSweepAmpl)
17899  MaxAmpl = numpy.amax(FileSweepAmpl)
17900  NormAmpl = MaxAmpl
17901  s = askstring("Normalize Max Amplitude", "Max Amplitude = " + str(MaxAmpl) + "\n\n Enter New Max value:\n in dB", parent = bodewindow)
17902  if (s == None): # If Cancel pressed, then None
17903  return()
17904  try: # Error if for example no numeric characters or OK pressed without input (s = "")
17905  v = int(s)
17906  except:
17907  s = "error"
17908 
17909  if s != "error":
17910  NormAmpl = MaxAmpl - v
17911  else:
17912  NormAmpl = MaxAmpl
17913  FileSweepAmpl = FileSweepAmpl - NormAmpl # normalize max amplitude to requested dBV
17914  CSVFile.close()
17915  StopBodeEntry.delete(0,"end")
17916  StopBodeEntry.insert(0,FileSweepFreq[len(FileSweepFreq)-1])
17917  StartBodeEntry.delete(0,"end")
17918  StartBodeEntry.insert(0,FileSweepFreq[0])
17919  SweepStepBodeEntry.delete(0,"end")
17920  SweepStepBodeEntry.insert(0,len(FileSweepFreq))
17921  except:
17922  showwarning("WARNING","No such file found or wrong format!", parent = bodewindow)
17923 #

18238 def FreqCaresize(event):
18239  global Freqca, GRWF, XOLF, GRHF, Y0TF, CANVASwidthF, CANVASheightF, FontSize
18240 
18241  CANVASwidthF = event.width - 4
18242  CANVASheightF = event.height - 4
18243  GRWF = CANVASwidthF - (2 * X0LF) # new grid width
18244  GRHF = CANVASheightF - int(10 * FontSize) # new grid height
18245  UpdateFreqAll()

18248 def MakeSpectrumWindow():

18510 def XYcaresize(event):
18511  global XYca, GRWXY, XOLXY, GRHXY, Y0TXY, CANVASwidthXY, CANVASheightXY, FontSize
18512  global YminXY, YmaxXY, XminXY, XmaxXY
18513 
18514  CANVASwidthXY = event.width - 4
18515  CANVASheightXY = event.height - 4
18516  GRWXY = CANVASwidthXY - int(2.25 * FontSize) - X0LXY # 18 new grid width
18517  GRHXY = CANVASheightXY - int(10 * FontSize) # new grid height
18518  YminXY = Y0TXY # Minimum position of time grid (top)
18519  YmaxXY = Y0TXY + GRHXY # Maximum position of time grid (bottom)
18520  XminXY = X0LXY # Minimum position of time grid (left)
18521  XmaxXY = X0LXY + GRWXY # Maximum position of time grid (right)
18522  UpdateXYAll()

18769 def SelfCalibration():

19114  CHAVSrN45Raw = CHAVSrN45Raw / 1000.0 # calculate average
19115  CHAISrN45Raw = CHAISrN45Raw / 1000.0
19116  CHBVSrN45Raw = CHBVSrN45Raw / 1000.0 # calculate average
19117  CHBISrN45Raw = CHBISrN45Raw / 1000.0
19118  VString = "CA 50 Src -45 " + ' {0:.4f} '.format(CHAVSrN45Raw) # format with 4 decimal places
19119  labelSIAN.config(text = VString) # change displayed value
19120  VString = "CB 50 Src -45 " + ' {0:.4f} '.format(CHBVSrN45Raw) # format with 4 decimal places
19121  labelSIBN.config(text = VString) # change displayed value
19122  # return all switches to open
19123  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, 0x51, 32, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set 2.5 V switch to open
19124  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, 0x51, 33, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set GND switch to open
19125  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, 0x51, 37, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set CHB 2.5 V switch to open
19126  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, 0x51, 38, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set CHB GND switch to open
19127  # Caculate voltage gain errors
19128  #
19129  CHAF25V = CHAF25vRaw * ( AD584act / CHA584Raw )
19130  CHBF25V = CHBF25vRaw * ( AD584act / CHB584Raw )
19131  #
19132  CHASr5v = CHASr5vRaw * ( AD584act / CHA584Raw ) # calculate actual voltage
19133  CHBSr5v = CHBSr5vRaw * ( AD584act / CHB584Raw ) # calculate actual voltage
19134  #
19135  CHA2p5 = CHA2p5Raw * ( AD584act / CHA584Raw )
19136  # print "calculated fixed 2.5 from CHA ", CHA2p5
19137  CHB2p5 = CHB2p5Raw * ( AD584act / CHB584Raw )
19138  # print "calculated fixed 2.5 from CHB ", CHB2p5
19139  #
19140  CHAActSrI = CHASr5v / OnBoardRes # adjust resistor value to include switch ron
19141  CHBActSrI = CHBSr5v / OnBoardRes # adjust resistor value to include switch ron
19142  #
19143  CHAActSnkI = CHASr0vRaw - CHA2p5 / OnBoardRes # adjust resistor value to include switch ron
19144  CHBActSnkI = CHBSr0vRaw - CHB2p5 / OnBoardRes # adjust resistor value to include switch ron
19145  #
19146  CHASr0i = CHAVSr0iRaw * ( AD584act / CHA584Raw )
19147  CHASr0iAct = CHASr0i / OnBoardRes # adjust resistor value to include switch ron
19148  CHASr100 = CHAVSr100Raw * ( AD584act / CHA584Raw )
19149  CHASrI100Act = (CHASr100 - CHA2p5) / OnBoardRes # adjust resistor value to include switch ron
19150  CHASrN45 = CHAVSrN45Raw * ( AD584act / CHA584Raw )
19151  CHASrIN45Act = (CHASrN45 - CHA2p5) / OnBoardRes # adjust resistor value to include switch ron
19152  #
19153  CHBSr0i = CHBVSr0iRaw * ( AD584act / CHB584Raw )
19154  CHBSr0iAct = CHBSr0i / OnBoardRes # adjust resistor value to include switch ron
19155  CHBSr100 = CHBVSr100Raw * ( AD584act / CHB584Raw )
19156  CHBSrI100Act = (CHBSr100 - CHB2p5) / OnBoardRes # adjust resistor value to include switch ron
19157  CHBSrN45 = CHBVSrN45Raw * ( AD584act / CHB584Raw )
19158  CHBSrIN45Act = (CHBSrN45 - CHB2p5) / OnBoardRes # adjust resistor value to include switch ron
19159  # Write cal factors to file
19160  #
19161  CalFile.write('# Channel A, measure V\n')
19162  CalFile.write('</>\n')
19163  CalFile.write('<0.0000, ' + '{0:.4f}'.format(CHAGndRaw) + '>\n')
19164  CalFile.write('<' + '{0:.4f}'.format(AD584act) + ', ' + '{0:.4f}'.format(CHA584Raw) + '>\n')
19165  CalFile.write('<>\n')
19166  CalFile.write('\n')
19167  #
19168  CalFile.write('# Channel A, measure I\n')
19169  CalFile.write('</>\n')
19170  CalFile.write('<0.0000, ' + '{0:.4f}'.format(CHAI02p5Raw) + '>\n')
19171  CalFile.write('<' + '{0:.4f}'.format(CHAActSrI) + ', ' + '{0:.4f}'.format(CHAISr5vRaw) + '>\n')
19172  # CalFile.write('<' + '{0:.4f}'.format(CHAISr0vRaw) + ', ' + '{0:.4f}'.format(CHAActSnkI) + '>\n')
19173  CalFile.write('<' + '{0:.4f}'.format(-CHAActSrI) + ', ' + '{0:.4f}'.format(-CHAISr5vRaw) + '>\n')
19174  CalFile.write('<>\n')
19175  CalFile.write('\n')
19176  #
19177  CalFile.write('# Channel A, source V\n')
19178  CalFile.write('</>\n')
19179  CalFile.write('<0.0000, ' + '{0:.4f}'.format(CHAF0vRaw) + '>\n')
19180  CalFile.write('<4.5000, ' + '{0:.4f}'.format(CHAF25V) + '>\n')
19181  CalFile.write('<>\n')
19182  CalFile.write('\n')
19183  #
19184  CalFile.write('# Channel A, source I\n')
19185  CalFile.write('</>\n')
19186  CalFile.write('<0.0000, ' + '{0:.4f}'.format(CHAISr0iRaw) + '>\n')
19187  CalFile.write('<0.045, ' + '{0:.4f}'.format(CHASrI100Act) + '>\n')
19188  CalFile.write('<-0.0450, ' + '{0:.4f}'.format(CHASrIN45Act) + '>\n')
19189  CalFile.write('<>\n')
19190  CalFile.write('\n')
19191  #
19192  CalFile.write('# Channel B, measure V\n')
19193  CalFile.write('</>\n')
19194  CalFile.write('<0.0000, ' + '{0:.4f}'.format(CHBGndRaw) + '>\n')
19195  CalFile.write('<' + '{0:.4f}'.format(AD584act) + ', ' + '{0:.4f}'.format(CHB584Raw) + '>\n')
19196  CalFile.write('<>\n')
19197  CalFile.write('\n')
19198  #
19199  CalFile.write('# Channel B, measure I\n')
19200  CalFile.write('</>\n')
19201  CalFile.write('<0.0000, ' + '{0:.4f}'.format(CHBI02p5Raw) + '>\n')
19202  CalFile.write('<' + '{0:.4f}'.format(CHBActSrI) + ', ' + '{0:.4f}'.format(CHBISr5vRaw) + '>\n')
19203  # CalFile.write('<' + '{0:.4f}'.format(CHBISr0vRaw) + ', ' + '{0:.4f}'.format(CHBActSnkI) + '>\n')
19204  CalFile.write('<' + '{0:.4f}'.format(-CHBActSrI) + ', ' + '{0:.4f}'.format(-CHBISr5vRaw) + '>\n')
19205  CalFile.write('<>\n')
19206  CalFile.write('\n')
19207  #
19208  CalFile.write('# Channel B, source V\n')
19209  CalFile.write('</>\n')
19210  CalFile.write('<0.0000, ' + '{0:.4f}'.format(CHBF0vRaw) + '>\n')
19211  CalFile.write('<4.5000, ' + '{0:.4f}'.format(CHAF25V) + '>\n')
19212  CalFile.write('<>\n')
19213  CalFile.write('\n')
19214  #
19215  CalFile.write('# Channel B source I\n')
19216  CalFile.write('</>\n')
19217  CalFile.write('<0.0000, ' + '{0:.4f}'.format(CHBISr0iRaw) + '>\n')
19218  CalFile.write('<0.045, ' + '{0:.4f}'.format(CHBSrI100Act) + '>\n')
19219  CalFile.write('<-0.0450, ' + '{0:.4f}'.format(CHBSrIN45Act) + '>\n')
19220  CalFile.write('<>\n')
19221  #
19222  CalFile.close()
19223  showinfo("Finish","Successfully measured cal factors!", parent=calwindow)
19224  if askyesno("Write cal", "Write Cal Data to Board?", parent=calwindow):
19225  devx.write_calibration(filename)
19226  #print "wrote new " , filename

19229  CHA.mode = Mode.HI_Z_SPLIT # Put CHA in Hi Z split mode
19230  CHB.mode = Mode.HI_Z_SPLIT # Put CHB in Hi Z split mode
19231  contloop = 0
19232  discontloop = 1
19233  # session.cancel()
19234  calwindow.destroy()

19329 def SPIShiftOut(DValue):
19330  global devx, PIO_0, PIO_1, PIO_2, PIO_3, SCLKPort, SDATAPort, SLATCHPort
19331 
19332  binstr = bin(DValue)
19333  binlen = len(binstr)
19334  datastr = binstr[2:binlen]
19335  datalen = len(datastr)
19336  if datalen < 16:
19337  datastr = str.rjust(datastr , 16 , '0')
19338  datalen = len(datastr)
19339  i = 1
19340  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, 0x50, SLATCHPort.get(), 0, 0, 0, 100) # fsync to 0
19341  while i < datalen+1:
19342  # sending 0x50 = set to 0, 0x51 = set to 1
19343  D1code = 0x50 + int(datastr[i-1])
19344  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, D1code, SDATAPort.get(), 0, 0, 0, 100) # data bit
19345  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, 0x51, SCLKPort.get(), 0, 0, 0, 100) # sclk to 1
19346  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, 0x50, SCLKPort.get(), 0, 0, 0, 100) # sclk to 0
19347  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, 0x51, SCLKPort.get(), 0, 0, 0, 100) # sclk to 1
19348  i = i + 1
19349  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, 0x51, SLATCHPort.get(), 0, 0, 0, 100) # fsync to 1
19350 #
19351 def SetAD9833(temp):
19352  global FminEntry, HtMulEntry, MinigenFout, MinigenMode, etssrlab, EnableMinigenMode # , Fclk, Fout
19353  global Two28, mclk, EnableHSsampling, MinigenScreenStatus, ETSts, Two_X_Sample
19354 
19355  #
19356  if MinigenScreenStatus.get() == 0:
19357  #SRstring = "ET Sample Rate = " + str(SAMPLErate*MulX)
19358  #etssrlab.config(text=SRstring)
19359  return
19360  #
19361  if EnableMinigenMode == 2:
19362  MinigenMode.set(40)
19363  #
19364  try:
19365  FminE = float(eval(FminEntry.get()))*1000
19366  except:
19367  if EnableHSsampling > 0:
19368  FminEntry.delete(0,END)
19369  FminEntry.insert(0, FminE/1000)
19370  if MulX == 1:
19371  Fmin = FminE
19372  else:
19373  Fmin = FminE - (FminE/MulX)
19374  #
19375  MinigenFout.delete(0,"end")
19376  MinigenFout.insert(0,Fmin)

19381 def BSendMG():
19382  global MinigenFclk, MinigenFout, MinigenMode
19383  global Two28, SCLKPort, SDATAPort, SLATCHPort
19384 
19385  DValue = 8192 + MinigenMode.get()
19386  SPIShiftOut(DValue)
19387  try:
19388  fout = float(eval(MinigenFout.get()))
19389  except:
19390  MinigenFout.delete(0,"end")
19391  MinigenFout.insert(0,100)
19392  try:
19393  mclk = float(eval(MinigenFclk.get()))*1000000 # convert from MHz to Hz
19394  except:
19395  MingenFclk.delete(0,"end")
19396  MinigenFclk.insert(0,16)
19397  Freg = int((fout*Two28)/mclk)
19398  Foutstr = bin(Freg)
19399  Foutlen = len(Foutstr)
19400  datastr = Foutstr[2:Foutlen]
19401  datalen = len(datastr)
19402  if datalen < 28:
19403  datastr = str.rjust(datastr , 28 , '0')
19404  datalen = len(datastr)
19405  Fmsb = '0b01' + datastr[0:14]
19406  Flsb = '0b01' + datastr[14:]
19407  FValue = int(eval(Flsb))
19408  SPIShiftOut(FValue)
19409  FValue = int(eval(Fmsb))
19410  SPIShiftOut(FValue)

19506 def DA1ShiftOut(D1Value, D2Value):
19507  global devx
19508  global PIO_0, PIO_1, PIO_2, PIO_3
19509 
19510  binstr = bin(D1Value)
19511  binlen = len(binstr)
19512  data1str = binstr[2:binlen]
19513  datalen = len(data1str)
19514  if datalen < 16:
19515  data1str = str.rjust(data1str , 16 , '0')
19516  datalen = len(data1str)
19517  #
19518  binstr = bin(D2Value)
19519  binlen = len(binstr)
19520  data2str = binstr[2:binlen]
19521  datalen = len(data2str)
19522  if datalen < 16:
19523  data2str = str.rjust(data2str , 16 , '0')
19524  datalen = len(data2str)
19525  # sync --> PIO 0
19526  # D0 --> PIO 1
19527  # D1 --> PIO 2
19528  # SCLK --> PIO 3
19529  i = 1
19530 #
19531  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, 0x50, 0, 0, 0, 0, 100) # sync to 0
19532  while i < datalen+1:
19533  # sending 0x50 = set to 0, 0x51 = set to 1
19534  D1code = 0x50 + int(data1str[i-1])
19535  D2code = 0x50 + int(data2str[i-1])
19536  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, D1code, PIO_1, 0, 0, 0, 100) # data 0 bit
19537  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, D2code, PIO_2, 0, 0, 0, 100) # data 1 bit
19538  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, 0x51, PIO_3, 0, 0, 0, 100) # sclk to 1
19539  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, 0x50, PIO_3, 0, 0, 0, 100) # sclk to 0
19540  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, 0x51, PIO_3, 0, 0, 0, 100) # sclk to 1
19541  i = i + 1
19542  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, 0x51, PIO_0, 0, 0, 0, 100) # sync to 1
19543  #
19544 def BSendDA1():
19545  global DAC1Entry, DAC2Entry, DAC3Entry, DAC4Entry, REFEntry
19546 
19547  try:
19548  RefValue = float(eval(REFEntry.get()))
19549  except:
19550  RefValue = 3.3
19551  try:
19552  D1Value = float(eval(DAC1Entry.get()))
19553  except:
19554  D1Value = 0.0129
19555  D1Code = int((D1Value/RefValue)*255)
19556  if D1Code > 255:
19557  D1Code = 255
19558  D1Code = D1Code + 0x2000
19559  try:
19560  D2Value = float(eval(DAC2Entry.get()))
19561  except:
19562  D2Value = 0.0129
19563  D2Code = int((D2Value/RefValue)*255)
19564  if D2Code > 255:
19565  D2Code = 255
19566  D2Code = D2Code + 0x2400
19567  try:
19568  D3Value = float(eval(DAC3Entry.get()))
19569  except:
19570  D3Value = 0.0129
19571  D3Code = int((D3Value/RefValue)*255)
19572  if D3Code > 255:
19573  D3Code = 255
19574  D3Code = D3Code + 0x2000
19575  try:
19576  D4Value = float(eval(DAC4Entry.get()))
19577  except:
19578  D4Value = 0.0129
19579  D4Code = int((D4Value/RefValue)*255)
19580  if D4Code > 255:
19581  D4Code = 255
19582  D4Code = D4Code + 0x2400
19583  #
19584  DA1ShiftOut(D1Code, D3Code)
19585  DA1ShiftOut(D2Code, D4Code)
