19645 def DigPotShiftOut(DValue):
19646  global devx, SingleDualPot
19647  global PIO_0, PIO_1, PIO_2, PIO_3
19648 
19649  binstr = bin(DValue)
19650  binlen = len(binstr)
19651  datastr = binstr[2:binlen]
19652  datalen = len(datastr)
19653  if SingleDualPot.get() == 0: # send 10 bits of data
19654  if datalen < 10:
19655  datastr = str.rjust(datastr , 10 , '0')
19656  datalen = len(datastr)
19657  if SingleDualPot.get() == 1: # send 8 bits of data
19658  if datalen < 8:
19659  datastr = str.rjust(datastr , 8 , '0')
19660  datalen = len(datastr)
19661  if SingleDualPot.get() == 2: # send 8 bits of data
19662  if datalen < 8:
19663  datastr = str.rjust(datastr , 8 , '0')
19664  datalen = len(datastr)
19665  i = 1
19666  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, 0x50, PIO_3, 0, 0, 0, 100) # clock to 0
19667  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, 0x50, PIO_0, 0, 0, 0, 100) # CS to 0
19668  while i < datalen+1:
19669  # CS --> PIO 0
19670  # D0 --> PIO 1
19671  # D1 --> PIO 2
19672  # SCLK --> PIO 3
19673  D1code = 0x50 + int(datastr[i-1])
19674  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, D1code, PIO_1, 0, 0, 0, 100) # data bit
19675  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, 0x51, PIO_3, 0, 0, 0, 100) # clock to 1
19676  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, 0x50, PIO_3, 0, 0, 0, 100) # clock to 0
19677  i = i + 1
19678  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, 0x51, 0, 0, 0, 0, 100) # CS to 1
19679  #
19680 def DigPotSend(Temp):
19681  global DigPot1, DigPot2, DigPot3, DigPot4, SendPot1, SendPot2, SendPot3, SendPot4
19682  global SingleDualPot
19683 
19684  if SingleDualPot.get() == 0 or SingleDualPot.get() == 1:
19685  NumTaps = 255
19686  if SingleDualPot.get() == 2:
19687  NumTaps = 63
19688  try:
19689  DValue1 = DigPot1.get()
19690  if DValue1 > NumTaps:
19691  DValue1 = NumTaps
19692  except:
19693  DValue1 = 0
19694  try:
19695  DValue2 = DigPot2.get()
19696  if DValue2 > NumTaps:
19697  DValue2 = NumTaps
19698  except:
19699  DValue2 = 0
19700  try:
19701  DValue3 = DigPot3.get()
19702  if DValue3 > NumTaps:
19703  DValue3 = NumTaps
19704  except:
19705  DValue3 = 0
19706  try:
19707  DValue4 = DigPot4.get()
19708  if DValue4 > NumTaps:
19709  DValue4 = NumTaps
19710  except:
19711  DValue4 = 0
19712  if SendPot1.get() > 0:
19713  DigPotShiftOut(DValue1)
19714  if SendPot2.get() > 0:
19715  DigPotShiftOut(DValue2+NumTaps+1)
19716  if SendPot3.get() > 0:
19717  DigPotShiftOut(DValue3+2*(NumTaps+1))
19718  if SendPot4.get() > 0:
19719  DigPotShiftOut(DValue4+3*(NumTaps+1))

19795 def BSendGS():
19796  global serialwindow, GenericSerialStatus, SCLKPort, SDATAPort, SLATCHPort, SLatchPhase, SClockPhase
19797  global NumBitsEntry, DataBitsEntry, devx, SerDirection, DValue, NumBits, AD5626SerialStatus, AD5626Entry
19798 
19799  if AD5626SerialStatus.get() == 0:
19800  try:
19801  DValue = int(eval(DataBitsEntry.get()))
19802  if DValue < 0:
19803  DValue = 0
19804  except:
19805  DValue = 0
19806  try:
19807  NumBits = int(NumBitsEntry.get())
19808  if NumBits < 1:
19809  NumBits = 1
19810  except:
19811  NumBits = 8
19812  else:
19813  try:
19814  DValue = int(eval(AD5626Entry.get())*1000)
19815  if DValue < 0:
19816  DValue = 0
19817  AD5626Entry.delete(0,"end")
19818  AD5626Entry.insert(0,'0.000')
19819  if DValue > 4095:
19820  DValue = 4095
19821  AD5626Entry.delete(0,"end")
19822  AD5626Entry.insert(0,DValue/1000.0)
19823  except:
19824  DValue = 0
19825  AD5626Entry.delete(0,"end")
19826  AD5626Entry.insert(0,'0.000')
19827  NumBits = 12
19828  # print DValue
19829  binstr = bin(DValue)
19830  binlen = len(binstr)
19831  datastr = binstr[2:binlen]
19832  datalen = len(datastr)
19833  if datalen < NumBits:
19834  datastr = str.rjust(datastr , NumBits , '0')
19835  datalen = len(datastr)
19836  if SLatchPhase.get() == 0:
19837  LatchInt = 0x50
19838  LatchEnd = 0x51
19839  else:
19840  LatchInt = 0x51
19841  LatchEnd = 0x50
19842  if AD5626SerialStatus.get() > 0:
19843  LatchInt = 0x51
19844  LatchEnd = 0x50
19845  if SClockPhase.get() == 0:
19846  ClockInt = 0x50
19847  ClockEnd = 0x51
19848  else:
19849  ClockInt = 0x51
19850  ClockEnd = 0x50
19851  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, ClockInt, SCLKPort.get(), 0, 0, 0, 100) # clock to start value
19852  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, LatchInt, SLATCHPort.get(), 0, 0, 0, 100) # CS to start value
19853  i = 1
19854  while i < datalen+1:
19855  if SerDirection.get() == 1: # for MSB first
19856  D1code = 0x50 + int(datastr[datalen-i]) # 0x50 = set to 0, 0x51 = set to 1
19857  else:
19858  D1code = 0x50 + int(datastr[i-1]) # for LSB first
19859  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, D1code, SDATAPort.get(), 0, 0, 0, 100) # data bit
19860  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, ClockEnd, SCLKPort.get(), 0, 0, 0, 100) # clock to end value
19861  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, ClockInt, SCLKPort.get(), 0, 0, 0, 100) # clock to start value
19862  i = i + 1
19863  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, ClockEnd, SCLKPort.get(), 0, 0, 0, 100) # clock to end value
19864  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, LatchEnd, SLATCHPort.get(), 0, 0, 0, 100) # CS to end value
19865  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, LatchInt, SLATCHPort.get(), 0, 0, 0, 100) # CS to start value
19866  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, LatchEnd, SLATCHPort.get(), 0, 0, 0, 100) # CS to end value
19867

20129 def BuildBoxCarA():
20130  global BCALenEntry, DFiltACoef, DigFiltABoxCar, DifFiltALength
20131 
20132  if DigFiltABoxCar.get() == 0:
20133  return
20134 
20135  FLength = int(BCALenEntry.get())
20136  if FLength < 2:
20137  return
20138 
20139  DFiltACoef = [] # empty coef array
20140 
20141  for n in range(FLength):
20142  DFiltACoef.append(float(1.0/FLength))
20143 
20144  DFiltACoef = numpy.array(DFiltACoef)
20145  DifFiltALength.config(text = "Length = " + str(int(len(DFiltACoef)))) # change displayed length value
20146

20178 def BLoadDFiltA():
20179  global DFiltACoef, digfltwindow, DifFiltALength, DifFiltAFile
20180 
20181 # Read values from CVS file
20182  filename = askopenfilename(defaultextension = ".csv", filetypes=[("CSV files", "*.csv")], parent=digfltwindow)
20183  try:
20184  CSVFile = open(filename)
20185  csv_f = csv.reader(CSVFile)
20186  except:
20187  showwarning("WARNING","No such file found or wrong format!", parent=digfltwindow)
20188  return
20189  DFiltACoef = []
20190 
20191  for row in csv_f:
20192  try:
20193  DFiltACoef.append(float(row[0]))
20194  except:
20195  print( 'skipping non-numeric row')
20196  DFiltACoef = numpy.array(DFiltACoef)
20197  DifFiltALength.config(text = "Length = " + str(int(len(DFiltACoef)))) # change displayed length value
20198  DifFiltAFile.config(text = "File Name, " + os.path.basename(filename)) # change displayed file name
20199  CSVFile.close()
20200 #
20201 def BDFiltAMath():
20202  global DFiltACoef, digfltwindow, DifFiltALength, DifFiltAFile, DigFilterAString
20203 
20204  TempString = DigFilterAString
20205  DigFilterAString = askstring("CH A Filter Math Formula", "Current Formula: " + DigFilterAString + "\n\nNew Formula:\n", initialvalue=DigFilterAString, parent=digfltwindow)
20206  if (DigFilterAString == None): # If Cancel pressed, then None
20207  DigFilterAString = TempString
20208  return
20209  DFiltACoef = eval(DigFilterAString)
20210  DFiltACoef = numpy.array(DFiltACoef)
20211  coefsum = numpy.sum(DFiltACoef)
20212  DFiltACoef = DFiltACoef / coefsum
20213  DifFiltALength.config(text = "Length = " + str(int(len(DFiltACoef)))) # change displayed length value
20214  DifFiltAFile.config(text = "Using Filter A formula" ) # change displayed file name
20215

20290 def BExecuteFromString(): # global VBuffA,AWGAwaveform;VBuffA=AWGAwaveform
20291  global ExecString, LastCommand
20292 
20293  try:
20294  exec( ExecString.get() )
20295  LastCommand.config(text = ExecString.get() ) # change displayed last command
20296  except:
20297  LastCommand.config(text = "Syntax Error Encountered" ) # change displayed last command
20298  return()

20304  CANVASwidth = event.width - 4

20307  GRH = CANVASheight - (Y0T + (FontSize * 7)) # new grid height

20501 def SelectBoard():

20516  try:
20517  session.remove(dev2)

20519  except:

20528  except:

20531  session.remove(dev2)

20533  except:

20539  print( DevID)

20541  HWRevOne = str(devx.hwver)

20544

20546  if FWRevOne < 2.17:

20554  #
20555  # if session.continuous == 0:
20556  #session.start(0)
20557 
20566  devx.set_adc_mux(0)
20567  if devx.hwver == "F":
20568  print( "Rev F Board I/O ports set")
20569  PIO_0 = 28
20570  PIO_1 = 29
20571  PIO_2 = 47
20572  PIO_3 = 3
20573  PIO_4 = 4
20574  PIO_5 = 5
20575  PIO_6 = 6
20576  PIO_7 = 7
20577  else:
20578  PIO_0 = 0

20580  PIO_2 = 2
20581  PIO_3 = 3
20582  PIO_4 = 4
20583  PIO_5 = 5
20584  PIO_6 = 6
20585  PIO_7 = 7

20669 def SetSampleRate():
20670  global SAMPLErate, BaseSampleRate, AWGSAMPLErate, session, ETSStatus, etssrlab, BaseRatesb
20671  global Two_X_Sample, ADC_Mux_Mode, rtsrlab, RUNstatus
20672 
20673  #
20674  WasRunning = 0
20675  if (RUNstatus.get() == 1):
20676  WasRunning = 1
20677  BStop() # Force Stop loop if running
20678  try:
20679  NewRate = int(BaseRatesb.get())
20680  if NewRate <= 100000: # rate has to be less than or equal to 100,000
20681  BaseSampleRate = NewRate
20682  else:
20683  BaseSampleRate = 100000
20684  BaseRatesb.delete(0,"end")
20685  BaseRatesb.insert(0,BaseSampleRate)
20686  SAMPLErate = BaseSampleRate # Scope sample rate
20687  except:
20688  donothing()
20689  session.configure(sample_rate=BaseSampleRate)
20690  BaseSampleRate = session.sample_rate
20691  #print("Session sample rate: " + str(session.sample_rate), BaseSampleRate)
20692  SAMPLErate = BaseSampleRate # Scope sample rate
20693  #print("Session sample rate: " + str(session.sample_rate), SAMPLErate)
20694  AWGSAMPLErate = BaseSampleRate
20695  if ETSStatus.get() > 0:
20696  SRstring = "RT Sample Rate = " + str(BaseSampleRate)
20697  rtsrlab.config(text=SRstring)
20698  ETSUpdate()
20699  BaseRatesb.delete(0,"end")
20700  BaseRatesb.insert(0,BaseSampleRate)
20701  ReMakeAWGwaves() # remake AWG waveforms for new rate
20702  if (WasRunning == 1):
20703  WasRunning = 0
20704  BStart() # restart loop if was running

20706 def onStopfreqScroll(event):
20707  global StopFreqEntry, Two_X_Sample, ADC_Mux_Mode, FWRevOne
20708 
20709  onTextScroll(event)
20710  try:
20711  StopFrequency = float(StopFreqEntry.get())
20712  except:
20713  StopFreqEntry.delete(0,"end")
20714  StopFreqEntry.insert(0,50000)
20715  StopFrequency = 50000
20716  if FWRevOne > 2.16:
20717  if StopFrequency >= 50000:
20718  Two_X_Sample.set(1)
20719  ADC_Mux_Mode.set(0)
20720  SetADC_Mux()
20721  else:
20722  Two_X_Sample.set(0)
20723  ADC_Mux_Mode.set(0)
20724  SetADC_Mux()
20725 #
20726 def onStopBodeScroll(event):
20727  global StopBodeEntry, Two_X_Sample, ADC_Mux_Mode, FWRevOne
20728 
20729  onTextScroll(event)
20730  try:
20731  StopFrequency = float(StopBodeEntry.get())
20732  except:
20733  StopBodeEntry.delete(0,"end")
20734  StopBodeEntry.insert(0,20000)
20735  StopFrequency = 20000
20736  if FWRevOne > 2.16:
20737  if StopFrequency >= 20000:
20738  Two_X_Sample.set(1)
20739  ADC_Mux_Mode.set(0)
20740  SetADC_Mux()
20741  else:
20742  Two_X_Sample.set(0)
20743  ADC_Mux_Mode.set(0)
20744  SetADC_Mux()

20746 def SetADC_Mux():
20747  global devx, SAMPLErate, BaseSampleRate, Two_X_Sample, ADC_Mux_Mode, CHA, CHB
20748  global v1_adc_conf, i1_adc_conf, v2_adc_conf, i2_adc_conf
20749  global AWGSync, discontloop, session, ADsignal1
20750 
20751  if Two_X_Sample.get() == 1:
20752  if ADC_Mux_Mode.get() == 0: # VA and VB
20753  devx.set_adc_mux(1)
20754  elif ADC_Mux_Mode.get() == 1: # IA and IB
20755  devx.set_adc_mux(2)
20756  elif ADC_Mux_Mode.get() == 2: # VA and IB
20757  # cycle trhough default mux values as starting point
20758  devx.set_adc_mux(2)
20759  # now set new mux values
20760  devx.set_adc_mux(7)
20761  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, 0x20, v1_adc_conf, 0, 0, 0, 100) # U12
20762  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, 0x21, i1_adc_conf, 0, 0, 0, 100) # U12
20763  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, 0x22, v2_adc_conf, 0, 0, 0, 100) # U11
20764  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, 0x22, i2_adc_conf, 0, 0, 0, 100) # U11
20765  time.sleep(0.1)
20766  elif ADC_Mux_Mode.get() == 3: # VB and IA
20767  # cycle trhough default mux values as starting point
20768  # now set new mux values
20769  devx.set_adc_mux(7)
20770  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, 0x20, v1_adc_conf, 0, 0, 0, 100) # U12
20771  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, 0x21, i1_adc_conf, 0, 0, 0, 100) # U12
20772  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, 0x22, v2_adc_conf, 0, 0, 0, 100) # U11
20773  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, 0x22, i2_adc_conf, 0, 0, 0, 100) # U11
20774  time.sleep(0.1)
20775  elif ADC_Mux_Mode.get() == 4: # VA and IA
20776  # cycle trhough default mux values as starting point
20777  devx.set_adc_mux(2)
20778  if AWGSync.get() > 0: # awg syn flag set so run in discontinuous mode
20779  if discontloop > 0:
20780  session.flush()
20781  else:
20782  discontloop = 1
20783  time.sleep(0.01)
20784  BAWGEnab()
20785  ADsignal1 = devx.get_samples(1000) # get samples for both channel A and B
20786 
20787  else: # running in continuous mode
20788  if session.continuous:
20789  ADsignal1 = devx.read(1000, -1, True) # get samples for both channel A and B
20790  # now set new mux values
20791  devx.set_adc_mux(4)
20792  elif ADC_Mux_Mode.get() == 5: # VB and IB
20793  # cycle trhough default mux values as starting point
20794  devx.set_adc_mux(2)
20795  if AWGSync.get() > 0: # awg syn flag set so run in discontinuous mode
20796  if discontloop > 0:
20797  session.flush()
20798  else:
20799  discontloop = 1
20800  time.sleep(0.01)
20801  BAWGEnab()
20802  ADsignal1 = devx.get_samples(1000) # get samples for both channel A and B
20803 
20804  else: # running in continuous mode
20805  if session.continuous:
20806  ADsignal1 = devx.read(1000, -1, True) # get samples for both channel A and B
20807  # now set new mux values
20808  devx.set_adc_mux(5)
20809  SAMPLErate = BaseSampleRate * 2 # set to 2X sample mode
20810  else:
20811  devx.set_adc_mux(0)
20812  SAMPLErate = BaseSampleRate
20813 #
20814 def TraceSelectADC_Mux():
20815  global ADC_Mux_Mode, Alternate_Sweep_Mode, ShowC1_V, ShowC1_I, ShowC2_V, ShowC2_I
20816 
20817  if ShowC1_V.get() == 1 and ShowC1_I.get() == 1 and ShowC2_V.get() == 1 and ShowC2_I.get() == 1:
20818  ADC_Mux_Mode.set(0) # All four traces
20819  Alternate_Sweep_Mode.set(1)
20820  elif ShowC1_V.get() == 1 and ShowC1_I.get() == 1 and ShowC2_V.get() == 1 and ShowC2_I.get() == 0:
20821  ADC_Mux_Mode.set(0) # three traces
20822  Alternate_Sweep_Mode.set(1)
20823  elif ShowC1_V.get() == 1 and ShowC1_I.get() == 1 and ShowC2_V.get() == 0 and ShowC2_I.get() == 1:
20824  ADC_Mux_Mode.set(0) # three traces
20825  Alternate_Sweep_Mode.set(1)
20826  elif ShowC1_V.get() == 0 and ShowC1_I.get() == 1 and ShowC2_V.get() == 1 and ShowC2_I.get() == 1:
20827  ADC_Mux_Mode.set(0) # three traces
20828  Alternate_Sweep_Mode.set(1)
20829  elif ShowC1_V.get() == 1 and ShowC1_I.get() == 0 and ShowC2_V.get() == 1 and ShowC2_I.get() == 1:
20830  ADC_Mux_Mode.set(0) # three traces
20831  Alternate_Sweep_Mode.set(1)
20832  #
20833  elif ShowC1_V.get() == 0 and ShowC1_I.get() == 1 and ShowC2_V.get() == 0 and ShowC2_I.get() == 1:
20834  ADC_Mux_Mode.set(1) # IA and IB
20835  Alternate_Sweep_Mode.set(0)
20836  elif ShowC1_V.get() == 0 and ShowC1_I.get() == 1 and ShowC2_V.get() == 0 and ShowC2_I.get() == 0:
20837  ADC_Mux_Mode.set(1) # just IA
20838  Alternate_Sweep_Mode.set(0)
20839  elif ShowC1_V.get() == 0 and ShowC1_I.get() == 0 and ShowC2_V.get() == 0 and ShowC2_I.get() == 1:
20840  ADC_Mux_Mode.set(1) # just IB
20841  Alternate_Sweep_Mode.set(0)
20842  elif ShowC1_V.get() == 1 and ShowC1_I.get() == 1 and ShowC2_V.get() == 0 and ShowC2_I.get() == 0:
20843  ADC_Mux_Mode.set(4) # VA and IA
20844  Alternate_Sweep_Mode.set(0)
20845  elif ShowC1_V.get() == 0 and ShowC1_I.get() == 0 and ShowC2_V.get() == 1 and ShowC2_I.get() == 1:
20846  ADC_Mux_Mode.set(5) # VB and IB
20847  Alternate_Sweep_Mode.set(0)
20848  else:
20849  ADC_Mux_Mode.set(0)
20850  Alternate_Sweep_Mode.set(0)
20851  SetADC_Mux()
20852  UpdateTimeTrace()

20854 def UpdateFirmware():
20855  global devx, dev0, dev1, dev2, session, BrdSel, CHA, CHB, DevID, MaxSamples
20856  global bcon, FWRevOne, HWRevOne, FWRevTwo, HWRevTwo, WRevThree, HWRevThree
20857

20859  if askyesno("Update current firmware","Flash new firmware to current device:\n(Yes) or (No)?"):
20860  filename = askopenfilename(defaultextension = ".bin", filetypes=[("Binary", "*.bin")])
20861  print( filename)
20862  #print DevID
20863  #print FWRevOne, HWRevOne # devx.fwver, devx.hwver
20864  try:
20865  print( "Cancel current session.")
20866  session.cancel()
20867  print( session.cancelled)
20868  session.end()
20869  print( "Waiting 5...")
20870  time.sleep(5)
20871  print( "Put board in Samba mode and flash firmware.")
20872  session.flash_firmware(filename)
20873  except:
20874  showwarning("Complete","Flash Firmware Complete: \n Un-plug board to cycle power.")
20875 
20883  showwarning("Complete","Flash Firmware Complete: \n Un-plug board to cycle power.")
20884  showwarning("Exit ALICE","Must Exit Program: \n Restart ALICE to continue.")
20885  Bcloseexit()

21100 def onMulXScroll(event):
21101  global Two_X_Sample, HtMulEntry, ETSts, etssrlab, SAMPLErate
21102 
21103  onTextScroll(event)
21104  # ETSUpdate()
21105  try:
21106  TscaleX = float(HtMulEntry.get())
21107  except:
21108  HtMulEntry.delete(0,END)
21109  HtMulEntry.insert(0, 1)
21110  if Two_X_Sample.get() == 0:
21111  ToffsetX = TscaleX/10.0 # set channel B offset to 1/10 the time scale only for 1X sampeling
21112  else:
21113  ToffsetX = 0
21114  ETSts.delete(0,"end")
21115  ETSts.insert(0,ToffsetX)
21116  SRstring = "ET Sample Rate = " + str(SAMPLErate*TscaleX)
21117  etssrlab.config(text=SRstring)
21118  #
21119  SetETSComp()
21120  SetAD9833(event)
21121 #
21122 def ETSUpdate():
21123  global FMulXEntry, MulXEntry, ETSStatus, ETSDisp, ETSDir, ETSts, eqivsamplerate, MaxETSrecord
21124  global SAMPLErate, DivXEntry, FOffEntry, FminDisp, DivX, FOff, MulX, Fmin, FMul, SAMPLErate, TIMEdiv
21125  global FminEntry, HtMulEntry, Two_X_Sample, DeBugMode
21126 
21127  if TIMEdiv > 0.2:
21128  MaxETSrecord = int(SAMPLErate * 10 * TIMEdiv / 1000.0)
21129  else:
21130  MaxETSrecord = int(SAMPLErate * 20 * TIMEdiv / 1000.0)
21131  if (MaxETSrecord*100) > MaxSamples:
21132  MaxETSrecord = MaxSamples / 100
21133  try:
21134  DivX = float(eval(DivXEntry.get()))
21135  if DivX < 2:
21136  DivX = 2
21137  if DivX > 75:
21138  DivX = 75
21139  DivXEntry.delete(0,END)
21140  DivXEntry.insert(0, DivX)
21141  except:
21142  DivXEntry.delete(0,END)
21143  DivXEntry.insert(0, DivX)
21144  #
21145  FOff = 25
21146  MulX = (DivX*SAMPLErate)/(100*FOff)
21147  while MulX > MaxETSrecord:
21148  FOff = FOff + 5
21149  MulX = (DivX*SAMPLErate)/(100*FOff)
21150  FOff = 0 - FOff
21151  if DeBugMode > 0:
21152  SRstring = "Rec Len Mul = " + str(MulX) + " samples"
21153  MulXEntry.config(text = SRstring) # change displayed value
21154  SRstring = "Offset = " + str(FOff) + " samples"
21155  FOffEntry.config(text = SRstring) # change displayed value
21156  baseFreq = SAMPLErate/DivX
21157  try:
21158  FMul = float(eval(FMulXEntry.get()))
21159  if FMul < 1:
21160  FMul = 1
21161  FMulXEntry.delete(0,END)
21162  FMulXEntry.insert(0, int(FMul))
21163  if FMul > 75:
21164  FMul = 75
21165  FMulXEntry.delete(0,END)
21166  FMulXEntry.insert(0, int(FMul))
21167  except:
21168  FMulXEntry.delete(0,END)
21169  FMulXEntry.insert(0, int(FMul))
21170  FreqMin = baseFreq * FMul
21171  SRstring = "Multiplied Freq = " + ' {0:.1f} '.format(FreqMin) + " Hz"
21172  FminDisp.config(text = SRstring) # change displayed value
21173  SRstring = "Base Frequency = " + ' {0:.2f} '.format(baseFreq) + " Hz"
21174  eqivsamplerate.config(text = SRstring) # change displayed value
21175  # calculate time scale multiplication factor
21176  try:
21177  MinFreq = eval(FminEntry.get()) * 1000 # convert KHz to Hz
21178  except:
21179  FminEntry.delete(0,END)
21180  FminEntry.insert(0, 25)
21181  #
21182  try: # catch for divide by zero
21183  TscaleX = int((MinFreq)/(DivX * (MinFreq - FreqMin)))
21184  except:
21185  TscaleX = 1
21186 
21187  if TscaleX > 0:
21188  ETSDir.set(0) # set sample direction to forward if positive
21189  else:
21190  ETSDir.set(1) # set sample direction to reverse if negative
21191  TscaleX = abs(TscaleX)
21192  if Two_X_Sample.get() == 0:
21193  ToffsetX = TscaleX/10.0 # set channel B offset to 1/10 the time scale only for 1X sampeling
21194  else:
21195  ToffsetX = 0
21196  ETSts.delete(0,"end")
21197  ETSts.insert(0,ToffsetX)
21198 
21199  HtMulEntry.delete(0,END)
21200  HtMulEntry.insert(0, TscaleX)
21201  SRstring = "RT Sample Rate = " + str(SAMPLErate)
21202  rtsrlab.config(text=SRstring)
21203  SRstring = "ET Sample Rate = " + str(SAMPLErate*TscaleX)
21204  etssrlab.config(text=SRstring)
21205 #

21484 def SetETSComp():
21485  global Auto_ETS_Comp, ETS_TC1, ETS_A1, ETS_TC2, ETS_A2
21486  global ets_TC1Entry, ets_A1Entry, ets_TC2Entry, ets_A2Entry
21487  global CHA_RC_HP, CHB_RC_HP, CHA_TC1, CHA_TC2, CHB_TC1, CHB_TC2
21488  global CHA_A1, CHA_A2, CHB_A1, CHB_A2
21489  global cha_TC1Entry, cha_TC2Entry, chb_TC1Entry, chb_TC2Entry
21490  global cha_A1Entry, cha_A2Entry, chb_A1Entry, chb_A2Entry
21491 
21492  if Auto_ETS_Comp.get() == 1:
21493  try:
21494  MulX = float(HtMulEntry.get())
21495  #
21496  Value = float(ets_TC1Entry.get()) * MulX
21497  cha_TC1Entry.delete(0,"end")
21498  cha_TC1Entry.insert(0, Value)
21499  cha_A1Entry.delete(0,"end")
21500  cha_A1Entry.insert(0, ets_A1Entry.get())
21501  chb_TC1Entry.delete(0,"end")
21502  chb_TC1Entry.insert(0, Value)
21503  chb_A1Entry.delete(0,"end")
21504  chb_A1Entry.insert(0, ets_A1Entry.get())
21505  #
21506  Value = float(ets_TC2Entry.get()) * MulX
21507  cha_TC2Entry.delete(0,"end")
21508  cha_TC2Entry.insert(0, Value)
21509  cha_A2Entry.delete(0,"end")
21510  cha_A2Entry.insert(0, ets_A2Entry.get())
21511  chb_TC2Entry.delete(0,"end")
21512  chb_TC2Entry.insert(0, Value)
21513  chb_A2Entry.delete(0,"end")
21514  chb_A2Entry.insert(0, ets_A2Entry.get())
21515  except:
21516  MulX = 1.0

21524 def SettingsUpdate():
21525  global GridWidth, TRACEwidth, TRACEaverage, Vdiv, HarmonicMarkers, ZEROstuffing, RevDate
21526  global Settingswindow, SettingsStatus, ZSTuff, TAvg, VDivE, TwdthE, GwdthE, HarMon
21527  global CHA_TC1, CHA_TC2, CHB_TC1, CHB_TC2
21528  global CHA_A1, CHA_A2, CHB_A1, CHB_A2, TrgLPFEntry, Trigger_LPF_length
21529  global cha_TC1Entry, cha_TC2Entry, chb_TC1Entry, chb_TC2Entry
21530  global cha_A1Entry, cha_A2Entry, chb_A1Entry, chb_A2Entry
21531 
21532  try:
21533  GW = int(eval(GwdthE.get()))
21534  if GW < 1:
21535  GW = 1
21536  GwdthE.delete(0,END)
21537  GwdthE.insert(0, int(GW))
21538  if GW > 5:
21539  GW = 5
21540  GwdthE.delete(0,END)
21541  GwdthE.insert(0, int(GW))
21542  except:
21543  GwdthE.delete(0,END)
21544  GwdthE.insert(0, GridWidth.get())
21545  GridWidth.set(GW)
21546  #
21547  try:
21548  T_length = int(eval(TrgLPFEntry.get()))
21549  if T_length < 1:
21550  T_length = 1
21551  TrgLPFEntry.delete(0,END)
21552  TrgLPFEntry.insert(0, int(GW))
21553  if T_length > 100:
21554  T_length = 100
21555  TrgLPFEntry.delete(0,END)
21556  TrgLPFEntry.insert(0, int(GW))
21557  except:
21558  TrgLPFEntry.delete(0,END)
21559  TrgLPFEntry.insert(0, Trigger_LPF_length.get())
21560  Trigger_LPF_length.set(T_length)
21561  #
21562  try:
21563  TW = int(eval(TwdthE.get()))
21564  if TW < 1:
21565  TW = 1
21566  TwdthE.delete(0,END)
21567  TwdthE.insert(0, int(TW))
21568  if TW > 5:
21569  TW = 5
21570  TwdthE.delete(0,END)
21571  TwdthE.insert(0, int(TW))
21572  except:
21573  TwdthE.delete(0,END)
21574  TwdthE.insert(0, TRACEwidth.get())
21575  TRACEwidth.set(TW)
21576  # Number of average sweeps for average mode
21577  try:
21578  TA = int(eval(TAvg.get()))
21579  if TA < 1:
21580  TA = 1
21581  TAvg.delete(0,END)
21582  TAvg.insert(0, int(TA))
21583  if TA > 16:
21584  TA = 16
21585  TAvg.delete(0,END)
21586  TAvg.insert(0, int(TA))
21587  except:
21588  TAvg.delete(0,END)
21589  TAvg.insert(0, TRACEaverage.get())
21590  TRACEaverage.set(TA)
21591  # Number of vertical divisions for spectrum / Bode
21592  try:
21593  VDv = int(eval(VDivE.get()))
21594  if VDv < 1:
21595  VDv = 1
21596  VDivE.delete(0,END)
21597  VDivE.insert(0, int(VDv))
21598  if VDv > 16:
21599  VDv = 16
21600  VDivE.delete(0,END)
21601  VDivE.insert(0, int(VDv))
21602  except:
21603  VDivE.delete(0,END)
21604  VDivE.insert(0, Vdiv.get())
21605  Vdiv.set(VDv)
21606  # number of Harmonic Markers in SA
21607  try:
21608  HM = int(eval(HarMon.get()))
21609  if HM < 1:
21610  HM = 1
21611  HarMon.delete(0,END)
21612  HarMon.insert(0, int(HM))
21613  if HM > 9:
21614  HM =9
21615  HarMon.delete(0,END)
21616  HarMon.insert(0, int(HM))
21617  except:
21618  HarMon.delete(0,END)
21619  HarMon.insert(0, HarmonicMarkers.get())
21620  HarmonicMarkers.set(HM)
21621  # The zero stuffing value is 2 ** ZERO stuffing, calculated on initialize
21622  try:
21623  ZST = int(eval(ZSTuff.get()))
21624  if ZST < 1:
21625  ZST = 1
21626  ZSTuff.delete(0,END)
21627  ZSTuff.insert(0, int(ZST))
21628  if ZST > 5:
21629  ZST = 5
21630  ZSTuff.delete(0,END)
21631  ZSTuff.insert(0, int(ZST))
21632  except:
21633  ZSTuff.delete(0,END)
21634  ZSTuff.insert(0, ZEROstuffing.get())
21635  ZEROstuffing.set(ZST)
21636 #
21637  try:
21638  TC1A = float(cha_TC1Entry.get())
21639  CHA_TC1.set(TC1A)
21640  if TC1A < 0:
21641  TC1A = 0
21642  cha_TC1Entry.delete(0,END)
21643  cha_TC1Entry.insert(0, TC1A)
21644  except:
21645  cha_TC1Entry.delete(0,END)
21646  cha_TC1Entry.insert(0, CHA_TC1.get())
21647  try:
21648  TC2A = float(cha_TC2Entry.get())
21649  CHA_TC2.set(TC2A)
21650  if TC2A < 0:
21651  TC2A = 0
21652  cha_TC2Entry.delete(0,END)
21653  cha_TC2Entry.insert(0, TC2A)
21654  except:
21655  cha_TC2Entry.delete(0,END)
21656  cha_TC2Entry.insert(0, CHA_TC2.get())
21657  #
21658  try:
21659  Gain1A = float(cha_A1Entry.get())
21660  CHA_A1.set(Gain1A)
21661  except:
21662  cha_A1Entry.delete(0,END)
21663  cha_A1Entry.insert(0, CHA_A1.get())
21664  try:
21665  Gain2A = float(cha_A2Entry.get())
21666  CHA_A2.set(Gain2A)
21667  except:
21668  cha_A2Entry.delete(0,END)
21669  cha_A2Entry.insert(0, CHA_A2.get())
21670  #
21671  try:
21672  TC1B = float(chb_TC1Entry.get())
21673  CHB_TC1.set(TC1B)
21674  if TC1B < 0:
21675  TC1B = 0
21676  chb_TC1Entry.delete(0, END)
21677  chb_TC1Entry.insert(0, TC1B)
21678  except:
21679  chb_TC1Entry.delete(0,END)
21680  chb_TC1Entry.insert(0, CHB_TC1.get())
21681  try:
21682  TC2B = float(chb_TC2Entry.get())
21683  CHB_TC2.set(TC2B)
21684  if TC2B < 0:
21685  TC2B = 0
21686  chb_TC2Entry.delete(0, END)
21687  chb_TC2Entry.insert(0, TC2B)
21688  except:
21689  chb_TC2Entry.delete(0,END)
21690  chb_TC2Entry.insert(0, CHB_TC2.get())
21691  #
21692  try:
21693  Gain1B = float(chb_A1Entry.get())
21694  CHB_A1.set(Gain1B)
21695  except:
21696  chb_A1Entry.delete(0,END)
21697  chb_A1Entry.insert(0, CHB_A1.get())
21698  try:
21699  Gain2B = float(chb_A2Entry.get())
21700  CHB_A2.set(Gain2B)
21701  except:
21702  chb_A2Entry.delete(0,END)
21703  chb_A2Entry.insert(0, CHB_A2.get())
21704  # set ETS base comp
21705  #
21706  SetETSComp()
